				"kuvausteksti" : "Polar is the pioneer of wearable sports and fitness technology and the leader of heart rate monitoring for more than 35 years. We at Polar believe that all people are made to move - this is why we cater for all levels of fitness. We combine leading physiological research with cutting-edge technology solutions and innovative design to create products that help everyone achieve more, whether their goal is to be more active in daily life, boost sports performance or break world records. Our devices are accompanied by Polar Flow, the app and web service that acts as a personalized window into the user's life data. Our wide range of products, apps, services and group solutions reflects Polar's mission: to help everyone live a healthy and happy life.\r\n\r\nAt Polar, you will be working for a global company with an international team of professionals who truly believe in what they do.\r\n\r\nWe are now looking for the following professional\r\n\r\nWeb Expert, Team Pro for a permanent position\r\n\r\nWe're searching for talented web software expert to join our Polar Team Pro -team. You will be part of our highly skilled and enthusiastic development program team focusing to deliver high quality real-time player monitoring and tracking systems to highly ranked and globally acknowledged sports teams, athletes and coaches.\r\n\r\nYou will take care of team pro web solution development from requirements to production with good command of technical skills and strong willingness to complete your daily tasks with can-do attitude. In addition to different project stakeholders, you will be working closely with software development team members; product owner, scrum master, testing specialists and UI designers to ensure high quality solutions to our customers worldwide.\r\n\r\nIf you feel that you are ready to take the next step in your professional career -apply now! We offer you a truly once in a life time opportunity to create totally new sporting solutions and concepts to world leading sport teams. Don't just watch the games from your couch, but be part of the game and join the Polar team!\r\n\r\nWe expect you to have:\r\n- Experience in web development tools and technologies (such as Java, JavaScript, HTML/CSS, React library, Play framework, RESTful systems, microservice architectures, etc.)\r\n- Strong understanding of agile software development methodologies\r\n- Continuous integration and test automation development experience\r\n- Fluent use of Git, Jenkins, Bitbucket Server and Jira\r\n- Good written and spoken English\r\n- Strong cooperation & problem solving skills\r\n\r\nThe position is located in Kempele, Finland.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.polar.com/en/b2b_products/team_sports\r\n\r\nPlease note that position will be filled when suitable candidate is found.\r\n\r\nFor further information please contact Mr. Kai Pietilä, kai.pietila@polar.com or tel +358 (0)8 5202 367. Please send your application to recruitment@polar.com with the title of 'Web Expert'.",
