				"kuvausteksti" : "Join us - we create unique arctic experiences in Kemi!\r\n \r\nKemi Tourism Ltd. offers unique arctic experiences in Kemi, Sea Lapland. We operate the Icebreaker Sampo and Kemi SnowCastle with its restaurants, hotel and activities. Our clients are international and they come from over 50 countries.\r\n \r\nWe are now recruiting staff for winter season 2017-18. We offer versatile work profiles in our attractions and services. You also have the possibility to work in several tasks during the season - all of them are dedicated to the wellbeing of our customers.\r\n We appreciate open and positive attitude, customer serving skills, resistance and flexibility - in tourism business situations can change quickly. We want you to have fluent English speaking skills (and we appreciate also German, French, Spanish and \r\nChinese skills).\r\nYou have completed the Finnish Food Hygiene Certificate and the Finnish Alcohol Serving Licence. You have either strong previous experience or training in your field of work.\r\nWe hope that you are exuberant and social. You should have completed First Aid (EA1) training.\r\nOur company is no-smoking\r\nwww.visitkemi.fi",
