				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for an Transverse Test Analysis Engineer for our client in Olkiluoto. The job starts as soon as the right person has been found and lasts approximately for 9 months.\r\n\r\nThe successful candidate should posses the following skills:\r\n\r\n- Engineering Degree in Mechanical, Electrical and/or I&C\r\n- At least 2 years of field experience in nuclear power plant or preliminary period within nuclear project. Oil & Gas and shipbuilding experience can also be considered\r\n- PWR technology and EPR technology knowledge would be a plus\r\n- System design experience would be a plus\r\n- MS Office knowledge\r\n- Capable of writing documents and reports\r\n- Versatile, adaptable, rigorous\r\n- Good interpersonal skills, client and results oriented\r\n- Attention to detail\r\n- Fluent English required, ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Working inside Commissioning Department and under Technical Commissioning Manager's responsibility\r\n- Validation of the commissioning documentation through the RFA (Ready For Application) process for the NSSS (Nuclear Steam Supply System) and BNI (Balance of Nuclear Island) and participation in the RFA meeting with the Client\r\n- Test reports analysis for the NSSS and BNI\r\n- Preparation of the Result Record Sheets (RRS) before the commissioning tests of motors, actuators and control valves and binary and analog measuring circuits, including the review of design changes and open points before testing\r\n- Review of RRS after testing, and issuance or review of the associated test reports\r\n- Technical event analysis\r\n- Technical control of the commissioning master files\r\n\r\nPlease apply for this position through www.rtkhenkilostopalvelu.fi Don't forget to attach your updated CV in English and salary request to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Eveliina Tayfur +35844412466 or eveliina.tayfur@rtkpalvelu.fi\r\n\r\nRTK-Henkilöstöpalvelu Oy's core business is long-term placement of rental personnel and recruitment. We operate as a reliable and professional partner for human resource services. The purpose of our operation is to bring employees and employers together in an easy and flexible way. Our aim is to find suitable personnel for our customers in long-term contracts.",
