				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them.\r\nWe are currently looking for Spare Part Engineers/Technicians for our client in Olkiluoto, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain Tasks and Responsibilities\r\n\r\n-Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time\r\n-Review and search for items in warehouse inventories\r\n-Generate Purchase Requests and technical Requisition Files\r\n-Follow-up of the Purchase Requests and Purchase Orders\r\n-Coordinate the required inspections of the spare parts\r\n-Generate Issue Notes to receive parts from the warehouse\r\n-Provide the documentation of the spare parts for maintenance reports and other work orders\r\n-Prepare the pick-up and handover of required spare parts\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n-Engineering Degree/Diploma with an emphasis on Mechanical Engineering (or similar) or experienced Technician with a Mechanical or Electromechanical background\r\n-Understanding of technical documentation for power plant components\r\n-General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology\r\n-Computer literacy in MSOffice\r\n-Good communicator\r\n-Experience with warehousing and related software seen as beneficial\r\n-Understanding of quality documentation and certificates seen as beneficial\r\n-First experience with specifications and design documents (Construction Plans) are favorable\r\n-Exposure to facets of either maintenance, commissioning, quality, warehousing, procurement or spare parts is mandatory\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills:\r\n\r\n-Fluent in English\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
