				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Electrical As-Built Documentation Engineer for our client in Olkiluoto Nuclear Power Plant, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities: \r\n\r\n- Work within the team of As-Built-Documentation for electrical entity\r\n- Checking of data bases regarding correct revision and implementation of all changes in electrical documentation (Field Change Requests, Design Change Requests, Open Points, etc.)\r\n- Modification of AutoCAD and pdf drawings where necessary to get documentation in As-Built state\r\n- Coordination with sub-suppliers where As-Builts are in scope of sub-suppliers\r\n- Reporting of work progress to As-Built Task Leader of Electrical Engineering\r\n\r\nRequirements: \r\n\r\n- Experience in electrical engineering documentation\r\n- Work confidently within site teams and HBO\r\n- Able to express clearly verbally and in writing \r\n- Adapt successfully to changing situations & environments\r\n- Gather information systematically to establish facts & principles\r\n- Good problem solving skills\r\n- Manage time effectively and able to work to deadlines\r\n- Motivated to solve problems/ issues & target oriented\r\n\r\nTechnical:\r\n\r\n- Experienced in Electrical Engineering or related (e.g. Cabling, Transformer, Electrical Actuators, Switch gears, Motors, UPS-Systems, etc.)\r\n- Basic knowledge of the OL3-Project (tools, project-structure, teams & documentation)\r\n- Knowledge in AutoCAD, pdf-processing, MS-Office (including MS Access)\r\n- Basic knowledge in PDMS (Plant Design Management Tool - no operator skills needed)\r\n- Knowledge in working with data bases\r\n\r\nLanguages:\r\n\r\n- Fluent English required\r\n- French, German and Finnish language skills considered as a benefit\r\n\r\nDrug test and concise security clearance will be done for the selected person in order to get the permanent access to OL3 site.\r\n\r\nPlease note that due to client's urgent need only applicants with a valid working permit / EU-citizenship can be considered.\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
