				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Electrical & Instrumentation Test Analysis Engineer  for our client in Olkiluoto Nuclear Power Plant, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Preparation of the Result Record Sheets (RRS) for the commissioning tests of the motors, actuators and control valves and the binary and analog measuring circuits, including the review, COVER changes and all open point testing\r\n- Update the above mentioned RRSs\r\n- Review of the above mentioned RRSs after testing by the field electrical and I&C commissioning team, including the review of the reference configuration, design changes and open points after testing\r\n- Preparation, insurance and review of the associated test reports\r\n- Interface with engineering, construction and commissioning branches to evaluate impact of the design changes and open points on the test of the motors, actuators and control valves and measuring binary and analog circuits and test results\r\n- Technical support to Technical Commissioning Branch SCI 52/SCI 53 NI Team Leader\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n- Engineering degree in mechanical and/ or I&C disciplines\r\n- At least 2 years field experience in nuclear power plant or preliminary working period within nuclear project. Oil & gas, ship building or similar experience can also be considered\r\n- PWR & EPR technology knowledge considered as a benefit\r\n- System design experience considered as a benefit\r\n- MS office knowledge\r\n- Document writing capacity\r\n- Versatile, adaptable and rigorous\r\n- Good interpersonal skills\r\n- Client & result oriented\r\n- Good attention to detail\r\n\r\nLanguages: \r\n\r\n- Fluent English required\r\n- Other languages considered as a benefit\r\n\r\nDrug test and concise security clearance will be done for the selected person in order to get the permanent access to OL3 site.\r\n\r\nPlease note that due to clients urgent need only applicants with a valid working permit / EU-citizenship can be considered.\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
