				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for I&C Change Database Engineers for our client in Olkiluoto Nuclear Power Plant, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities: \r\n\r\n1. I&C Commissioning change database: \r\n\r\n- Drafting a database specification according to change management procedures (PI6.10 rev.C)\r\n- Design and implementation of the change database to record all the temporary modifications and changes from existing databases and I&C systems\r\n- Implementation of relevant reports functions\r\n- Preparing and performing training's to I&C and process commissioning teams\r\n- Administration and upgrade of I&C change database according to procedure updates\r\n\r\n2. Simulation Management: \r\n\r\n- Defining assessment to be done before a simulation block implementation\r\n- Managing temporary modifications removal\r\n- Track deviations in TM traceability processes\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n- Experience in database creation, implementation and administration is mandatory\r\n- Knowledge of Visual Basic, SQL, Ms Access and Excel\r\n- Experience in configuration management\r\n- Experience in I&C design/ engineering/ commissioning considered as a benefit\r\n- EPR knowledge considered as a benefit\r\n\r\nSkills required: \r\n\r\n- Analysis and synthesis skills\r\n- Rigorous, especially for adherence to procedures in force on site including configuration management\r\n- Good relational and communication skills\r\n- Good oral expression & writing skills\r\n- Ability to work in international team\r\n- Aware of HSE and IT security aspects\r\n\r\nLanguages: \r\n\r\n- Fluent English required\r\n- Ability with French, German or Finnish considered as a benefit\r\n\r\nDrug test and concise security clearance will be done for the selected person in order to get the permanent access to OL3 site.\r\n\r\nPlease note that due to client's urgent need only applicants with a valid working permit / EU-citizenship can be considered.\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
