				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for Electrical and I&C PTW Work Planner for our client in Olkiluoto. The job starts as soon as the right candidate has been found and lasts for 12 months.\r\n\r\nCANDIDATE PROFILE\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n\r\n- Several years of experience with work scheduling\r\n- At least 3 years commissioning and/or operation of nuclear power plants\r\n- Experience in mechanical/electrical and I&C installation and commissioning of OL3\r\n- At least 3 years of experience with work orders and blockings\r\n- General understanding of mechanics, thermodynamics, fluid mechanics and measurement/instrumentation technology\r\n- General understanding in electrical and I&C technology\r\n- Computer literacy in MS Office\r\n- Ability to use the different project data bases, software etc\r\n- Deep knowledge of MS Project\r\n- Deep knowledge of Primavera\r\n- Knowledge about the OL3 tecnology\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills\r\n\r\n- Fluent in English\r\n- Finnish, German and French language skills are regarded as beneficial\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Create work plans on PTW/PTT basis considering all disciplines\r\n- Harmonize the different works between all disciplines\r\n- Schedule these PTW/PTT in the very best way for the overall progress of the plant\r\n\r\nPlease apply for this position: www.rtkhenkilostopalvelu.fi Don't forget to attach your updated CV in English and salary request to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Eveliina Tayfur +358444124622 or eveliina.tayfur@rtkpalvelu.fi\r\n\r\nRTK-Henkilöstöpalvelu Oy's core business is long-term placement of rental personnel and recruitment. We operate as a reliable and professional partner for human resource services. The purpose of our operation is to bring employees and employers together in an easy and flexible way. Our aim is to find suitable personnel for our customers in long-term contracts.",
