				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for I&C Commissioning engineer for our client in Olkiluoto. The job starts as soon as the right candidate has been found and lasts for 12 months.\r\n\r\nCANDIDATE PROFILE\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n\r\n- Engineer or Technician degree in applicable field of study\r\n- Experience in commissioning activities\r\n- Experience in design / engineering - test bay of commissioning based on the TXP and/or TXS product line\r\n- Familiar with testing procedures\r\n- Ability to perform functional analysis, covering on one hand the process requirements, and on the other hands the I&C implementation\r\n- EPR knowledge considered as a plus\r\n- Familiarity with Access considered as benefit\r\n- Good relational and communication skills\r\n- Analysis and synthesis skills\r\n- Rigorous especially for adherence to procedures in force on site including configuration management\r\n- Good oral expression and writing skills\r\n- Ability to work in an international team\r\n- Aware of HSE and IT security aspects\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills\r\n\r\n- Fluent in English\r\n- Finnish and German language skills are regarded as beneficial\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\n1. Analysis:\r\n\r\n- Highlight of I&C logic covered by process commissioning instructions, and if needed, test bay results\r\n- Check of I&C function coverage, based on System Descriptions\r\n- Proposal of process commissioning instructions improvement, in order to ensure the expected I&C function test coverage\r\n- Management of the Access database collecting all evidences of test coverage\r\n\r\n2. Test procedure elaboration:\r\n\r\n- Elaboration of Commissioning Instructions \"CI69\" aiming at covering previously identified gaps, based on I&C simulation\r\n- Definition of the simulations needed for their implementation on site\r\n- Scheduling of test execution\r\n\r\n3. Execution:\r\n\r\n- Execution of the tests with support of related I&C commissioning sections\r\n- Issuance of the test reports including the assessment of the I&C test outcomes\r\n- Delivery of test report to related process commissioning engineer\r\n\r\n4. Control and monitoring:\r\n\r\n- Provide inputs to progress measurement and reporting\r\n- Initiate corrective actions in case of deviations\r\n-\r\n\r\nPlease apply for this position: www.rtkhenkilostopalvelu.fi Don't forget to attach your updated CV in English and salary request to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Eveliina Tayfur +358444124622 or eveliina.tayfur@rtkpalvelu.fi\r\n\r\nRTK-Henkilöstöpalvelu Oy's core business is long-term placement of rental personnel and recruitment. We operate as a reliable and professional partner for human resource services. The purpose of our operation is to bring employees and employers together in an easy and flexible way. Our aim is to find suitable personnel for our customers in long-term contracts.",
