				"etatyo" : false,
				"kuvausteksti" : "As our UI Designer, you will be a member of our Product Development team with the main goal of creating amazing user experiences. You will work on every stage of the UI design process, from creating concepts to transforming those concepts into beautiful and intuitive user interfaces together with our developers, clients, and other stakeholders.\r\n \r\n\r\nYour responsibilities will include:\r\n\r\n- Collaborating with Product Management and Product Development to define and implement easy-to-use designs and visuals\r\n- Creating and testing UI concepts and prototypes based on customer needs\r\n- Designing new features and improving existing ones\r\n- Ensuring a consistent UI design that matches our globally recognized HappyOrNot 4 Smileys brand\r\n \r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate will have:\r\n\r\n- A keen eye for clean and beautiful designs \r\n- Attention to detail \r\n- Experience producing graphical assets\r\n- Experience with HTML and CSS\r\n- Proficiency in English, both written and spoken\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat we offer\r\n\r\nOur work environment is open, energetic, multicultural, flexible, and positive. We have a significant international client base and a large reseller network all over the world. Joining our happy team means becoming part of the company behind the globally recognized 4 Smileys whose mission is to make people happier - one Smiley at a time.\r\n\r\n--\r\n\r\nWhen applying, make sure to include your CV and tell us briefly why you would be a good fit. Also, please include your salary request. The position will be filled as soon as suitable candidate is found.\r\n \r\n\r\nAbout us\r\n\r\nHappyOrNot® is the global leader in instant customer and employee satisfaction reporting. Our innovative feedback collecting Smileys and intelligent data analytics Reporting Service help our clients to improve their customer experience, relationships, and employee engagement. We serve nearly 4,000 companies across 117 countries and have collected and reported on over a half billion feedbacks.\r\n\r\nP.S: don't forget to check us out on our website and social media!",
