				"kuvausteksti" : "Vaisto Solutions aims to become a forerunner in the world of Deep Tech. We bring together smart people, smart machines and smart ways of working to create concrete business benefits and unique value. We exist to help our customers develop winning products and experiences.\r\n\r\nJOB DESCRIPTION\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a Test Automation expert to join our team of enthusiastic professionals. You will be working with our team creating testing solutions for our industrial customers.\r\nYour role\r\n\r\nOur customers want our expertise and deserve excellent service. You'll be mainly working with our project team helping Vaisto customers getting the full benefit out of Test Automation. Work requires good communication skills and ability work independently depending on nature of the projects. Main tasks include following:\r\n Design and implement test solutions utilising test automation, ensuring test development processes and automated test suites are efficient\r\n Executing and analysing automated test results; participating in troubleshooting issues with different teams to drive towards root cause identification and resolution\r\n Communicating with project management and development teams to develop a strong understanding of the project and product and testing objectives.\r\n\r\nREQUIREMENTS\r\n\r\n Prior experience in QA and in Test Automation\r\n Expertise with automated testing tools like: Robot Frameworks, Cucumber etc.\r\n DevOps toolchain: CI (Jenkins, CircleCI), GitHub, Docker, Selenium\r\n Programming/scripting: Python, C++, Java\r\n Web technologies: HTML5, CSS, PHP, JavaScript, MySQL\r\n Operating systems: Linux, Windows\r\n Knowledge of QA & Agile methodologies and processes\r\n Willingness to learn new things continuously\r\n Good communication skills with our customers and internal teams\r\n\r\nWE APPRECIATE\r\n\r\n Willingness to travel (occasionally)\r\n Prior working experience in industrial business. E.g. robotics, manufacturing, industrial automation\r\n Experience with one or more other programming languages like Java, JavaScript, and/or Node.js is seen as an advantage.\r\n\r\nWE OFFER\r\n\r\nThe chance to be part of an forward looking and energetic, non-bureaucratic and capable company building killer solutions for our customers.\r\n\r\nA friendly, fun and diverse workplace where new ideas are valued. Our culture embraces openness, learning, encouragement and having fun.",
