				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \r\n\r\nWe are looking for an IC Commissioning Engineer for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration is 12 months.\r\n\r\nCWS69 procedure intent to provide the evidence that all I&C functions related to Nuclear Island are properly tested, in frame of Commissioning activities. ln order to fulfill with CWS69 procedure. \r\nThe IC Commissioning Engineer has therefore to be able to perform some functional analysis, covering on one hand the process requirements, and on the other hands the I&C implementation.\r\n\r\nLanguage skills:\r\n-Fluent English required. Ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus;\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n-Engineer degree in automation or mechanical field.\r\n-General and technical background expected.\r\n-Experience in commissioning activities and EPR knowledge would be a plus.\r\n-Good oral expression & writing skills.\r\n-Ability to work in an international team.\r\n-Aware of HSE and IT security aspects.\r\n\r\nTechnical skills:\r\n-Knowledge of CWS69 standards. \r\n\r\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For further information please go to www.nipromec.com.",
