				"kuvausteksti" : "N-PRO Resources Oy Ltd is a staffing and recruiting company focusing mainly on needs of our customers in the fields of energy, industry and offshore.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for Cost Controllers for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration 12 months.\r\n\r\nCost Controller for Constructions task include but are not limited to:\r\n-Cost follow-up and internal reporting.\r\n-Construction invoice and purchase request handling for Cost Control.\r\n-Periodical financial reviews related to own scope.\r\n-Periodical closings related to own scope.\r\n-Cash forecast related to own scope.\r\n\r\nRequirements for Cost Controller:\r\n-Master level University or Business school degree with Finance as major.\r\n-Can handle pressure and has some abilities to prioritize also.\r\n-SAP experience (not mandatory), excellent technical skills on Excel.\r\n-Fluent English mandatory. Finnish, French or German is considered an advantage.\r\n\r\nRequired personal skills:\r\n-Analytical and rigorous. Team player but can work also autonomously.\r\n-Reliable, flexible, proactive and solution provider.\r\n-With good communication skills and stress management.\r\n\r\nPositions are filled as soon as suitable candidates are found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi or fill in an application at www.n-pro.fi",
