				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for Administration Coordinator for our client in Olkiluoto. The job starts in November as soon as the right candidate has been found and lasts for 6-12 months.\r\n\r\nCANDIDATE PROFILE\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n\r\n- Sufficient experience on Administration related tasks (1-3 years)\r\n- Driving license (Finland B)\r\n- Flexibility and initiative\r\n- Hardworking, flexible team player who can work independently\r\n- Capacity to work with excel\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills\r\n\r\n- Fluent in English required\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Administration coordinator will coordinate actions related to expatriates arrival and departure\r\n- Coordination of furniture move, first arrival and housing\r\n- Administration coordinator is the first single entry point for expatriates when they arrive\r\n- Responsible of the arrivals and departures follow-up\r\n- Among other duties the person will support other Administration team members when needed\r\n\r\nPlease apply for this position: www.rtkhenkilostopalvelu.fi Don't forget to attach your updated CV in English and salary request to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Eveliina Tayfur +358444124622 or eveliina.tayfur@rtkpalvelu.fi\r\n\r\nRTK-Henkilöstöpalvelu Oy's core business is long-term placement of rental personnel and recruitment. We operate as a reliable and professional partner for human resource services. The purpose of our operation is to bring employees and employers together in an easy and flexible way. Our aim is to find suitable personnel for our customers in long-term contracts.",
