				"kuvausteksti" : "Academic Work is looking for a Junior Consultant to Helsinki! If you are customer focused with good collaboration and communication skills, you might be the right person! This is an excellent opportunity to work with interesting customer projects and experience the digitalization of business processes from a unique viewpoint. Keep reading and apply already today!\r\n\r\nABOUT THE ROLE\r\n\r\nAcademic Work is looking for a Junior Consultant for our client Good Sign.\r\n\r\nYou will be recruited to our client company. Academic Work will take care of the recruitment process, therefore candidates are kindly asked to direct all questions to Academic Work hel01@academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\nJOB DUTIES\r\n\r\nIn this position you will be working as a part of Good Sign's Implementation team. Your daily work includes various steps from different kind of customer projects and processes. You will be working in a team of 6 members with support of more experienced colleagues.\r\n\r\nThe job includes:\r\n\r\n-Analyzing customer's needs together with your senior colleagues\r\n-Selecting business cases for Proof of Concept together with customers\r\n-Configuring Proof of Concept using the Good Sign Software\r\n-Presenting the outcomes of concept or other deliverables to the customer\r\n-Planning and implementing the customer's processes in a production environment\r\n-Supporting customers as their needs evolve\r\n\r\nThis is a great opportunity to work in an innovative environment where the whole team is working together towards common goal. Good Sign also offers good benefits for their employees, such as lunch benefits, extended healthcare, support for physical exercise and cultural events.\r\n\r\nWE ARE LOOKING FOR \r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate has a relevant educational background (e.g. Economics, Technical, IT) and understanding of different business concepts. You have needed technical skills or ability to learn quickly. In order to succeed in this position you have good collaboration and presentation skills. In addition, you communicate fluently both in Finnish and English, other language skills are seen as an advantage.\r\n\r\nApply for this position, if you have:\r\n\r\n-Suitable educational background\r\n-Knowledge in SQL and/or similar databases, or ability to learn quickly\r\n-Interest towards working with clients\r\n-Proactive attitude and willingness to improve your skills\r\n-Fluent communications skills in Finnish and English\r\n\r\nPrevious work experience from service business is seen as a great advantage.\r\n\r\nTo apply for the job you need to register on our website and then click on \"Apply here\". Remember to attach your CV into your application! We only process applications through our website but if you have questions about the position you can reach us via email in hel01@academicwork.fi. Please write the advert ID in the subject field and paste the advert link in the mail. We are continuously screening and contacting candidates so make sure to send your application as soon as possible. Please note that the advert can be removed prior to the last application dates on our external advertising pages. In the event the advert has been removed it is either due to the process being completed or because we have a sufficient number of qualified applications and are proceeding to the selection/interview phase in the process.\r\n\r\nWe are the Home of the Young Professionals. We are experts in recruitment and staffing university students, recently graduated and professionals in the beginning of their career. You can be employed by us as a consultant in one of our client companies or be recruited directly to our client via our recruitment co-operation. You can read more about us at www.academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\nINFORMATION ABOUT THE COMPANY\r\n\r\nGood Sign Oy develops intelligent service management platform for the internet era. Good Sign works actively on telecom, ICT and intelligent traffic with future focus on general internet of services and things.\r\n\r\nThe company employs currently over 20 people. Good Sign has offices in Finland, Netherlands and the USA. Their office in Helsinki is located in Munkkiniemi within a good reach of public transport.",
