				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for a qualified Kindergarten Teacher and Assistant!\r\n\r\nNorthern Stars International Kindergarten, a newly established private international Kindergarten in the city of Järvenpää is looking for a qualified Kindergarten Teacher and Assistant.  \r\n\r\nIn case your Kindergarten teaching qualification was completed outside of Finland, it must have been approved by the Finnish National Agency for Education (Opetushallitus) as official Kindergarten teaching qualification for Finland. \r\n\r\nThe Teacher and Assistant candidate is required to be fluent in English and basic knowledge of Finnish language would be an advantage.\r\n\r\nPrior work experiences in the field would be beneficial but not a pre-requisite as long as the candidate has right qualifications and professionally sound personality. This position will be filled as soon as the suitable candidate is found. \r\n\r\nWorking with children requires an extract from criminal records provided (6 § 2 mom).\r\n\r\nPlease contact us via email with your CV at: admin@northernstar.fi",
