				"kuvausteksti" : "4finance is seeking Data Scientist to join their highly skilled international team in the heart of Helsinki. This is an opportunity to influence decision-making through the delivery of insights. \r\nData Scientist will be responsible for risk assessment models in Helsinki office. \r\nCandidate will report to the Country Manager in Finland and Regional Head of Risk and will work as member of Nordic Risk Team. Approximately 10 to 20 travel days per year are expected.\r\n\r\nMain responsibilities\r\nDevelopment of risk assessment models using various statistical techniques, data gathering and preparation, model development and validation, including peer model reviews, practical application of models etc. \r\nDevelopment and monitoring risk based limits and pricing models\r\nDevelopment and monitoring of fraud models\r\nRegular monitoring of model performance and effectiveness \r\nImprovement of existing modeling techniques \r\nDocumentation of modeling process and results\r\n\r\nSkills and Experience required\r\nMasters degree in Mathematics, Statistics, IT, Finance, Economics or similar area\r\nMinimum of 3+ years of analytical experience in financial institution\r\nMinimum of 2+ years of statistical modelling experience\r\nPrevious experience working with tools as R, SQL and SAS (certification is a plus)\r\nExperience with Python, unstructured data, machine learning is advantage\r\nAbility to present the findings and recommendations to the management\r\nConsulting skills are advantage \r\nAbility to work independently\r\nGood problem-solving skills and creativity\r\nGood knowledge of MS Office, especially Excel \r\nFluent written and spoken Finnish and English \r\nHigh energy level and positive attitude \r\nProven record of leadership in a work setting and/or through extracurricular activities\r\n\r\nAbout us \r\n\r\n4finance is a market-leading short-term loan provider throughout the world. To date, 4finance has provided more than ten million loans to over five million customers. \r\nAt 4finance, we believe that our achievements are based on our ability to attract and retain the right kind of people. That is why we focus on making 4finance a great company to work for. \r\n\r\n- We invest in skills and knowledge of our people \r\n- With 16 offices across the globe, we enjoy working in a multicultural environment \r\n- We are a fast-growing company in an exciting industry\r\n\r\nIf you believe that you are the right person, please apply for this position by sending your CV and salary request to HR@4finance.fi no later than November 30, 2017. \r\nFor more information, please contact us from same email address. We will start interviews already now and fulfill position as soon as we find suitable person.",
