				"kuvausteksti" : "We are hiring an Expert, Electrical Engineering - Switchyard and substation with business mindset and confidence in making decisions and taking initiatives. We need you as a specialist in power transmission and distribution networks related to switchyards and substations.\r\nIn this role, you will be joining our electrical team providing solutions and technical services in operative, sales and development projects. Your location is preferably our headquarter In Finland Vaasa but other Citec office locations in Finland can also be considered.\r\n\r\nMain responsibilities:\r\n\r\nDeveloping concept solutions for switchyards and substations based on the customer targets and criteria\r\nNegotiating and communicating with the customers\r\nActively participating in the sales and offering phase as a specialist\r\nLeading and supporting the detailed design phase\r\nBuilding up the competence in the electrical team globally by mentoring\r\nDeveloping competence continuously\r\n\r\nQualifications:\r\n\r\nM.Sc. or B.Sc. in Electrical Engineering\r\n10 years working experience\r\n3 years of proven design experience for substation and switchyards including lay-outs, specifications, protection, switchgears, cables, connections and communication\r\nSite work experience, e.g. installation supervision, commissioning and testing\r\nKnowledge of applicable standards\r\nExperience in sales projects for equipment delivery or engineering services\r\nCooperative team player with business mindset\r\nFluent verbal and written knowledge in English\r\n\r\nWe offer you:\r\n\r\nExciting and challenging work within domestic and international engineering projects\r\nInternational and flexible work environment\r\nSkilled colleagues and friendly working environment\r\n\r\nWould you like to grab this chance for career development? Join our team of professionals!\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Timo Wolff + 358 50 4320 321 or Rickard Nygård +358 50 4283 862. Please submit you application by 22th September, 2017 via our career pages, www.citec.com/careers.",
