				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for a Cloud/IT infra/Dev Ops engineer to join our Jolla boat. This position is primarily based in our office in Finland in Tampere or Helsinki, but other locations can be considered based on the applicant.\r\n\r\nIn this role you will be developing and maintaining services supporting Sailfish OS devices in the cloud and participate in developing build and release infrastructure. You need to perform troubleshooting and proactive monitoring. You will plan, build and support the environment, as well as manage and support the production environment. You should have good experience in patches, upgrades and maintaining active environments.\r\nThis is a permanent, full-time position and starts immediately once we have found the ideal candidate.\r\n\r\nYou are the person we are looking for, if you\r\n- have experience working with Web/App Servers Administration, Installation, Configuration and Monitoring\r\n- have knowledge of UNIX scripting, and automation\r\n- have experience in maintaining public services in AWS\r\n- have good command of English language, other languages seen as an advantage\r\n- have good team working skills and 'can do' attitude\r\n\r\nWe offer you\r\n- a unique opportunity to work in an international and dynamic company\r\n- a chance to be part of Jolla's growth\r\n- a multicultural, passionate and professional crew to work with\r\n- Please send your CV and application to careers@jolla.com and mark \"Devops Engineer\" to the email subject field. We will call suitable candidates to interviews and fill the position when we have the right match.",
