				"kuvausteksti" : "Android Runtime Technical Lead\r\nWe are currently looking for an Android Runtime Technical Lead to join our Jolla boat. This position can be based in one of our offices in Finland in Helsinki or Tampere, but other locations can be considered based on the applicant.\r\nIn this role you will be evolving the Android Runtime found on Sailfish OS. You will be interacting with many functions of the company. Performing this role will require a good understanding of how Android applications function in practice along with how they interact with components within the Android architecture.\r\nThis is a permanent, full-time position and starts immediately once we have found the ideal candidate.\r\n\r\nYou are the person we are looking for, if you\r\n- have the following technical skills: Java, C/C++ (Qt), Shell scripting (bash), cross-compiling, Android, AOSP development\r\n- have experience with the Android stack from both being a developer for it and of it, knowing the architecture of Android; preferably with experience modifying AOSP\r\n- able to manage a quality product from technical angle while at same time rolling up your sleeves to debug and code when needed\r\n- are a good communicator who pro-actively brings issues to closure\r\n- have a good command of English language, other languages seen as an advantage\r\n- have good team working skills and 'can do' attitude\r\n\r\nWe offer you\r\n- a unique opportunity to work in an international and dynamic company\r\n- a chance to be part of Jolla's growth\r\n- a multicultural, passionate and professional crew to work with\r\n\r\nPlease send your CV and application to careers@jolla.com and mark \"Android Runtime Technical Lead\" to the email subject field. We will call suitable candidates to interviews and fill the position when we have the right match.",
