				"kuvausteksti" : "As our creative and forward-thinking Area Marketing Manager, your role will involve leading localized marketing activities, creating sales enhancing campaigns, supporting event participation, and executing industry specific marketing material for our sales teams and reseller network. As part of our global team in Tampere, Finland, you will have a key role in improving our brand awareness worldwide and growing our business.\r\n\r\nYour responsibilities will include:\r\n\r\n- Creating, executing, and coordinating sales enhancing campaigns and marketing activities to promote our products and services by supporting our subsidiaries and reseller network\r\n- Having a strong focus on creating efficient tactics for lead generation and nurturing\r\n- Increasing our incoming leads significantly\r\n- Leading and developing our trade show and event activities to secure improved ROI\r\n- Supporting our reseller network to ensure they have all necessary content and templates available for marketing and press activities in their respective markets\r\n- Creating an efficient marketing mix for our homebased market with content creation in Finnish\r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate will have:\r\n\r\n- Experience in similar position for several years\r\n- An outstanding understanding of B2B marketing tactics\r\n- A creative mindset and skills to manage with limited budgets, and being innovative to making the most out of these\r\n- Comfort in working with various nationalities and have a pro-active, can-do attitude with a 100% team player mentality\r\n- A (preferably) good understanding of the Customer Experience (CX, CEM) market\r\n- Fluent professional proficiency in English and Finnish, both written and spoken\r\n\r\nThe following are considered as advantages: proficiency in additional languages such as Spanish, French, or German; and experience working with Press.\r\n\r\nWhat we offer\r\n\r\nOur work environment is open, energetic, multicultural, flexible, and positive. We have a significant international client base and a large reseller network all over the world. Joining our happy team means becoming part of the company behind the globally recognized 4 Smileys whose mission is to make people happier - one Smiley at a time.",
