				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them.\r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Civil Engineers for our client in the United Kingdom for Hinkley Point C power plant project. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nHinkley Point C power plant project is the first Nuclear New Build Power Station in 20 years in the UK and it is the largest Nuclear Power Plant Construction project in UK at the moment.\r\n\r\nMain Tasks and Responsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Site experience on major civil / structural engineering projects\r\n- Site supervision of trades labour onsite\r\n- Ability to answer technical civil engineering queries (a civil engineering degree is nearly always essential in site candidates)\r\n- Ability to read designs and interpret this into the construction phase\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n- Degree in Civil Engineering\r\n- Different experience levels are considered\r\n- Strong experience with concrete and reinforced structures\r\n- Experience in technical negotiations, participation in licensing processes in supervisory bodies\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills:\r\n\r\n- Fluent English required\r\n- French considered as a benefit\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
