				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you a person with strong problem-solving skills and can work independently? Is your working style precise and you understand the hygiene standards in food industry? Are you familiar with physical working and not afraid working on night shifts?\r\n\r\n We are currently looking for more than one employee for\r\n\r\n PRESSURE WASHING\r\n\r\n to our customers' sites in Seinäjoki and Nurmo.\r\n\r\n ISS Food hygiene services is specialized in washing manufacture spaces and machines in food factory sites. Our actions are led by a deep knowledge of our customers' manufacture processes and solutions that support our customers' needs both in efficiency and hygiene.\r\n\r\n In this position your job is to clean manufacturing spaces and machines with low-pressure washer. Your working time is between 8 pm and 6 am and we offer you 30-37,5 working hours per week, also during the weekends.\r\n\r\n The job fits for you if you work conscientiously and you are a self-driven person. Previous experience from same kind of job or a proper education is an advantage but we will also train you to the job if you lack earlier experience. We hope that you are used to work physically hard work and you have a good working attitude. Hygiene pass and work safety card are considered a benefit. In your work you need Finnish skills or proper English skills. The sites situate little bit away from the downtown so having a car is an advantage.\r\n\r\n When working for ISS you get competitive salary and a position in an international company. We want to create good quality to our customers and we take work safety issues seriously. People make long careers in our service and are keen on giving their best to our customers.\r\n\r\n Interested? Submit your application already today but no later than 31.12.2017 and join our professional team.",
