				"kuvausteksti" : "Vaadin provides technology, tools, and services for software developers who create web based business oriented applications. Vaadin Framework is a Java web application development framework that is designed to make creation and maintenance of high quality web-based user interfaces easy.\r\n\r\nWe believe in open source, transparency, and that the best user experience wins. We've been in the business for over 15 years and are operating with positive cash flow. Today we have more than 120 people working with us globally with our HQ office in Turku, Finland, and additional offices in Helsinki, Berlin, and Silicon Valley.\r\n\r\nOur framework is currently adopted by more than 100,000 developers, and the user base has grown significantly in recent years, due to the explosion in mobile and other applications. We have customers all over the globe, with the vast majority in Europe and North America.\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a BDR to join our Sales team in Turku, Finland or Berlin, Germany. Your tasks are to nurture the leads, accounts while you are creating sales opportunities making sure we meet our sales targets.\r\n\r\nThis is what your day might look like:\r\nYou start by checking your emails and seeing if your customers request more information about our products and services. You start to answer your emails based on the prioritized order. You have a short meeting with your colleagues to catch up on the last period's tasks and discuss the next period plans. You have some time until your next scheduled call, so you have decided to chat in our online chat service and assist a visitor who is visiting our commercial pages . After agreeing upon the next steps with your lead at the website, you move on to one of the meeting rooms you booked for the calls. After finishing your scheduled call, you start to go through the call-list you prepared yesterday, to follow up your open lead cases from last week. As soon as you finish the call, you log the conservation to the CRM system while your memory is still fresh. During the call you notice that your customer is also interested in our services portfolio, and as the next step, you agree to introduce your colleague who is responsible for the service selling. In one of the calls, you promised to provide your customer an answer on a technical topic that you are not much familiar with, therefore you contact one of our experts to find the accurate answer to fulfill your promise to your customer.\r\nAt the end of the day, you monitor your own activity and the agreed next steps with your customers. You can make a realistic forecast for your sales to hit the numbers in given time. You start to make the next day's call-list by checking your accounts and prospects from the CRM system. It is time to call it a day. You start to think about your wins in helping your customers to succeed in their projects before heading home or having a couple of beers with your colleagues after work.\r\n\r\nTo succeed as our Business Development Representative, we expect you to have\r\n-Proven track record of succeeding in a goal-oriented environment\r\n-Skills in both in lead prospecting and account management tasks\r\n-Good organization and analytical skills\r\n-Strong desire to succeed and positive attitude\r\n-Native level German language skills\r\n-Strong oral and written communication skills in English\r\n-Eager to learn and present technical information\r\n-Comfort level with technical conversations\r\n-Experience working with data, reporting and CRM systems such as HubSpot\r\n-Able to work in fast-paced self-directed environment\r\n-Some experience in a similar type sales role\r\n-Studies in Information Technology or Business Administration (Bachelor's Degree or Master's degree)\r\n\r\nWe offer\r\n-A chance to be a part of a fast growing international software company with a community of over 150.000 software developers\r\n-Clear career development path\r\n-Position in a growing and prosperous organization\r\n-A creative and friendly work environment with minimal bureaucracy\r\n-Flexible working hours\r\n-Competitive salary, excellent benefits, and commission based compensation plan\r\n-Assistance for relocation offered.\r\n\r\nCandidates will be contacted as they apply, and the position will be fulfilled as soon as a suitable candidate is found. \r\nSend your resume and application today!\r\n\r\nFor questions or more info don't hesitate to contact us at jobs@vaadin.com",
