				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for an industry leader with a potential interest in taking the company to the international level. Our company is a family business with registrated hat designs and needed equipment. We have experience of some years on the fashion market in Finland. Marketing research to Russia, Estonia and Spain showed a steady buyer interest in our products. Currently, we promote our products in Japan and we are participating in a 2-year project in cooperation with one university in Finland. Our customers include women, men and children. Our products are presented all over Finland in specialized hats stores as well as in Finnish design stores. \r\n\r\nHere is a list that we have in company's stock:\r\n-over 80 Autumn/Winter, over 40 Spring/Summer, over 10 children model patterns\r\n-about 1000-1200 ready and shaped products\r\n-GRAFIS software (licence)\r\n-5 industrial sewing machines\r\n-crease 40 X 60 cm\r\n-wooden beams for hats\r\n-big cutting board\r\n-digital table for digitalizing patterns to the computer\r\n-fabrics, stiffeners, threads\r\n-plastic, baseball visor blanks\r\n-real anchor buttons (gold and silver)\r\n-small, white cardboard boxes for to send products\r\n\r\nThe company is at the point where new innovations should be made e.g. by taking new point of views to the business. Our 5 years business plan is covering e.g. the usage of robotics. \r\nGot interested in this small design company? Please, contact salecontacts2017@gmail.com",
