				"kuvausteksti" : "The owners of Barstown house live in County Kildare which is c 25 kms from the centre of Dublin city on the east coast of Ireland. They have a commercial business on the premises and also have several horses and other animals which they need \r\nhelp with. This includes 3 horses and 3 ponies, 2 dogs and chickens.\r\n\r\nWanted person with experience in caring from horses and ponies with ability to ride.\r\n\r\nEssential requirements:\r\nDriver essential.\r\n\r\nThe owners of Barstown house live in County Kildare which is c 25 kms from the centre of Dublin city on the east coast of Ireland. They have a commercial business on the premises and also have several horses and other animals.\r\n\r\nThey are looking for a 'live in' rider groom to help with these animals to start as soon at possible till the end of April 2018 or longer.  \r\nApplicants needs to be able to do all the normal stable jobs, cleaning stables, feed and watering and cleaning the horses, taking care of the equipment and being able to ride.  \r\n\r\nWe offer accommodation and food in the family home and welcome all enquiries - we need someone to start as soon as possible and to stay at least 6 months - with paid breaks to go home for Christmas/new year or other short visits.\r\n\r\nWe are near Dublin city near the University town of MAYNOOTH which has plenty of young people and we have references from previous employees.  We look forward to receiving your information.\r\nNon smoker on the premises please.\r\n\r\nFull accommodation on premises.  No living expenses for electricity, heating etc.  \r\nSkype interview or contact by email/facebook etc.  Possibly help with the cost of travel to/from Ireland.",
