				"kuvausteksti" : "Mrs. Camilla Caffolla is looking for a Swedish speaking child carer.\r\nEssential requirements:\r\nMust have some child care experience. Must be Swedish speaking as mother is Swedish and she would like her children to speak Swedish at home.  \r\nMust have references of some sort.\r\nDrivers license an advantage.  \r\n\r\nDesirable requirements:\r\nMust have clean police certificate to work with children in Ireland.  It would be helpful if you like animals as they family have 2 large dogs and several horses and ponies and are interested in country lifestyle although they live within commuter distance of Dublin.  Both parents work and grandparents live as neighbours.\r\n\r\nFull accommodation and food - own bedroom/bathroom in the family home. Skype interview. References from previous employees",
