				"kuvausteksti" : "L&L Europe Ltd is interested in speaking to talented and motivated individuals for their Customer Support role. We are a successful international online casino operator with many high quality brands in our portfolio. With the massive increase of players, we are continuously growing and need you to help us give players the best online support in the market. We will buy you a flight to Malta and housing for 2+ weeks when you get here so you can be sure to have a smooth transition to a new country.  L&L Europe LTD will take care of you, we have been helping people move to Malta for many years now and always had great success here.\r\n\r\nEmployees of L&L Europe Ltd enjoy a social and healthy working environment. In terms of work place environment, we are one of the top companies to work for in Malta. There is a way to combine work with being happy. When you spend time at the office, why not enjoy it? Choose L&L Europe and you'll have a great time with colleagues and make true friends.\r\n\r\nOur customer support systems are easy to learn even if you have no experience in gaming. We will give you excellent training on them and the gaming industry as a whole. If this is your first support or gaming role, we know there is a lot to learn. We expect you'll be slower at the start and might make some mistakes. Then after a month or two you'll be quicker and making less mistakes. Simple right? Also, we do not push our agents to hit targets as we believe in putting the players first. We want you to speak to the players like a friend, there are no forced scripts or chat time limits. You get to resolve issues directly instead of waiting for a manager to clear a decision. As avid casino players ourselves, we know that good customer support is based around well trained, naturally speaking, and empowered staff.\r\n\r\nWe believe in our staff and have centred our company around giving the best working environment in Malta. We love working here and are sure you will too! We know that micromanaging and strict rules causes stress and feelings of distrust. You are given independence to do the job here and you take breaks, have lunch, play in the games room, etc... as you decide.\r\n\r\nOur offices are located in the Mediterranean island of Malta where you will enjoy loads of sunny days! You'll get a free gym membership to stay beach ready all year round.\r\n\r\nThe role:\r\nAnswer players by phone, live chat and e-mail (mostly chat and email)\r\nCreate and translate content about our promotions\r\nFollow validation procedures of customer accounts\r\nProactively contact players\r\nShift work 7 days a week\r\n\r\nYour qualities:\r\nFriendly personality \r\nGreat Finnish and English language skills, spoken and written\r\nCapable of multitasking\r\nBe on time to work shifts\r\nDecent typing speed and know your way around computers\r\n\r\n\r\nInterested but having second thoughts about Malta or the gaming industry? \r\nNo worries! We are ready for you to interview us as much as we talk with you. We want the best people to work here who fit in with our team and will also enjoy Malta. The igaming industry is booming and Malta is a fantastic destination, all around 100% safe and enjoyable from work life to personal life. We encourage you to chat with our current customer support agents so you know who we are, they are free to talk to you about anything and they usually will! What other company gives you that much insight in a new job? We are so confident in our reputation and work environment that we will let you in and find out everything. That has helped us recruit wonderful people who make L&L Europe so special.\r\n\r\nSee how Malta life will give you a new and exciting direction and career.\r\n\r\nTake the opportunity and apply now. Send a CV in English to eures.recruitment.jobsplus@gov.mt. Quote the vacancy name and number in your email (Finnish Speaking Cutomer Support Agent (325932)",
