				"kuvausteksti" : "BOS is an international family owned company and is one of the hidden champions in the automotive industry. We develop and produce innovative mechatronic, kinematic and plastic systems, and are the technology leaders for covering blinds and sun protection systems. With over 7000 employees, we are shaping the global automotive future as actively and dynamically as well as setting standards in comfort, safety, lightweight construction and energy efficiency. At our BOS location in Hungary we offer you an interesting opportunity as an \r\n\r\nProcess Engineer Glass Encapsulation (m/f)\r\n\r\nYour Tasks:\r\n\r\nManage the daily operation process\r\nSet up of new encapsulation machines\r\nTraining of machine setters and operators\r\nCreating necessary documentation\r\nDefine corrective actions and counter measures for quality issues related to product and process\r\nMeasurement of cycle times and balancing of operations\r\nContinuous Improvement\r\n\r\nYour Profile:\r\nExperience in glass encapsulation technology and processes\r\nExperience with gluing related processes\r\nBSc or MSc degree with technical background\r\nFluent English is a must, advanced level of German is preferred and Hungarian language knowledge is a plus\r\n\r\n\r\nWillingness to work abroad (in Hungary)\r\nExcellent teamworker and organizational ability\r\n\r\nWe Offer You:\r\nLong-term perspectives within the automotive industry\r\nProfessional challenges in a positive work environment\r\nPersonal development in a committed and motivated team\r\nAttractive compensation package and relocation allowance\r\n\r\nThis employment complies with the legislation of Germany.",
