				"kuvausteksti" : "Digital Marketing Manager Europe\r\n \r\nPowervision Robot (www.powervision.me) since its inception in 2010 has had the mission to innovate the future focusing on artificial intelligence (AI), robotics, and big data. Powervision has been a market leader in commercial UAV-related products and services including smart drones, data visualization and forecasting, virtual reality and augmented reality. Beyond its headquarters in Beijing, China, Powervision has international offices in Helsinki, Silicon Valley, Boston, Perth, Frankfurt, Shanghai, and Shenzhen.\r\n \r\nWe're looking for a Digital Marketing Manager to join our European team based in Espoo, Finland. The role covers all facets of online marketing, digital customer journeys, social media and advocacy management across the whole European region, focusing on key markets like UK, Germany, France, Netherlands, Italy, and Spain. Powervision is growing rapidly worldwide, and our efficient European marketing team is now looking for you to improve our visibility. The products you will be working with are consumer drones and robots, for both air and water.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a person that is used working in a quickly changing environment, has great prioritizing skills and can work efficiently both independently and as a proactive team member.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities:\r\nDevelop, produce and publish engaging, entertaining and educating content aimed at creating brand awareness and foster advocacy on our social media presences.\r\nEnsure all social media platforms and online efforts (e.g. newsletters) are updated and maintained consistently\r\nMonitor and evaluate competitor activity in the social and digital space to gain and propose actionable insights.\r\nManage Key Opinion Leaders and media relations  \r\nWeb analytics and reporting owner\r\nImplement and optimise marketing automation journeys\r\n\r\nRequirements\r\nBachelor's degree in marketing, communications, advertising or related field.\r\n3+ years of experience, a plus if it's in consumer electronics \r\nDeep understanding of social media trends and how influence marketing works\r\nPassionate about technology and drones in particular (desirable)\r\nWorking knowledge of SEO\r\nWorking knowledge of paid social\r\nExperience in cross-cultural working environments is a plus\r\nPossibly with media connections\r\nStrong analytics skills with focus on proving ROI\r\nExpertise in marketing automation, tools and attribution models\r\nEnglish as working language, German, Spanish, Italian, French or Russian a definitive advantage \r\nGlobal and growth mindset\r\n\r\nWhat we offer you\r\nFront seat in a growing, innovative global company\r\nPossibility to influence the company marketing strategies\r\nSpace to express creativity and develop the own marketing skills\r\nPossibility to travel\r\nCompetitive salary\r\n \r\nWe are interviewing immediately suitable candidates and the role will be filled as soon as the right profile is found. What are you waiting for?! Send us your cover letter and CV as soon as possible to: europe@powervision.me.\r\nWebsite: www.powervision.me",
