				"kuvausteksti" : "KIDE Systems is a rapidly growing startup company in healthtech sector. Our solutions serves greater good by enabling better accessibility and efficiency in clinical imaging and diagnostics. Our customers are optical shops, clinics and hospitals. \r\n\r\nKIDE is now in an exciting growth phase and looking for a motivated Sales Manager to build and expand the sales in DACH. At KIDE you will join a team of energetic and motivated professionals.\r\n\r\n\r\nDesired skills and Experience\r\n\r\n- You are a positive and outgoing person who is great at networking and who can proactively open new doors for KIDE internationally.\r\n\r\n- You're also a driven, motivated sales professional who wants to work in a startup company environment and will take charge of a significant territory and grow the business there. This position requires true entrepreneurial attitude, meaning you are able to work indepedently and proactively.\r\n\r\n- You have a suitable technical and/or business background, preferably with a few years experience from B2B software sales. Also experience selling in the healthcare market is a big plus.\r\n\r\n- You speak native or at least excellent German and fluent English and find it motivating working in an international environment.\r\n\r\n- You are able and willing to travel about 10 days per month.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a job where there is clear structure and set routines, this job is probably not for you. However if you are looking to work in small dynamic company where you can shape the future of the business in an international environment we would like to meet you. We seek an individual who wants to take their shot in a high growth opportunity and wants to be part of building and growing a company. We offer you a competitive salary and opportunity to join the company in an early stage and grow with it. Initially you would work from our Helsinki office, but when you're familiar with our products and KIDE working culture, we enable and even encourage you to relocate abroad.\r\n\r\nPlease send your applications along with desired salary information to rekry@kidesystems.com",
