				"kuvausteksti" : "As an Software Developer you will be a part of our Customer Experience team where you ensure that customer feedback, custom requirements and integrations are implemented with care. We know our clients well and we want to make sure they are excited about our systems.\r\n\r\nIn your role, you will be solving issues, implementing custom functionality and integrations to financial and other property solutions. You have the motivation to make our customers happy and show your enthusiasm while exploring new things. You face challenges with a \"can do\" attitude and you're ready to grab the ball when it's needed.\r\n\r\nWe expect you to have a relevant experience in Software Engineering or Computer Science. You have gained experience in Java software development and have willingness to continue your development in these areas:\r\n- Web technologies, modern web frameworks, especially Vaadin and NativeScript/AJS\r\n- RESTful APIs, S/FTP, MySQL and NoSQL\r\n- JSON, XML\r\n- IDE's, scripting, building tools and version control systems\r\n- Agile product development mindset with a passion for open innovation\r\n\r\nWe are a multicultural company where we expect you to work day-to-day in English. If you want to develop your skills in an open culture, send your application to info@assetti.pro with the title \"Software Developer\". The position will be filled as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nAbout Assetti\r\nAssetti is a fast growing software development company which creates memorable software designs for business and software professionals with a passion. We offer you a great place to succeed and welcome the local Carelian way of living in Lappeenranta. Assetti was chosen as the growth company with most potential in South Carelia in Kasvu Open 2017.\r\n\r\nFor further information, please contact:\r\nShannon Merritt, R&D Manager, +358 40 729 4474, shan@assetti.pro\r\nSamuli Hiltunen, Operations Manager, +358 400 317 347, samuli@assetti.pro",
