				"kuvausteksti" : "Do you have a passion for sales  and experience in  B2B -sales? Does winning deals and achieving goals motivate You in your work? Do You wish to work in a multicultural environment in a growth company? Can you do your work fluently in English and in Finnish? We are at the moment seeking a highly motivated Sales Manager to Finland.\r\n\r\nThe person we are looking for will master and develop the Assetti Sales Process - from making the first contact with a prospect to bringing the deal home! Also if you are Real Estate professional, e.g. real estate agent or broker, who is interested in becoming passionate sales person in PropTech domain - be sure to read further.\r\n\r\nYou will be responsible for \r\nNew customers acquisition for Assetti in Finland\r\nBusiness development and account management for named customers\r\nPartnerships with technology providers and service providers in the market area\r\nAdopting and mastering B2B SaaS sales process \r\n\r\nWhat we expect\r\n- Experience in B2B Sales\r\n- Ability to work independently and prioritize effectively \r\n- Strong written and verbal communication skills\r\n- A strong work ethic; take the initiative and think creatively to get the job done\r\n- Analytical and problem-solving skills\r\n\r\nWe are a multicultural company where we expect you to work day-to-day in English. Send your application to info@assetti.pro with the title \"Sales Manager, Finland. Location is in Lappeenranta or Helsinki. The position will be filled as soon as possible. \r\n\r\nAbout Assetti\r\nAssetti is a fast growing software development company which creates memorable software designs for business and software professionals with a passion. We offer you a great place to succeed and welcome the local Carelian way of living in Lappeenranta. Assetti was chosen as the growth company with most potential in South Carelia in Kasvu Open 2017.\r\n\r\nFor further information, please contact:\r\nHannu Rantanen, CEO, +358 40 537 8722, hannu@assetti.pro",
