				"kuvausteksti" : "We're currently looking for a Test Engineer with solid experience in software testing. Your job is to ensure that quality is present from the idea level all the way to a finished product. You get to build applications that will solve our clients day-to-day business problems. \r\n\r\nAs our new test engineer you are ready to take the ball when it's needed. You're motivated to achieve our targets together with other team members and eager to learn new technologies. You get inspired by working in an open culture where agile teamwork is highly appreciated. \r\n\r\nWe expect you to have a B.Sc, M.Sc. or equivalent in Test Engineering or Computer Science or supporting experience in testing and software development. You enjoy working with different types of duties in realm of quality assurance. You are familiar with the software development process and have willingness to continue your development in these areas:\r\n- Plan and implement test automation activities\r\n- Test automation coding and scripting proficiency\r\n- Mobile testing\r\n- Web technologies, modern web frameworks, especially Vaadin\r\n- Cloud and mobile platforms\r\n- SQL and NOSQL databases.\r\n- SFTP, XML and RESTful integrations\r\n- Continuous Integration Platforms\r\n\r\nWe are a multicultural company where we expect you to work day-to-day in English. If you demonstrate a \"can do\" attitude and are ready to develop your skills, send your application to info@assetti.pro with the title \"Test Engineer\". The position will be filled as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nAbout Assetti\r\nAssetti is a fast growing software development company which creates memorable software designs for business and software professionals with a passion. We offer you a great place to succeed and welcome the local Carelian way of living in Lappeenranta. Assetti was chosen as the growth company with most potential in South Carelia in Kasvu Open 2017.\r\n\r\nFor further information, please contact:\r\nShannon Merritt, R&D Manager, +358 40 729 4474, shan@assetti.pro\r\nSamuli Hiltunen, COO, +358 400 317 347, samuli@assetti.pro",
