				"kuvausteksti" : "RECEPTIONIST\r\nArctic TreeHouse Hotel is a new luxury hotel that was opened in November 2016. We give great importance to the customer experience through design that has been featured internationally and our dedicated team is always willing to go that extra mile for our guests. \r\nWith guests already enquiring for their stay in the Arctic TreeHouse Hotel in 2019, we are happy to open more positions in our team in the Arctic TreeHouse Hotel. If you have a positive attitude, who loves to always exceed the guest's expectations and you wish to work in new, luxury environment with a good team spirit, we are welcoming you for the position of the receptionist. \r\n\r\nOur reception team is known for their wonderful customer service skills even during the busiest moment. If you are looking for a job that is always a learning place and you have a positive approach to tasks with aim to exceed the customer experience, we are offering you an opportunity to grow with the hotel, improve your hospitality skills and provide memorable experiences to our guests.\r\n \r\nOur requirements are that you have great communication skills in two or more languages, you have hygiene and alcohol pass, you are reliable and helpful, you like to work in a team and most importantly, you love guest service. Experience in Opera is a regarded as beneficial.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a full time team-member and we are looking forward to offering a competitive salary and additional staff benefits. \r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please do not hesitate to ask the hotel manager Tina Kaikkonen, tina@arctictreehousehotel.com Applications should be sent to the same email address latest by 15th of November 2017. We fulfill the positions as soon as we find the perfect new team members.",
