				"kuvausteksti" : "PICCOLO\r\nArctic TreeHouse Hotel is a new luxury hotel that was opened in November 2016. We give great importance to the customer experience through design that has been featured internationally and our dedicated team is always willing to go that extra mile for our guests. \r\nWith guests already enquiring for their stay in the Arctic TreeHouse Hotel in 2019, we are happy to open more positions in our team in the Arctic TreeHouse Hotel. If you have a positive attitude, who loves to always exceed the guest's expectations and you wish to work in new, luxury environment with a good team spirit, we are welcoming you for the position of the piccolo. \r\n\r\nOur piccolo team is known for their charm and joy, and are the first ones to start the guest experience on a magical note. If you are looking for a place to bring your personality and social skills to use, as well as have a touch of luxurious customer service skills, we are offering an opportunity to grow with the hotel, improve your hospitality skills and provide memorable experiences to our guests.\r\n\r\nWe require that you have excellent communication skills in two or more languages, you are reliable, flexible and love to assist others and most importantly you breathe hospitality.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for both full-time and part-time team members during the season, and offer you in return a competitive salary and additional team member benefits.\r\n\r\nFor questions and applications, contact Hotel Manager Tina Kaikkonen via e-mail \r\ntina@arctictreehousehotel.com. Applications should be sent out latest 15th November and will be conducting interviews for the applicants throughout the process.",
