				"kuvausteksti" : "Vision Development is a rapidly growing and developing company providing software- and machine vision solutions. Software development for embedded systems and related mobile and IT-solutions are in the heart of our business. The use of model based design is growing especially in functional safety critical projects and in which we are a leading provider in Finland. Our machine vision solutions are ensuring quality and controlling processes in thousands of applications through out the world.    \r\n\r\nWe are looking for a new team player to our frontend development team in Espoo. We are looking for candidates having following experience and knowledge:  \r\n\r\n-strong experience in frontend development using HTML, CSS and JavaScript\r\n-good knowledge of the latest UI techniques  \r\n-experience in working Scrum/Agile  development processes\r\n-understanding about the meaning of good usability, functionality and great visual outlook\r\n-good spoken and written command in English and Finnish \r\n-open mind and eagerness to develop Your professional skills \r\n-relevant MSc or BSc level education and relevant experience from the field helps you to succeed in this position.\r\n    \r\nWe at Vision Company value active forward looking attitude and desire for working on demanding and diverse projects in cooperation with our clientele. We offer modern office space, great team players, open flat organization, market relevant compensation and benefits.",
