				"kuvausteksti" : "Hyped up about mechanics!\r\n\r\nDo you want to work with high level technology and innovative solutions, spiced with top talented engineers and international environment? As the largest global player in smart metering we are able to provide you a top view on energy management solutions and trends. \r\n\r\nWe are looking for a Senior Designer to join our Devices Design Team. You work in smart metering projects with latest technologies, creating concepts and architecture for our smart metering device solutions.\r\n\r\nWith us, you get the opportunity to\r\n\r\n- work with high level technology and innovative solutions at the edge of constantly developing business\r\n- design, model and modify electronic product design\r\n\r\nDo you love challenges, are you passionate with quality and want to use your creativity? Are you familiar with CAD tools like Creo or other feature based tools (Catia/Solid Works/Inventor)? How about concept level modelling, designing and manufacturing of plastic injection molds? Great! Due to our international environment English skills and the ability to create technical documentation is important.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested and have experience in aforementioned, we are more than happy to hear from you!\r\n\r\nThe location of the job is in our Nordics main office at Jyväskylä.\r\n\r\nFor further details please contact Seppo Räihä, seppo.raiha@landisgyr.com, +358 40 531 1287.\r\n\r\nWe wish you to leave your application and CV latest on November 17th, 2017.\r\n\r\n\r\nLandis+Gyr is the leading global provider of integrated energy management solutions for the energy utility sector. We help our customers around the world to improve their energy efficiency and to manage energy better. Landis+Gyr operates worldwide and offers international, inspiring working environment. Our Jyväskylä site is a global technology center for smart metering solutions and the hub for Nordic operations. Read more at landisgyr.eu",
