				"kuvausteksti" : "Do you enjoy putting your hands on demanding test cases? Do you love problem solving and failures do not discourage you?\r\n\r\nGreat, you may be our new Testing Designer, as our Devices Test Team is looking for a team member!\r\n\r\nWith us, you get the opportunity to\r\n\r\n- work with high level technology and innovative solutions\r\n- take responsibility of the quality in customer focused solutions with ongoing testing and test automation\r\n- test embedded software components and functionality\r\n\r\nDo these words raise your interest / are you familiar with: robot framework, protocol testing, Web service / REST, IPv6? How about routing, VPNs and firewalls on Linux platform? Also, Java and C would help you with this interesting work.\r\n\r\nAs we are at the edge of constantly developing business internationally, the working environment also offers multinational aspect to your work. Therefore English communication skills are important. Our projects ensure that you get interesting tasks now and in the future.\r\n\r\nWe work together, respect each other's contribution and share positive atmosphere. It would be great if you share same values!\r\n\r\nThe location of the job is in our Nordics main office at Jyväskylä.\r\n\r\nFor further details please contact Seppo Räihä, seppo.raiha@landisgyr.com, + 358 40 5311 287.\r\n\r\nWe wish you to leave application and CV latest on November 17th, 2017.\r\n\r\n\r\nLandis+Gyr is the leading global provider of integrated energy management solutions for the energy utility sector. We help our customers around the world to improve their energy efficiency and to manage energy better. Landis+Gyr operates worldwide and offers international, inspiring working environment. Our Jyväskylä site is a global technology center for smart metering solutions and the hub for Nordic operations. Read more at landisgyr.eu",
