				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you a devoted project professional who feels at home in technical engineering environments? Are you inspired by energy management business?  \r\n\r\nWe're looking for a Project Manager to build a smarter energy infrastructure in the Nordics. You work in smart metering projects and bring the latest technology available for our network distribution company clients, operating in an advanced energy market that is taking the next step in the digital transformation.\r\n\r\nWith us, you get the opportunity to \r\n\r\n- take a comprehensive responsibility on planning and executing inspiring customer projects in  2nd generation smart metering rollouts  \r\n- support our Sales team to success in bid process and customer negotiations \r\n- orchestrate a team of professionals comprising our own experts as well as partners and service suppliers\r\n\r\nWith us you get to exploit your experience from international customer projects. It's essential that you feel comfortable and confident in cooperating with various stakeholders. You're appreciated by customers and various stakeholders as a trusted partner who understands their expectations, and you have the talent to balance customers' needs and project control.\r\n\r\nIn our smart metering projects you can leverage your expertise in system integration, IT and telecommunications. As we are a globally operating company and our Project Manager position focuses on the Nordic market, you're able to utilize your fluent skills in Swedish and English. Close collaboration with the market will also require travelling. \r\n\r\nYou can choose to work either in our head office for Nordics in Jyväskylä or at our site office in Vantaa.\r\n\r\nWe invite you to join a journey with an energetic team of Landis+Gyr experts and the greatest customers. Every day is full of new opportunities.\r\n\r\nFor further details please contact Janne Leppäaho, janne.leppaaho@landisgyr.com, +358 40 504 5257.\r\n\r\nWe wish you to leave application and CV latest on November 17th, 2017.\r\n\r\n\r\nLandis+Gyr is the leading global provider of integrated energy management solutions for the energy utility sector. We help our customers around the world to improve their energy efficiency and to manage energy better. Landis+Gyr operates worldwide and offers international, inspiring working environment. Our Jyväskylä site is a global technology center for smart metering solutions and the hub for Nordic operations. Read more at landisgyr.eu",
