				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Site secretary/Interpreter for our Client in Klaundborg, Denmark. As a Site Secretary/ Interpreter you are responsible for administrative support for the day-to-day operations of the Project Management Department.\r\n\r\nTasks and Responsibilities: \r\n\r\n- Administrative tasks\r\n- Supporting project with administrative duties\r\n- Preparing time sheets\r\n- Translation work\r\n- Access control\r\n- Provide appropriate and proactive support to the Project Management Department and organization for project-related administrative activities \r\n- Cooperate with the subcontractors\r\n- Organize trainings (booking trainers, meeting rooms etc.) \r\n- Support the project personnel in administrative/ organizational and site related matters that arise on project \r\n- Secretarial duties\r\n- Organizing accommodations\r\n- Other assistance as assigned and needed\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n- Experience of construction site conditions\r\n- Natural user of common sense\r\n- Project management skills are appreciated\r\n- Well organized and active person\r\n- Proactive, able to think critically and independently\r\n- Strong communication and coordination skills\r\n- Good adjustment and planning capacity\r\n\r\nLanguages:\r\n\r\n- Fluent in English and Danish languages\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
