				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for concrete element factory workers to our customer. If you have previous experience in making pracast concrete element panels, put in an application for the position by filling the recruitment form on our website! The work starts immediately when potential candidates have been found!\r\n\r\nRequirements\r\n- Work permit or EU citizenship \r\n- Previous experience of working in a concrete factory\r\n- Own car is a plus\r\n\r\nWe offer\r\n- Permanent employment\r\n- Accomodation near the plant\r\n- Service in: Finnish, English, Russian, Estonian, Lithuanian and Polish\r\n- Competitive salary\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for an opportunity to work in Finland, contact Lavonia recruitment at jesse@lavonia.fi by sending your CV or fill the recruitment form at our website http://lavonia.fi/avoimet-tyopaikat/\r\n\r\nYou can also call Jevgenij Jeprintsev at +358406800998 or jevgenij@lavonia.fi",
