				"kuvausteksti" : "Viima Solutions is growing fast and they are looking for a Jr. Web Developer to grow with them. We are looking for a student or a recent graduate to kick-start their career as a future full-stack web developer. If you have at least some web development experience, relevant studies and, most of all, a high ambition to learn and become a true professional in a company that is offering you tons of support, responsibility, and a fun working environment, this might be the job for you!\r\n\r\nABOUT THE ROLE\r\n\r\nAcademic Work is looking for Jr. Web Developer for our client Viima Solutions Oy. Viima is a fast growing software company with both international and domestic customers, such as If Insurance, Telia, and United Nations. They are looking for a young talent to grow with them and develop into a full-stack superstar. Work is either part-time or fulltime depending on your situation.\r\n\r\nYou will be recruited to our client company. Academic Work will take care of the recruitment process, therefore candidates are kindly asked to direct all questions to Academic Work hel03@academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\n\r\nJOB DUTIES\r\n\r\nIn this position, you will become part of a talented, ambitious and fun-loving development team of four web development experts at Viima. You will build and develop Viima's main product, a SaaS tool for companies to engage their employees, customers, or other stakeholders in transparent and collaborative development of ideas. This position allows you to develop into a full-stack professional and it will be tailored to match your experience, expertise and interest. Your job will include, for example, improving the functionality and quality of the product, creating entirely new features from scratch, user interface design, testing, and might also include customer specific projects. With Viima you will work with technologies such as Python, Django, jQuery, Marionette.js and Backbone.js.\r\n\r\nViima offers extensive support for your development and a great amount of responsibility according to your skills and ambitions. Besides a great career opportunity, they offer a fun working environment. They are hard-working and ambitious but always make sure to have fun while doing their job.\r\n\r\nWE ARE LOOKING FOR\r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate has, or is studying for, a bachelor's or master's degree in IT, engineering or economics. You are highly motivated to develop into a full-stack professional and possess some previous experience in web development, for example through school or hobby projects. Technical skills naturally matter but your motivation, ability to think critically, drive to learn and to get things done with the highest quality possible, are more important. You also speak and write English fluently, Finnish is a plus.\r\n\r\nApply for this position if you have:\r\n\r\n-Relevant academic background\r\n-Some experience in web development\r\n-High motivation to become a stellar full-stack web developer\r\n-Ability to think critically\r\n-Great initiative and a responsible approach to work\r\n-Fluent written and spoken English skills and preferably Finnish language skills.\r\n\r\nViima believes that the best people are not necessarily the ones with the most experience but those with the desire to always learn more and get better at their job every day. So, send your CV the soonest, we would be happy to discuss this opportunity further with you!\r\n\r\n\r\nTo apply for the job you need to register on our website and then click on \"Apply here\". Remember to attach your CV into your application! We only process applications through our website but if you have questions about the position you can reach us via email in hel03@academicwork.fi. Please write the advert ID in the subject field and paste the advert link in the mail. We are continuously screening and contacting candidates so make sure to send your application as soon as possible. Please note that the advert can be removed prior to the last application dates on our external advertising pages. In the event the advert has been removed it is either due to the process being completed or because we have a sufficient number of qualified applications and are proceeding to the selection/interview phase in the process.\r\n\r\nWe are the Home of the Young Professionals. We are experts in recruitment and staffing university students, recently graduated and professionals in the beginning of their career. You can be employed by us as a consultant in one of our client companies or be recruited directly to our client via our recruitment co-operation. You can read more about us at www.academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\nINFORMATION ABOUT THE COMPANY\r\n\r\nViima Solutions offers a SaaS tool for companies to engage their employees, customers, or other stakeholders in transparent and collaborative development of ideas. Viima's goal is to help companies all around the world unleash the unrealized potential in their stakeholders by transforming the way they turn ideas into innovations quickly and easily. Their current happy customers, such as United Nations, If, Veikkaus and Telia are just a tip of the iceberg.",
