				"kuvausteksti" : "Finnish  Account Manager (Current / Existing Customers) \r\n\r\nNo Cold Calling! You will be required to sell a range of products to existing customers through outbound telephone calling. In doing so, you will provide the customers with a professional and courteous service, whilst establishing long-term customer relationships.\r\nYou will be responsible for generating sales from existing customer orders. You will be assessed by the revenue generated from selling activities, number of orders approved and the quality and accuracy of order entry.\r\n\r\nFunctions:\r\n\r\nGenerate revenue from a database of accounts with associated Sales Revenue and \r\nKey Performance targets\r\nCalling customers from existing mail orders received\r\nEntering orders on database and upselling live to customers\r\nVerifying the order and customer details on-line\r\nAny other duties/projects as directed by Senior Management\r\n\r\nSkills/Attributes/Requirements:\r\n\r\nHave previous experience within a sales environment, particularly direct sales and with a proven sales ability. Be adept at identifying and developing new sales opportunities Achieve and/or exceed sales targets using defined sales techniques\r\nHave the ability to work accurately & show good attention to detail while working under pressure\r\nGood telephone manner: professional, courteous, clear speech, good call management, assertive. Be a good team player\r\nFluent Finnish  and very good knowledge of English\r\nBe computer literate, with good keyboard skills; familiar with different on-line data-base packages.\r\n\r\n\r\nNormal Hours of Work: 39.5 hrs per work - 8 hour Day Shift, Monday  to Friday\r\nStarting Salaries from €24,000 basic per annum plus sales commission of  €100 - €500 per week (depending on targets reached)= €35,000 OTE uncapped commission depending on targets reached.\r\n\r\nAdditional Benefits\r\n\r\nPaid Holidays \r\nBonus\r\nRelocation package\r\nVouchers\r\nParking\r\nStaff Discount\r\nSports and Social Club\r\n\r\n\r\nApplication and CV to:   info@ofarrellonline.de",
