				"kuvausteksti" : "Trelleborg Group is a global polymer engineering company with world class products and customized solutions to seal, damp and protect in demanding environments.\r\nTrelleborg Group has turnover slightly over 3 billion euros with 15 000 employers and global presence.\r\n\r\n\r\nProject Engineer/Trelleborg Industrial Products Finland Oy, Sastamala\r\n\r\nWe are seeking Project Engineer to strengthen our R&D and customer support function. The position is in Sastamala at the main site of Trelleborg Electrical Protection Product Group.\r\n\r\nWe require strong customer focus and can do -mindset. An ideal candidate would have design/engineering knowledge from various industries, preferably from electro technical segment. Basic understanding of various physical phenomena and strong project management skills are essential in this role. Fluent English skills are necessary in this position. \r\n\r\nYou will be part of multinational team that is dedicated to create customer value through innovative solutions in the field of polymer engineering and manufacturing. Understanding the needs of the customer and developing innovative and smart solutions to customer's applications are key qualities in this role.\r\n\r\nReadiness to travel would be required and additional language skills with professional working proficiency are being considered as assets. \r\n\r\nPlease send your application and CV in English by 12.11.2017.\r\nMore information from Adecco's Jussi Ylönen, 046 8760313 or jussi.ylonen@adecco.fi",
