				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for an experienced security tester to work for our client at Hyvinkää.\r\n\r\nThe job is about minimizing cybersecurity related risks by finding and eliminating problems in client's software systems. The systems include embedded devices, IoT related server components and communication infrastructure.\r\n\r\nIn order to be successful, you need to\r\n-have a good grasp of cybersecurity fundamentals\r\n-understand typical security solutions used in embedded and IoT/cloud environments\r\n-have deep knowledge of typical communications protocols and their security properties\r\n-know the most common vulnerabilities in the domains of interest\r\n-be able to identify potential vulnerabilities with the highest risk\r\n-have good command of the methods and tools commonly used for penetration testing\r\n\r\nWe appreciate also\r\n-understanding hardware based security solutions and their weaknesses\r\n-being able to analyze cybersecurity designs and to do security assessments\r\n-being able to read and review C/C++ and JavaScript code in order to find vulnerabilities\r\n-having good command of Linux systems\r\n\r\nMost of our teams are working at our customer's premises, but we often meet and spend time together in team meetings and personnel events. We offer you a wide range of benefits and you can develop your competence with us - we are a certified ISTQB platinum partner and a leading trainer in the area of agile development, testing, automation and DevOps.\r\n\r\nCheck out our blog: we.knowit.fi\r\n\r\nMore information\r\nMore information about the job from Markku Degerholm, Senior Software Architect and Team Leader, markku.degerholm(a)knowit.fi, mob. +358 44 563 9408.\r\n\r\nJoin our team?\r\nSend your application and CV by clicking the application button. We process applications and keep interviews through the entire application period. The possibility to apply ends when we find the best candidates.\r\n\r\nKnowit is a consultancy firm which creates unique client value by offering interdisciplinary deliveries in three business fields: Experience, Insight and Solutions. Design and communication, management consultancy and technology competencies are combined in Knowit's services. We are more than 2,000 employees in Sweden, Norway, Finland, Denmark, Germany and Estonia. Knowit AB (publ) is listed on the OMX Nordic Exchange in Stockholm. Knowit - Creating Digital Opportunities. Further information: www.knowit.fi and www.knowitgroup.com.",
