				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you interested in a cleaning job in a hotel world? Are you the cleaning professional we are looking for?\r\n \r\n We are now searching for enthusiastic and professional CLEANERS for a nationally significant international hotel chain in the metropolitan area.\r\n \r\n Coor is one of the leading service providers in the Nordic region, specialising in demanding comprehensive commissions. Coor creates value by producing, leading, developing and enhancing services so that they optimally support customers' core-operations in the long run. We provide service solutions of the future. We call it Service with an IQ.\r\n \r\n As a cleaning professional you are responsible for the general cleanliness and sanitation of the facilities by following Coor's values and policies. You will work on the floors, e.g. making sure the hotel rooms stay tidy after each guest, and maintain the cleanliness of the public areas, including conference rooms. Once in a while your job also includes more thorough maintenance cleaning i.e. waxing and window cleaning. We provide both full and part-time work, as well as temporary work in variable work shifts. The work starts on agreement between December and February. \r\n \r\n Tehtävässä menestyäksesi sinulla tulee olla alan koulutus ja/tai kokemusta siivoustehtävistä, erityisesti kokemus hotellisiivouksesta on eduksesi. Sinulla on kyky omaksua ja vastaanottaa uusia työtehtäviä ja noudattaa annettuja ohjeistuksia. Työskentelet itsenäisesti, palvelualttiisti ja omaan hyvät tiimityöskentelytaidot. Asiakaspalvelutilanteissa tarvitset sujuvaa suomen kielen taitoa sekä riittävää englannin kielen taitoa.\r\n \r\n In order to succeed in the job you should have an education and/or experience in the field of cleaning; especially experience in hotel cleaning is seen as a benefit. You have the ability to adopt and receive new and varying tasks, and follow given instructions. You are able to work independently, helpful and able to serve the customers, and have great teamwork skills. In customer service situations you should be able to speak basic Finnish, otherwise fluent English is sufficient.\r\n\r\nWe offer you an opportunity to build new, and challenge the old, so come and join our Coor crew!\r\n \r\n Did we get your attention? Apply for the job through the following link by no later than November 30th. Please complete add a CV to your application as well. Recruitment will be carried out in co-operation with Personalhuset Staffing Group.\r\n \r\n Personalhuset Staffing Group is one of the fastest growing staffing company in the Nordic region. We have over 40 offices around the Nordics. On top of recruitment services we provide consulting- and modelling services and temporary staffing. Quality and inspiration are an essential part of our services, wherever you meet us. We want to be decisive for our customers success! www.personalhuset.fi",
