				"kuvausteksti" : "McDonald's is recruiting Crew to work in its restaurants in Cyprus. With the main objective being the satisfaction of our customers, the restaurant employees have varying responsibilities such as food preparation, food production, cleaning and the service of its customers according to McDonald's standards.\r\n\r\nHours:  8 hours a day, 6 days a week, shifts over a 24-hour period.\r\nSalary:  The first 6 months €870 and after 6 months €920, with 7.8% social insurance contributions.\r\nBenefits:  13th Salary\r\n22 working days annual leave paid by the Company\r\nBonus once a year based on performance review\r\nOne meal a day during the shift\r\nPaid accommodation for the first year and for the second year, will give rent allowance \r\nAn allowance for electricity and water will be paid by the Company and when that amount is exceeded, the employee will pay the difference\r\nThe employee has options for additional bonuses: Medical Insurance, Provident Fund\r\nJob locations: Ayia Napa, Protaras, Paphos, Limasson, Larnaka\r\nThe positions are for English spaking crew.",
