				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense is a trusted industrial software supplier. Our software development is multidisciplinary. We create completely new products, integrate already existing solutions and help our clients with their development projects, both in Finland and abroad.\r\n\r\nAs we continue to grow, we are looking for a motivated and experienced IT Product Manager to join our company either in Pori or Tampere.\r\n\r\nTasks and responsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Manages the daily tasks and clarifies the requirements during design, development, testing and release\r\n- Translates business process needs into IT requirements\r\n- Acts as a conduit between the business and development team\r\n- Attends SCRUM and field questions from the development team\r\n- Works with business, operations and finance stakeholders \r\n- Demonstrates leadership by establishing and articulating a clear vision of processes and how goals will be achieved\r\n- Identifies risks and challenges, opportunities and growth strategies\r\n- Manages product plan by following up changes in the market and needs of our customers\r\n- Uses detailed knowledge of application features and functions to assess scope and impact of business needs\r\n- Ensures the quality of the product\r\n- Reports to management\r\n\r\nRequirements\r\n\r\n- Relevant educational degree\r\n- Strong background in IT\r\n- Experience of working as a Product/Solution Manager or as a Project Manager in IT industry\r\n- Experience of life cycle management would be beneficial\r\n- Advanced technical skills with the ability to quickly adapt to new tools and processes \r\n- Familiar with an Agile development process\r\n- Familiar with requirements gathering, information architecture, visual design, functional and technical specifications\r\n- Good communication skills\r\n- Proactive attitude\r\n\r\nLanguage skills:\r\n \r\n\r\n- Fluent Finnish and English language skills\r\n\r\nPlease register as a jobseeker and apply for the position through our website.\r\n \r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
