				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for Sales Director who will join our Management team in Pori HQ Office. We offer the possibility to be a part of rapidly growing successful company in energy sector and to work with inspiring professionals both locally and internationally.\r\n \r\nMain tasks and responsibilities:\r\n \r\n-Support our Managing Director in sales projects to ensure that all business cases are taken care of with the highest level of professionalism\r\n-Craft national and international sales plans and develop sustainable strategy to reach targets, covering a wide geographical area\r\n- Achieve growth by successfully managing and evaluating the team of our Sales Area Managers \r\n-Build and promote strong, long-lasting Customer relationships by partnering and understanding Customers' needs\r\n- Follow-up on the processes and report to Managing Director \r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n \r\n- B.Sc. or M.Sc. Economics or Business Degree or equivalent \r\n- Professional certifications are beneficial\r\n- Phenomenal sales skills and extensive sales experience\r\n- Experience of complex energy constructions projects is beneficial\r\n- High adaptability in international business settings\r\n- Excellent leadership skills \r\n- Outstanding negotiation skills\r\n- Creativity, Approachability and a flexible mind\r\n\r\nLanguage skills:\r\n \r\n- Fluent in Finnish and English \r\n\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
