				"kuvausteksti" : "Main duties: Ensure reliable operation of the IT infrastructure and systems. Organization of  maintenance of IT infrastructure, performing routine and preventive maintenance, sustainability and accessibility of data in IT systems.\r\nDevelopment and design solutions for IT infrastructure.\r\nDevelop technical specifications and tender documentation for procurement of equipment and software. Ensure procurement procedures.\r\nInformation security of IT infrastructure and systems. User rights management in IT systems.\r\nTechnical and software user support, consultation of users regarding local network services and software.\r\nDevelopment of documentation in terms of IT infrastructure.\r\n\r\nMain skils: Windows 2003, 2008, 2012 confident system administrator (MCSA would be an advantage).\r\nBasic skills in '.nix platforms.\r\nExperience in building and administration of corporate networks based on Microsoft  products and related services (AD, DNS, DHCP, IIS, NAT, VPN, WSUS, Print Server, File Server, Certification Authority).\r\nUnderstanding of information security principles, domain group policies.\r\nExperience in Enterprise storage systems (HP 3PAR), active network (mostly Cisco) and server hardware at system administrator level, Virtualization platform Vmware ESX (VMware vSphere, MS Hyper-V would be an advantage). \r\nDatabase administration basic skills (mainly MS SQL server 2008, 2012) .\r\nCollaboration services (Microsoft Exchange 2010 server and newer).\r\nScripting (VBS, WHS, bat, etc.) for administration processes automation. \r\nVirtual Desktop solutions (MS Terminal Server). Citrix would be an advantage. \r\nRemote user support and server, network administration.\r\nWeb services administration. \r\nWriting Regulatory documentation, user instructions.\r\nBA degree in IT.\r\nRussian fluent, English upper-intermediate level, Finnish is a plus. CVs with salary expectations should be sent to ivan.evseev@rosatom.fi.",
