				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for a fully qualified manager (lastentarhanopettaja/sosionoomi ATK) with a possible starting date from November to December. \r\n\r\nExcellent Finnish skills (fluent) and strong/excellent English skills is a must. The job requires that the manager works in partnership with the admin manager and a curriculum coordinator, so the tasks/responsibilities are split. This position is full-time and permanent. The salary is reflective and competitive and will be according to experience and qualifications. Minimum experience in a senior or management position, must be 1 year. The salary is compliant with the G scale and will be adjusted accordingly.\r\n\r\nAll staff must have a current criminal record check made before employment can commence. Hygiene pass and minimum EA1 ensiapu kortti.  \r\n\r\nWe are an equal opportunity  employer and welcome all applications regardless. We are fully insured and have union membership.\r\n\r\nPlease contact michael.hutchinson@kiddifeet.eu via email with relevant documents required.",
