				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for Commercial Officer Painting for our client in Olkiluoto Nuclear Power Plant, Finland.  We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain Tasks and Responsibilities:\r\n\r\n- Summarizing of requests for material and service in line with the purchasing processes\r\n- Request for proce at different local and international suppliers\r\n- Production of approval document for purchase pf material\r\n- Communication and organization for the supply of materials\r\n- Placing of work orders after approval by management\r\n- Cooperation with storage keeper to update the stock of materials\r\n- Quality inspection of received material, documentation asg archiving of those documents\r\n- Issuance of chemical permit\r\n- Documentation and archiving of material and staff list\r\n- Handling and documentation for the supply PPE to the respective contractors\r\n- Participation in team meetings and presentation of key values of the works\r\n- Support of the Painting Manager for reporting of cost and effort inside the team towards the management\r\n- Reporting of weekly/ monthly effort values\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n- Minimum of 3 years of experience in office work on large projects\r\n- Good knowledge of MS Office programs\r\n- Self-organizing skills\r\n- Good communication skills inside the team\r\n- Positive attitude\r\n- Flexibility regarding working hours and breaks\r\n- Specific nuclear project experience in not necessary\r\n- Good report writing and communication skills\r\n- Team player, proactive\r\n- Strong interpersonal skills\r\n- Commercial awareness\r\n- Good planning and organizing skills\r\n\r\nLanguages:\r\n\r\n- Fluent in English (spoken and written)\r\n- Finnish or German considered as an advantage\r\n\r\nDrug test and concise security clearance will be done for the selected person in order to get the permanent access to OL3 site.\r\n\r\nPlease note that due to clients urgent need only applicants with a valid working permit / EU-citizenship can be considered.\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
