				"kuvausteksti" : "Quiksilver is the world's leading surf and snowboard company. We have an exciting position as an experienced part-time Sales Assistant (12-16 hours per week) to deliver excellent customer service to the customers.\r\n\r\nThis is the perfect opportunity for someone who works or wants to work in retail and who has a passion for our core sports, brands and lifestyle.\r\n \r\nThe Sales Assistant role is to, amongst other things, help achieve the store Sales Targets and KPIs ensuring the highest level of customer service with the ethos that the \"Customer is King\" and ensuring that the store merchandising guidelines are followed.\r\n \r\nThe ideal candidate must have proven customer service and communications skills and be target and results orientated. They must be fluent in Finnish and have good knowledge of the English language. Other languages are considered as a plus. The positions will be filled as soon as a suitable candidates are found.\r\n\r\nHakemuksen ja cv:n voi lähettää myös suomeksi.",
