				"kuvausteksti" : "American Express is a global service company, providing customers with exceptional access to products and experiences that enrich lives and build business success.\r\n \r\nEach day, we make it easier, safer and more rewarding for consumers and businesses to purchase the things they need and for merchants to sell their goods and services, enabling them to do and achieve more.\r\n \r\nWe're committed to becoming the world's most respected service brand and daily deliver extraordinary service to our customers, constantly reinventing our ways of working to ensure we offer rich rewards that redefine expectations for our clients and ourselves.\r\n\r\nWill be responsible for processing all maintenance requests received from internal or external customers for Corporate Card, Consumer Card and Business Travel Account products. The account maintenance will involve responding to queries, performing credit balance refunds and account maintenance such as; address changes, card cancellations, set up direct debits, add Program administrators e.g. \r\n \r\nThe successful candidate will be assuring the highest standard of case quality, customer service and relationship care as it is crucial in every case and interaction, whether it is with an internal or external customer.\r\n\r\nOffer of employment with American Express is conditioned upon the successful completion of a background verification check, subject to applicable laws and regulations.\r\n\r\n \r\nQualifications\r\n\r\n\r\nRequired Experience:\r\nPrevious administrative and customer focused experience is an advantage.\r\n \r\nRequired Skills:\r\nOutstanding customer care, excellent organizational and communicational skills with an eye for detail. Must be numerate, literate and have the ability to learn quickly and to analyse documentation against the guidelines.\r\n \r\nRequired language:\r\nNordic language - Finnish, Danish, Norwegian and/or Swedish speaker\r\n\r\nWe place great importance on doing what is right, what is best and what is innovative. And we continue seeking people to champion these values and beliefs as we grow. The world's a big place, filled with big ideas and amazing people. And we want the best of them here at American Express. We're interested in where you came from, but we're even more excited about where you will go with American Express.",
