				"kuvausteksti" : "Because of the construction work of the Hanhikivi-1 Nuclear Power Plant we are strengthening our resources in Finland. \r\nNow we are looking for a Secretary to work at our Pyhäjoki site.\r\n\r\nAs our Secretary your main duties will be:\r\n- Office documentation; receiving, recording and registering documents\r\n- Control execution of documents and tasks by management\r\n- Prepare meetings, prepare and store minutes of the meetings\r\n- Communication with third party organizations and internal communication\r\n- Welcome visitors\r\n- Other tasks inside office secretary job description\r\n\r\nSuitable candidate shall have applicable education and at least 1 years of work experience in similar positions. Language skills required are fluent English, with Finnish and Russian continued as advantage. You will have excellent verbal and written communication and reporting skills, excellent problem solving skills, stress management skills and ability to work in multitask environment.\r\n\r\nInterest?\r\n\r\nPlease let us have your CV, application and request for salary to hr@titan2.fi\r\nPlease write in the subject line in your application email: Secretary in Pyhäjoki.",
