				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for Accounting support for our client in Olkiluoto. The job starts as soon as the right candidate has been found and lasts for 12 months. Accounting support\r\n\r\n  CANDIDATE PROFILE\r\n\r\nGeneral and technical background expected:\r\n\r\n- Bachelorof Business Administration\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n\r\n- Hardworking\r\n- flexible Team player who can work independently also\r\n\r\nTechnical:\r\n\r\n- Excel\r\n- SAP knowledge is a plus\r\n\r\nLanguage skills:\r\n\r\n- Fluent English\r\n- Finnish or French is a plus\r\n\r\nREPORTS TO:\r\n\r\nOperationally to Chief Accountant and Hierarchically to OL3 Cost Control Manager\r\n\r\nCONFIDENTIALITY:\r\n\r\nAll matters related to the job are to be treated with the highest confidentiality.\r\n\r\nFunction:\r\n\r\nSupport for Accounts Payable (AP) process\r\n\r\no Invoice reception and review\r\n\r\no Invoice workflow and validations handling\r\n\r\no AP process required SAP steps\r\n\r\nSupport for Accounts Receivable (AR) process\r\n\r\nSupport for Accounting reporting\r\n\r\nSupport for Customer accounts management\r\n\r\nPersonal skills:\r\n\r\n- Autonomous\r\n- Rigorous\r\n- Proactive\r\n- Reliable\r\n- Good Communication skills\r\n- Fluent in English\r\n- Finnish or French is a plus\r\n\r\nPlease apply for this position: www.rtkhenkilostopalvelu.fi Don't forget to attach your updated CV in English and salary request to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Sanni Tapani, sanni.tapani@rtkpalvelu.fi\r\n\r\nRTK-Henkilöstöpalvelu Oy's core business is long-term placement of rental personnel and recruitment. We operate as a reliable and professional partner for human resource services. The purpose of our operation is to bring employees and employers together in an easy and flexible way. Our aim is to find suitable personnel for our customers in long-term contracts.",
