				"kuvausteksti" : "ABB is a pioneering technology leader in electrification products, robotics and motion, industrial automation and power grids, serving customers in utilities, industry and transport & infrastructure globally. Continuing more than a 125-year history of innovation, ABB today is writing the future of industrial digitalization and driving the Energy and Fourth Industrial Revolutions. ABB operates in more than 100 countries with about 136,000 employees and of them around 5,100 in Finland. www.abb.com\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a Global Sales Support Specialist at ABB Oy, Protection and Connection unit in Vaasa. You will be supporting our local sales organizations and product marketing teams with technical and commercial tasks. In this position, you will serve as the key technical resource in the assigned area.\r\n\r\nYour responsibilities\r\n- Supporting local sales organizations and product marketing teams in the assigned set of countries \r\n- Providing support for technical and commercial tasks \r\n- Serving as the key technical resource in the assigned area\r\n\r\nWe offer\r\n- A challenging position in an international working environment\r\n- The opportunity for personal development \r\n- The opportunity to further your career in the sales and marketing department of a global company\r\n\r\nRequirements\r\n- B.Sc. or M.Sc. in electrical engineering, or a solid technical background in electrotechnics\r\n- A strong service attitude\r\n- Good written and spoken communication skills in English and Finnish.\r\n\r\nIdeally, you have\r\n- Previous experience as a Sales Engineer or Sales Support Specialist",
