				"kuvausteksti" : "Do you have previous experience in working with integrations and/or back-end development? Do you want to take marketing automation to the next level and work with large global accounts and brands? If your answer is yes, keep on reading! We are now looking for a Back-End Developer to work with marketing automation integrations in Finland's leading automation expert, ID BBN.\r\n\r\nKUVAUS\r\n\r\nAcademic Work is looking for a Back-End Developer for our client company ID BBN to work in Helsinki or in Turku.\r\n\r\nYou will be recruited to our client company. Academic Work will take care of the recruitment process, therefore candidates are kindly asked to direct all questions to Academic Work esp01@academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\nTYÖTEHTÄVÄT\r\n\r\nIn this position, you will participate in planning and executing various integrations between custom made tools and marketing automation systems. You will have the possibility to utilize already existing integration modules or create new, custom made integrations.\r\n\r\nAccording to your skills and desires, you can have a consultative role working directly with clients, participate in the server architecture and/or conduct data-analysis based on the data generated from the system. In addition, you will have the possibility to take part in specifying, wireframing and building custom web applications for their clients. The technologies used in the team are e.g. Python, PHP, Node.js, REST interfaces and NoSQL.\r\n\r\nThis position suits you who wants to have great development possibilities, work with large international companies and be a part of Europe's leading marketing technology integrator!\r\n\r\nETSIMÄMME HENKILÖ ON\r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate has a suitable educational background and previous experience in working with integrations and/or with back-end development. You have eagerness to continuously improve your skill set and you are interested in taking marketing automation to the next level. You enjoy working in a team and if you wish to work directly with clients, great interaction skills are a must. You speak and write fluently in English.\r\n\r\nApply for this position if you have:\r\n\r\n- A suitable educational background\r\n- A minimum of one year work experience with integrations or a couple of years in back-end development\r\n- Fluent English language skills\r\n\r\nIt is also seen as an advantage if you have previous experience in working with REST interfaces, AWS Serverless Platform or you have knowledge of technologies such as Python and/or PHP.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo apply for the job you need to register on our website and then click on \"Apply here\". Remember to attach your CV into your application! We only process applications through our website but if you have questions about the position you can reach us via email in esp01@academicwork.fi. Please write the advert ID in the subject field and paste the advert link in the mail. We are continuously screening and contacting candidates so make sure to send your application as soon as possible. Please note that the advert can be removed prior to the last application dates on our external advertising pages. In the event the advert has been removed it is either due to the process being completed or because we have a sufficient number of qualified applications and are proceeding to the selection/interview phase in the process.\r\n\r\nWe are the Home of the Young Professionals. We are experts in recruitment and staffing university students, recently graduated and professionals in the beginning of their career. You can be employed by us as a consultant in one of our client companies or be recruited directly to our client via our recruitment co-operation. You can read more about us at www.academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\nINFOA ASIAKKAASTA\r\n\r\nID BBN is an international, award-winning digital marketing agency. It is one of Europe's leading marketing technology agency and Finland's leading automation expert. Its offices are located in Helsinki and Turku where a team of 30 people combine strategic thinking, creativity and technological know-how to create measurable business results.",
