				"kuvausteksti" : "Compliance & Quality Specialist for BlueFors \r\n\r\nBlueFors specializes in the manufacturing of state-of-the-art ultra-low temperature cooling systems with a strong focus on the field of quantum technology. We are looking for persons who want to be part of a dynamic team and use their expertise to help deliver BlueFors systems to cutting-edge research fields, such as quantum computing and nanotechnology. Our head office is in Pitäjänmäki, Helsinki. Since 2014, the number of our employees has increased from 20 to 80 and the markets for our high-tech products are constantly growing. \r\n\r\nWe are looking for a person with a mind-set for high-quality and professionalism and a capability to work in an international growth company. You will get the opportunity to develop yourself with challenging and varying tasks and grow with the company in a high-tech environment. We offer competitive benefits and flexible working hours. \r\n\r\nThe person will ensure that all BlueFors production practices are in compliance with relevant regulations and standards, in cooperation with our production departments. \r\n\r\nMain responsibilities are:\r\nAuditing and documenting follow-up of regulations and standards (CE, CSA, UL, ISO, Rohs)\r\nResolving potential compliance issues \r\nInteracting with our departments to ensure internal communication flow regarding compliance and quality\r\nKeeping up to date with regulatory changes and taking relevant action\r\nMaintaining internal quality instructions and customer user manuals\r\nAssisting with customer technical support, such as compiling an FAQ database\r\n\r\nQualities and skills:\r\nMSc degree in electrical or mechanical engineering or equivalent\r\nSeveral years of experience in compliance and quality control in a demanding manufacturing industry, including knowledge of the above mentioned standards\r\nSystematic, analytical and detail oriented\r\nExcellent command of English language with ability to write technical documents\r\n\r\n\r\nThe position will be filled once a suitable candidate is found. \r\nwww.bluefors.com",
