				"kuvausteksti" : "Do you want to work in SaaS development projects for airline and railway businesses? Do you have ambition to grow to a Lead Developer position in the future? QOCO Systems offers a lot of responsibility and possibilities to grow as a professional. If you got interested, please continue reading and send us your application as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nJOB DESCRIPTION\r\n\r\nAcademic Work is looking for a Full-Stack Developer for our client QOCO Systems.\r\n\r\nYou will be recruited to our client company. Academic Work will take care of the recruitment process, therefore candidates are kindly asked to direct all questions to Academic Work, esp02@academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nJOB DUTIES\r\n\r\nIn this position, you will participate in SaaS development projects as well as development projects for client companies. Depending on the project, there will be 2-3 full-stack developers working with you. The projects are often executed in close collaboration with aviation and railway clients. In your first project, you will work on Cabinworks, which is a solution for aircraft cabin defect reporting. Cabinworks software utilizes speech recognition and machine learning.  Read more about Cabinworks here: https://www.qoco.aero/#solutions\r\n\r\nYou have the possibility to influence the technologies you are going to use based on your experience and preferences. You will occasionally visit your clients that are located in the capital area. This position suits you who wants to develop software for various industries and are eager to grow to a Lead Developer position. \r\n\r\n\r\nREQUIREMENTS\r\n\r\n\r\nThanks to your educational background in computer sciences, you are able to contribute in software development for various industries. Our ideal candidate has proved his/her software development skills through a summer job or own projects. You have experience in at least one back-end technology (e.g. Java/Node.js) and one front-end technology (e.g. React/AngularJS). The most important thing is that you have motivation to learn more and develop yourself. You are eager to grow to a Lead Developer position within a year. \r\n\r\nOur ideal candidate has: \r\n\r\n- Relevant educational background\r\n- Previous software development experience e.g. through work or own projects\r\n- Experience in at least one back-end technology (e.g. Java/Node.js) and one front-end  technology (e.g. React/AngularJS) \r\n- Ambition to grow to a Lead Developer position\r\n- Fluent in both spoken and written English \r\n\r\nIt is seen as an advantage if you know database technologies (SQL/NoSQL) or mobile frameworks such as React Native. \r\n\r\n\r\nPublished: October 25, 2017\r\n\r\n\r\nTo apply for the job you need to register on our website and then click on \"Apply here\". https://www.academicwork.fi/avoimet-tyopaikat/full-stack-developer-to-espoo/14995927\r\n\r\n Remember to attach your CV into your application! We only process applications through our website but if you have questions about the position you can reach us via email in esp02@academicwork.fi. Please write the advert ID in the subject field and paste the advert link in the mail. \r\nWe are continuously screening and contacting candidates so make sure to send your application as soon as possible.  Please note that the advert can be removed prior to the last application dates on our external advertising pages. In the event the advert has been removed it is either due to the process being completed or because we have a sufficient number of qualified applications and are proceeding to the selection/interview phase in the process.\r\n\r\nWe are the Home of the Young Professionals. We are experts in recruitment and staffing university students, recently graduated and professionals in the beginning of their career. You can be employed by us as a consultant in one of our client companies or be recruited directly to our client via our recruitment co-operation. You can read more about us at www.academicwork.fi.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCLIENT INFORMATION\r\n\r\nSince its inception professionals at QOCO, https://www.qoco.aero/, have worked in close collaboration with MRO customers in aviation and railway business. Our customers include companies such as Finnair and VR. We thrive to build new solutions with agile methodologies and the most suitable technology. We are also very active in Finland's vibrant start-up scene and constantly scouting for innovative ideas. QOCO is here to bring change to the status quo, as we are the new kid on the block.",
