				"kuvausteksti" : "Team Electric Oy Ab is an electrical company founded in 2002 with a turnover of more than € 20 M and great success in the marine business. We work all over the world, mostly in Bahamas, Spain, Singapore, Japan, Norway, Germany and France. Our electrical work in Finland is mainly in Turku and Rauma.\r\n\r\nCurrently we are looking for the following position:\r\n\r\nAUTOCAD DESIGNER\r\n\r\nYou will work in cooperation with our Head Designer with electrical designs in the marine industry. \r\n\r\nTo succeed you need to have a few years' experience of using the AutoCAD program, a genuine \"can-do\" attitude and be curious to learn different task. An electrical background is an advantage. We also need you to have a structured work style and patience with details. The position can grow according to your skills.\r\n\r\nThe location of work is at our office in Inkoo and the work language is English.\r\n\r\nWe offer you a position in a growing company, our work place is very international and you will have regular contact with persons with different nationalities. Salary will be paid according to your skills.\r\n\r\nPlease note that Team Electric is a nonsmoking company.\r\n\r\nIf the above position has your interest please send your application and CV with your salary request in English as soon as possible to applications@team-electric.com. The position will be filled as soon as we have found the right person for the job.\r\n\r\n\r\nFor more information about Team Electric Oy Ab visit www.team-electric.com\r\n\r\nWe are looking forward to receiving your application soonest possible.",
