				"etatyo" : false,
				"kuvausteksti" : "One of our shareholders in our company is selling her company shares and for that reason her job position will become a vacancy. After you buy her shares you would become an Entrepreneur partner in our company.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an entrepreneur partner to take care of the web developer tasks that our actual partner performs. As an entrepreneur partner you will own shares in our company and at the same time you will be working in the company as a web developer.\r\n\r\nThe position is permanent and full time meaning that you would work (37,5 hours per week) and the position is based in Kirkkonummi, Finland. If you come from outside of the capital area we can arrange for you a reasonable-priced apartment for renting.\r\n\r\nThe company's share details like price, percentage, etc that our partner as shareholder is selling will be discussed after you have sent your curriculum vitae and been selected for the available position that our actual partner will leave open.\r\n\r\nApplication preferably before December 15th, 2017\r\n\r\nImmediate.- The position will be filled as soon as we find the suitable professional for the mentioned position.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a responsible, kind and internationally minded entrepreneur partner with good professional and language skills to take care of programming tasks that our actual partner performs.\r\n\r\nPROFESSIONAL PROFILE REQUIRED:\r\n\r\n- A university degree in; Information Technology/Informatics Engineering/ Computer Science/Software Engineering.\r\n- Web development experience/solid knowledge: XHTML, PHP, Frameworks: ZebKit, Fabric.JS\r\n- Definitely solid knowledge of javascript, Node.js, Python, HTML5, MVC PHP, SEO.\r\n- Creative programming skills and in-depth knowledge of modern HTML & CSS.\r\n- Experience in customizing CMS(Drupal, Joomla, Wordpress) and its plugins and modules.\r\n- A solid understanding of how web applications work including security, session management, and development practices.\r\n- Adequate knowledge of database systems (PostgreSQL, MySQL)\r\n- Self-initiative attitude.\r\n- Ability to learn new technologies so that you would grow in your professional career. Together, we will bring out the best in ourselves and our Company.\r\n\r\nOTHER REQUIREMENTS:\r\n\r\n- A minimum of 1-3 years of relevant working experience.\r\n- A high level of patience and confidence.\r\n- Due to English & Spanish target market spoken and written English & Spanish is required. Finnish is a plus.\r\n- Well versed about the web site development with flair for creativity.\r\n- A vision for the future and ability to see life beyond money.\r\n- High level of commitment on deliverables and respect for the ethics.\r\n- Great communication skills, positive attitude, and team player.\r\n- Proven ability to manage and complete tasks according to assigned timelines\r\n- Highly dependable, trustworthy and really values hard and honest work\r\n\r\nApplication: PLEASE APPLY ONLY IF YOU MEET ALL THE EDUCATIONAL AND PROFESSIONAL REQUIREMENTS AS WELL AS LANGUAGE REQUIREMENTS. WE WILL CONSIDER ONLY THOSE APPLICATIONS. Apply for the job by sending a cover letter and CV in English to tsiekkin@gmail.com entitled \"Web Developer Entrepreneur Partner\" as soon as possible. The position will be filled when the right candidate is found.",
