				"kuvausteksti" : "DIGITAL MARKETING EXPERT\r\n\r\nTETRIX, a market leader in portable display systems, is hiring a person with more than 3 years working experience in digital marketing. You have proven results of the ability to increase sales and you are up-to-date with the latest trends and best practices. \r\n\r\nWhat we are looking for:\r\nIf you live and breathe digital marketing - you are the person whom we are looking for!  A person who has an excellent skill in analysing visitor data and funneling prospects to our web shop. Good knowledge of payed for, multilevel advertising on the web. \r\n\r\nYou should have a strong grasp of current marketing and sales tools and strategies and be able to lead integrated marketing campaigns from concept to execution. We are not looking for an ordinary wizard, we are looking for a person who can move our sales to a completely new level! The target is a 25% increase of turnover in 2018. Fluency in Finnish is a must, as well as a good knowledge of Swedish. \r\n\r\nWhat we offer:\r\nA great friendly, open and supportive working environment with responsibility instead of time-wasting meetings and hierarchy structures. Own budgets to manage. Tools needed to succeed and in-house functions to support the strategy chosen: 3D, product videos, photo studio, graphical design support, copywriting. We will help you with accommodation should you need to move.\r\n\r\nIn our company hard work never goes unnoticed! We offer a competitive salary and a possibility to join the company and personal bonus program after the trial period. Good international working climate and possibility to structure work freely. Positive approach to innovative thinking and new ideas ...and lazy cuddles from the barkoholic office dog.\r\n\r\nJob description:\r\n- Brainstorm new and creative growth strategies\r\n- Analyse and make targets for our online sales and online visibility\r\n- Perform digital marketing campaigns in all its forms and channels\r\n- Follow digital marketing trends and do competitor mapping\r\n- Do budgeting Present budgets and spendings in coherence with goals set\r\n- Gather info, work with sales  and coordinate the sales team with approaching campaigns\r\n- Make improving suggestions on optimizing TETRIX website and social media channels for SEO as well as usab\r\n- Sales and administration tasks tasks with a passion for customer care\r\n- Communicate with the Head of the company about the marketing goals and results\r\n- Learn various tasks to support the whole team when needed\r\n\r\nWho is your future employer?\r\nTETRIX Ltd is specialized in portable marketing. Display systems, exhibition stands, backdrops. flags, and large format prints. You can see our products in shops, on TV shows, on exhibitions and so on.The past 2-3 years we have put down a lot of resources on developing new product lines and production of systems - and 2018 will be our best year ever!. We are a market leader in portable displays and have been in business since 2006. We are the most innovative company in our branch!.\r\nwww.tetrix.fi   https://www.facebook.com/tetrix.fi/   https://www.instagram.com/tetrixgram/   \r\n\r\nSend a short, punchy application and a CV before November 10:th to mats.sandvik@tetrix.fi\r\nPlease respect that we are busy and cold calling only to make a mind print is not necessary.\r\nPlace of business: Ab TETRIX Oy  Jakobsgatan 7,  68600 JAKOBSTAD",
