				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them.\r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Quality Manager for our client in Pyhäjoki, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities:\r\n\r\n-Work plans and Instruction Control\r\n-QA Supervision, control and lead while project ongoing\r\n-As-built Documentation Production Management\r\n-Ensure accurate Quality activities\r\n-Quality Manager is responsible of ensuring quality control production flow.\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n-Extensive experience of Quality Control in demanding Construction projects\r\n-Engineer degree or equivalent\r\n-Knowledge of Quality Management\r\n-Good communication skills\r\n-Problem-solving skills\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills:\r\n\r\n-Fluent Finnish and English\r\n-Russian beneficial\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as suitable applicant is found.",
