				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them. \r\n\r\nWe are currently looking for a Quality Engineer for our client in Pyhäjoki, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities:\r\n\r\n-Dams and embankments, steel poles and structures\r\n-Stone and steel construction work planning\r\n-Stone and steel structure As-built Documentation\r\n- Supervision during construction\r\n- Quality assurance\r\n \r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n-Experience of demanding stone and steel structures and Documentation in this field\r\n-Experience as Quality Engineer\r\n-Engineering degree or equivalent\r\n- Knowledge of terminology of the relevant field\r\n\r\nLanguage Skills:\r\n\r\n-Fluent in Finnish and English\r\n-Russian beneficial\r\n\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
