				"kuvausteksti" : "Hydraulics Design Engineer\r\n \r\nWe are looking for a hydraulics design engineer to develop Normet machine hydraulics. We expect you to be capable of designing mobile machinery hydraulic architectures in collaboration with engineers, production and purchasing.\r\n\r\nAs a person, we expect you to have a right attitude to develop machine hydraulics for harsh environments. You have either B. Eng. or M. Sc. (Tech.) education in relevant field. You are capable both individual and team work. You have previous working experience in mobile machinery hydraulics & mechanics or you are open to learn the necessary talents.\r\n\r\nYou are capable of working both with Finnish and English languages. You will be located primarily in Normet Oy factory in Iisalmi, Finland. Remote working practices can be discussed.\r\n\r\nSend your application and CV with salary request by 12.11.2017 to rekry@normet.com.  For further information, please contact Timo Oikarinen, Chief Design Engineer, +358 17 83 241",
