				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for our client, KONE KSS, a Tendering Specialist for long-term contract. The position is to be filled as soon as possible.\r\n\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\nB.Sc. in engineering or commercial\r\nGood spoken and written English\r\nCustomer Service orientation and service attitude\r\n\"Can do\" attitude (challenges solutions if needed)\r\nQuick decision making skills\r\nCapable of taking certain level risk\r\nUnderstand big picture without going very deep to details\r\nProactive on clarifications and finding solutions\r\nExcellent email handling skills (reply in 4 hours)\r\nCapable of handling some level of routine\r\n\r\n\r\nYour main responsibilities will be:\r\nSupport FLs globally by providing tendering solutions and specifications on elevator, escalator and modernization solutions\r\nbe the main SL contact towards FLs with technical questions and SL costing in tendering phase\r\nCoordinate SL specification creation\r\nManage tender drawings and related documents requests\r\nMake the material specifications for KONE and local material\r\nCheck and update the specifications based on variations\r\nEvaluate and assures the consistency & accuracy of tender quotations for SL Tendering Mgr. \r\nPrepare reliable quotations for volume product non-standard platforms project/option and variation orders (VO), feedback (FB), warranty claims, etc.\r\nUpdate delivery final price in ordering phase\r\n\r\n\r\nWe offer you a great possibility to use your full potential and work with highly professional collagues at fast moving international environment. If you are interested in this position, please send your application www.adecco.fi with CV and salary expectations by 10.11.2017. For more information please contact Senior HR Consultant Anita Fokin at Adecco Finland Oy: anita.fokin@adecco.fi.",
