				"kuvausteksti" : "DomaCare, developed by Invian Oy, is the leading ERP system in the social and health care sector in Finland. DomaCare ERP has thousands of satisfied daily users all over the country in small to large health companies.\r\n\r\nWe are now looking for an ambitious\r\n\r\nFRONT-END DEVELOPER\r\n\r\nto our growing team in Espoo or Oulu.\r\n\r\nAs a part of our front-end team you will develop user interfaces for DomaCare ERP using UI/UX plans made by our designer. Your tasks and responsibilities depend on your experience and will grow with you. To succeed you have to be able to work independently and have good communication and team player skills. You will also need English every day in our multilingual front-end team.\r\n\r\nWe appreciate if you have proven work experience on front-end development and have some kind of portfolio or earlier work projects to show.\r\n\r\nKnowledge required:\r\n\r\n - React\r\n - Redux\r\n - Webpack\r\n - SASS/CSS\r\n - REST\r\n - ES6\r\n - Responsive design\r\n - Git\r\n\r\nOther skills we also appreciate:\r\n\r\n - UI/UX design\r\n - SQL\r\n - Java\r\n\r\nWe offer:\r\n\r\n - Casual working environment\r\n - Organization with flat hierarchy\r\n - Possibility to grow with the company\r\n - Flexible working hours and possibility to do remote work\r\n - Ability to choose your own tools\r\n - Competitive salary and bonus system\r\n\r\nPlease send your application and resume in English or Finnish via email in careers@invian.fi. We'll fill the spot right away when we find the right person!\r\n\r\nFor more information about the position please contact our CTO Arttu Tanner by phone 040 8275446 or email arttu.tanner@invian.fi from Monday to Friday after 1 pm.",
