				"kuvausteksti" : "In keeping with our brand promise \"Engineering with a difference\", Etteplan takes a different attitude to embedded system and IoT solutions - something our customers confirm time and time again. We are proud of our expertise and our ability to impact our customers' success. \r\n\r\nYour expertise matters to us - come join our success story!\r\n\r\n\r\nSW testing is moving more and more towards automation. This has already happened in the traditional SW development and now test automation is growing rapidly in embedded SW development. Now we are looking for SW TEST AUTOMATION ENGINEERS to develop test automation systems and do automated tests. You will be located in one of our Etteplan offices in the capital area (Helsinki, Espoo, Vantaa, Hyvinkää). \r\n \r\n\r\nTo succeed in this role you should have\r\n- Degree in SW development or telecommunications or similar knowledge\r\n- Experience in embedded SW test design and testing\r\n- Experience in SW test automation system development and integration (e.g. Robot Framework, Selenium)\r\n- Experience in continuous integration tools (e.g. Jenkins)\r\n- Experience in Python or other scripting language\r\n- Experience in Agile project work\r\n- Innovative, enthusiastic, interactive and customer orientated \"can-do\" attitude\r\n- Very good communication skills both in English and in Finnish\r\n- Willingness to work in a customer interface and have marketing attitude\r\n\r\n\r\nKnowledge in Python or other scripting language and C/C++/C# experience is seen as an advantage. We also value experience in embedded SW design, experience in electronics as well as cloud and SW or system security knowledge. ISTQB certificate is also an asset.\r\n \r\n\r\nWe offer you an interesting and international working atmosphere among highly experienced professionals, varying tasks with high-end tools and possibility to develop your professional skills and competences.\r\n\r\n\r\nEtteplan is Finland's biggest employer in industrial engineering, technical product information, embedded systems and IoT solutions. We offer a vantage point to international industry, serving top players in their specific fields of expertise. With Etteplan you will gain a deeper insight into their products.\r\n\r\nWe are a genuine engineering house: our Group employs around 2,800 experts mainly in Finland, Sweden, the Netherlands, Germany, Poland and China - most of them engineers. Our success is based on our competence and our knowledgeable staff, both of which we take good care of. \r\n\r\nEtteplan offers interesting and challenging tasks in a growing working community in 30 locations around Finland. The work involved in customers' varied and demanding projects means constant learning and development.",
