				"kuvausteksti" : "Commis de Cuisine for Hotel Hilton Berlin\r\n\r\nHaving successfully passed your vocational training you are now planning your next steps of your career in a working environment with a wide range of tasks. You love to work with high quality regional products and you don't get stressed even in busy working conditions. \r\nOur restaurant \"Mark Brandenburg\" has a kitchen with various positions (saucier, entremetier, gardemanger) for which we are looking for highly motivated personnel. For this vacancy we offer trainings in all positions of our kitchen.  \r\n\r\nIf this short description arouses your interest and you want to be part of one of the leading hotel groups on the globe then don't hesitate to send us your complete application documents for the position as a chef.\r\nYour profile\r\n- Successfully completed vocational training as chef\r\n- High motivation and reliability\r\n- Flexibility and team spirit\r\n- Experience on one of the above mentioned positions \r\n- German language skills\r\n- Health certificate/ red card\r\nWhat we offer\r\n- Work clothes \r\n- Holiday pay and annual special payment (from the 2nd year on)\r\n- Staff canteen\r\n- Additional trainings\r\n- Good career opportunities\r\n- Benefits for accommodation in our global hotel group\r\n- We will assist applicants from abroad searching a flat\r\n- Salary: According to tariff, but it depends on the qualification\r\nWhat else to know\r\nEvery company has its own standards for selecting new staff members. Do not be discouraged if you do not meet every single requirement. What really counts is your personality and we are happy to assist you acquiring new skills.\r\n\r\nThis employment complies with the legislation of Germany.",
