				"kuvausteksti" : "Waiter / Waitress for banquet in the Marriott Hotel Berlin\r\n\r\nOur hotel is situated at Potsdamer Platz near the Brandenburg Gate in the heart of the German Capital. Its modern design with a touch of classical elegance fulfils the highest standards. Most of the cultural and historic sights are within walking distance as well as exclusive shopping malls and department stores. \r\nOur house counts 379 elegantly furnished rooms, suites and two executive floors, the ideal facility for business trips. In our two exclusive Club-levels the hotel offers a perfect environment for a successful stay in Berlin. We also provide a multifunctional banquet-hall and six conference rooms for up to 650 people. The restaurant, the bar and the spa-facilities are an example of the high standard of hospitality the Marriot Hotels are known for.\r\nWe are looking for a waiter/waitress in our banquet and catering area\r\nYour profile:\r\n- Passion for creating unforgettable moments and events \r\n- Stress resistant\r\n- Structured working method\r\n- Well-groomed appearance\r\n- Strong team spirit\r\n- Good command of English\r\n- Applicants from abroad need good German language skills\r\nWhat we offer:\r\n- Motivated team in a state-of-the-art working environment\r\n- Interesting and wide range of tasks\r\n- Staff events\r\n- Health-care services\r\n- We provide professional clothing and laundry service\r\n- Working with premium-quality products\r\n- Family & Friends benefits in all our hotels worldwide\r\n- Holiday regulations according to tariff\r\n- Fair payment according to tariff, minimum 8,90 € per hours a week, but it depends on the qualification\r\n\r\nAre you interested in enhancing our banquet team and in making career in one of the leading hotel groups worldwide?\r\n\r\nThis employment complies with the legislation of Germany.",
