				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for a\r\n\r\nResearcher\r\n\r\nThe position is permanent and located in Kilpilahti (Porvoo, Finland).\r\n\r\nAs a researcher you will be part of our laboratory equipment team and you will support several laboratories.  You will take part on laboratory practice and method development, equipment investment and problem solving.\r\n\r\nWe require at least a master's degree in chemistry. To be successful in this position you will need good method development skills and knowledge laboratory instruments and technics. \r\n\r\nGood co-operation and communication skills are appreciated as well as desire for professional development. Fluent English, both written and oral, is also required.\r\n\r\nFor further information of the position, please contact Jouni Meriläinen, Team Leader,\r\ntel. +358 50 4583024.\r\n\r\nFurther information and more detailed instructions for applying can be found from our website www.neste.com/joinus. The application period ends 15th November, 2017.",
