				"kuvausteksti" : "Haetaan monitaitoista ammattilaista rakennustyöntekijän tehtäviin. Pääasialliset työtehtävät lattiankaatotyöt ja odotamme myös osaamista laatoituksesta ja muurauksesta.\r\n\r\nHakijalta toivotaan vähintään 1-3  vuoden työkokemusta tehtävistä. Työmaat sijaitsevat Tamperella ja Tampereen lähiseudulla.\r\n\r\nOma auto välttämätön.\r\n\r\nTee hakemus mahdollisimman pian! Hakemukset: julian.koza@pp.inet.fi\r\n\r\nJob description:\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a multi-skilled professional for various building work. Your main duties would consist of sloping concrete floors. You would also be expected to have experience in tiling work and bricklaying. You would be required to have 1 to 3 years of experience in the above tasks. An ability to carry out assigned jobs independently is very important. \r\n\r\nWork sites are located in the city of Tampere and the surrounding regions. Having your own car is a must. We expect you to be able to communicate in Finnish or English and knowledge in Albanian would be an advantage. We will provide assistance in finding accommodation and other general affairs as necessary.\r\n\r\nExperience required:\r\n    1 to 3 years\r\n\r\n    Contract duration:\r\n    1 to 3 months, possibly longer\r\n\r\n    Contract type:\r\n    Fixed-term\r\n\r\n    Employer:\r\n    Rakennuspalvelu Veljekset Koza avoin yhtiö\r\n\r\n    How to apply:\r\n    Applications to Julian.koza@pp.inet.fi",
