				"kuvausteksti" : "Chinese Speaking Sales Associate\r\n\r\nWorld Duty Free operates 11 high-end Duty Free stores at Helsinki Airport, one of Finland's most international work environments. Our stores carry a large variety of Duty Free products and we are open every day of the year between 4 AM and midnight. We are part of Dufry Group which is currently present in 63 countries worldwide. You can find more information regarding our operations at www.Dufry.com. \r\n\r\nWorld Duty Free is now looking for a Chinese speaking Sales Associate to work in our BVLGARI Pop-Up Store in Helsinki Airport. The position is full-time and fixed term until 31.7.2018.\r\n\r\nThe selected candidate will work in our BVLGARI Pop-Up store, which is a new world-class luxury store located in the airport's NonSchengen terminal. \r\n\r\nAs a Sales Associate your tasks include providing a luxurious customer service and sales experience and promoting BVLGARI to our clientele. Your working hours will include early morning shifts and late evening shifts as well as working on weekends and bank holidays. \r\n\r\nTo succeed in this role, we expect you to have:\r\n- previous experience in customer service and sales with prestigious brands\r\n- willingness and commitment to work in a shift work environment where opening hours range from 4 AM to midnight\r\n- Chinese and English language skills\r\n\r\nWe offer you a possibility to work in a versatile customer service and sales role with a unique and prestigious brand. We provide our employees with customer service, sales and product trainings on a regular basis. We also offer our staff health and wellbeing related benefits. \r\n\r\nOur employees are entitled to a complimentary taxi service for commuting between home and work between 23 and 06 AM. As our employee you are also entitled to free parking at Helsinki Airport. \r\n\r\nInterested? Please send your CV and application letter in English to hr.helsinki@dufry.com by Sunday, November 12th 2017. \r\n\r\nFor further inquiries, please contact BVLGARI Store Supervisor & Brand Ambassador Jan Koskinen via email: jan.koskinen@dufry.com.",
