				"kuvausteksti" : "Financial Assistant - part time\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a motivated finance student to work part time as a Financial Assistant in our small finance team, assisting in various financial tasks. This position is at QPR Headquarters in Helsinki and is ideal for a to-be finance professional with some experience in finance routines and willingness to learn more.\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\nDaily routines for accounts payable and expense claims\r\nDaily routines for invoicing and accounts receivable\r\nActing as a back-up for accounting\r\nOther finance department accounting and reporting tasks\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\nPreferably some earlier finance experience\r\nPreferably a 2nd or 3rd year student in Finance or Business Administration\r\nLogical thinking skills\r\nHigh attention to details\r\nAbility to learn new things fast and eagerness to grow\r\nFluency in written and spoken English and Finnish\r\nGood knowledge of MS Excel\r\nAbility to work for 2-3 days a week (we also offer an opportunity to a summer job)\r\n\r\nWe offer:\r\n\r\nAn opportunity to work in an international, innovative company\r\nA good base experience of wide financial routines\r\nGrowth opportunities in a growing company\r\nGreat colleagues\r\nFlexible timing of work to combine work with your studies\r\n\r\n\r\nAbout us:\r\n\r\nQPR Software Plc (Nasdaq Helsinki) provides solutions for strategy execution, performance and process management, process mining and enterprise architecture in over 50 countries. Users of QPR Software gain the insight they need for informed decisions that make a difference. With 25 years of experience, 2 000 customers and over a million licenses sold, QPR's products are highly regarded by industry analysts and customers alike.\r\n\r\nQPR Software: Dare to improve\r\n\r\nMore information about us: www.qpr.com\r\n\r\nPlease send your application, salary request and CV as soon as possible via our website at https://www.qpr.com/company/careers , latest on 13 November 2017. We will proceed with the process as soon as we find a suitable person. For more information, please contact Maija Suominen (Accountant) at tel. +358 40 720 5497 on Thursday 9 November at 2.00 - 3.00 pm.\r\n\r\nHeadhunters and recruitment agencies may not submit resumes/CVs through this Web site or directly to managers. QPR Software does not accept unsolicited headhunter and agency resumes. QPR Software will not pay fees to any third-party agency or company that does not have a signed agreement with the Company.",
