				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for a skilled professional to perform actual product service work for Bittium products. In this position you would be a member of our Product Operations team, working also in co-operation with our R&D. \r\n\r\nWhat we need is a Technician/Engineer which have previous experience of products manufacturing and service work related to telecommunications and mobile products. Candidate typical work day consists of for example Bittium product repairs and also to give support for Bittium internal product development programs. We can promise, that the work with our high-end products will be interesting and versatile and there's a demand for great problem solving skills in co-operation with our people.  Position will require good soldering skills.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn brief, this is what we require:\r\n-Good soldering skills\r\n-Previous experience related to telecommunications technologies and also to measurement instruments(Baseband & RF) \r\n-Previous experience about manufacturing work or product service\r\n-Good problem solving skills\r\n-Suitable education, e.g. Electrical engineer/Technician\r\n-Good co-operation skills\r\n-Previous experience from soldering rework stations is an advantage.\r\n-RF experience would be great\r\n-Good written and spoken English language",
