				"kuvausteksti" : "Wärtsilä Energy Solutions is a leading global energy system integrator offering a broad range of environmentally sound solutions. Our offering includes ultra-flexible internal combustion engine based power plants, utility-scale solar PV power plants, energy storage & integration solutions, as well as LNG terminals and distribution systems. The flexible and efficient Wärtsilä solutions provide customers with superior value and enable a transition to a more sustainable and modern energy system. As of 2017, Wärtsilä has 65 GW of installed power plant capacity in 177 countries around the world.\r\n\r\nAt Wärtsilä Energy Solutions, designing and building power plants for utilities and industry has been our passion for decades. To strengthen our Engineering Team in Vaasa, Finland, we are now looking for an Electrical or Automation Project Engineer eager to develop the Energy Solutions business and solutions of the future. \r\n\r\nResponsibilities \r\n- Safeguard that Electrical works are executed according to contract specifications and design directives as a member of a project team \r\n- Make purchase specifications and bill of quantities as required for the project execution \r\n- Make project specific design and design packages \r\n- Co-ordinate the design between sub-suppliers \r\n- Develop Power Plant project wise Electrical solution for the client \r\n- Carry out sub-supplier quality- and delivery follow-ups \r\n- Support our site team during installation and commission phases \r\n- Give feedback regarding technical solutions and claims \r\n- Act as stand-in for Chief Project Engineer Electrical when requested \r\n- Possibility to participate in development projects.\r\n\r\nRequirements \r\n- BSc. or MSc. in Electrical or Automation Engineering \r\n- Being self-going, having team working skills, motivation to learn and grow professionally and willingness to travel as well as ability to understand and work with diverse cultures \r\n- Working experience is a benefit \r\n- Experience with industrial safety systems is a benefit \r\n- Fluency in English. \r\n\r\nContact person for additional information \r\nJonas Lundvik, Team Leader Project Engineering\r\nTel: +358 50 5361978 \r\n\r\nAnders Paavola, General Manager, Electrical Project Engineering \r\nTel: +358 40 5491253",
