				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you interested in working in our challenging infra development projects in Oulu or Tampere? We have openings for a few more skilled FPGA professionals. As an FPGA engineer you would be a key player in our base station product development projects, taking responsibility for defining, designing, implementing and verifying the FPGA/VHDL solutions. \r\n\r\nRequirements: \r\nMinimum three, preferably more than five years' experience on FPGA/VHDL design in base station projects \r\nStrong experience on VHDL Design tools (Vivado, Xilinx, Altera, Modelsim etc)\r\nStrong experience on FPGA design, specification, debug, and documentation\r\nExperience on a Matlab\r\nExperience on UVM system Verilog is a plus \r\nTeam playing -skills\r\n\r\nIn our multicultural organization you will also need good skills in written and spoken English.",
