				"kuvausteksti" : "Job description:  customer service, order fulfillment, telephone contact with individual customers, product\r\npromotion and sales, customer relationship management, data handling, administration and work with the internal system.\r\nEmployer name: Jobhouse Sp. z o.o.\r\n\r\nREQUIREMENTS\r\nEducation: Secondary\r\nProfessional experience: Language knowledge Language Level 1. Finnish\r\n1. C1-C2 spoken\r\nC1-C2 in writing\r\n\r\nOther relevant requirements: knowledge of MS Office. Knowledge of romanian on C1 level.\r\nKnowledge of english or polish on B2 level. Experience on similar position will be an\r\nadvantage (sales or/and call center); high communication and interpersonal skillsself-reliance,\r\nproblem-solving abilities, responibility for entrusted actions, motivation and involvment,\r\ncreativity, responsibility, stress resistance.\r\n\r\nThe employer offers: Full-time job, possibility of permament employment after trial\r\nperiod, possibility of individual, flexible working hours (between 8 and 21), possibility of\r\nworking in the office (office in the center of Warsaw) or home office. Rewarding good\r\nresults; Training system; Tools necessary for work; Friendly working environment;\r\nPossibility of development and promotion.\r\n\r\nHOW TO APPLY\r\nDocuments required:  CV in English to the Eures adviser\r\nIf you're interested in the vacancy - send your CV to m.tredota@wup.mazowsze.pl,\r\ngiving refference number: \"SPRZED/WAW/JEZ 23177\"\r\nContact details to EURES adviser or\r\nemployer's representative:\r\nemail:  m.tredota@wup.mazowsze.pl\r\n\r\nDeadline for applications / Closing date: 2017-12-31\r\nWe kindly inform, that we will contact selected candidates only.",
