				"kuvausteksti" : "System Architect, Abloy Oy, Joensuu\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an innovative and customer focused System Architect to join Abloy IT team. \r\n\r\nAs System Architect you will be participating in the design, development, implementation and continuous improvement of Abloy IT systems and IT service delivery. \r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\n analyze business processes and requirements,\r\n design and maintain system and service architectures,\r\n develop and continuously improve systems and service delivery.\r\n\r\nRight now we are in an exciting transitional phase, which brings both challenges and possibilities to the table, enabling you to be part of the solutions of tomorrow.  \r\n\r\nApplicant Qualification: \r\n\r\nUniversity degree in Computer Science or Software Engineering,\r\nA proven track record of system architecture design and system development,\r\nExpertise in secure system development and information security management,\r\nProven ability to work analytically,\r\nExcellent communication and teamwork skills,\r\nAbility to work under pressure and deliver on your commitments,\r\nSelf-motivated personality,\r\nPositive and customer focused person with strong business understanding,\r\nFluency in English and Finnish\r\n\r\nVarietal experience in system architecture, software engineering, IT infrastructure and IT service management is valued. To be successful in this role we believe previous work experience with ERP, Manufacturing, CRM and/or e-Solution development projects would be beneficial.\r\n\r\nBased on your knowledge, skills and interests, the content of this role can be built to meet the challenges you are looking for.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact IT Manager Ari Ronkainen, mobile 050 3688 261.\r\n\r\nPlease complete your application no later than November 14, 2017 at abloy.fi.\r\n\r\n\r\nLet's open the doors to the future - together! \r\nWorking for ASSA ABLOY means that you will be part of a dynamic and agile environment, developing innovative solutions to improve our customers' lives. As the global leader in door opening solutions we are using the latest technologies to open doors to events, hospitals, education, homes, hotels, airports and businesses. Joining ASSA ABLOY means being part of a fast-moving company with many opportunities. \r\nWould you like to join us in opening doors of the future?",
