				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for more developers to work in our Bittium Tough Mobile platform -team and in the many other exciting projects that we have. As an Android developer at Bittium you would be developing, testing and maintaining software in Android environment. Experience in Java would be vital, C and C++ recommended. \r\n\r\nIn addition to these we appreciate:\r\n-Experience in developing in Agile environment \r\n-Previous experience and merits in Android development\r\n-Previous experience using Git, Jenkins and Gerrit\r\n-Familiarity with continuous integration\r\n-Effective communication skills in English \r\n-Strong problem solving skills\r\n\r\nThe position is located in Oulu or Espoo.",
