				"kuvausteksti" : "The early morning newspaper delivery is an important field of business for Posti, which services are produced and developed by Posti Palvelut Ltd. There are 2700 professionals working in the company nationally, who ensure high quality and reliable service to our customers every day. \r\nThe early morning delivery of metropolitan area has over 1100 newspaper carriers that deliver eight different products, Helsingin Sanomat being the main product.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for\r\n\r\nNEWSPAPER CARRIERS \r\n\r\nto metropolitan area (Helsinki, Vantaa, Espoo, Kauniainen, Hyvinkää, Lohja, Porvoo) for fixed term and permanent employments. \r\n\r\nThe working time is during nights mainly between 2AM to 6AM. Newspapers are delivered in every day of the week and workers off days are changing weekly. Carriers work in 6+2 rotation, where every six work days are followed by two off days. \r\nThe work is very independent and requires initiative responsibility, good physical health and condition and 18 years of age because of the nighttime work legislation in Finland.\r\nBecause we value work safety, a minimum of two years driving experience and driving license in Finland are required for applicants who deliver newspapers by car.\r\n\r\nThe salary is based on the collective labor agreement TEAM.\r\nPlease mention the areas where you are willing to work in your application.\r\nLeave your application to our recruitment system at www.staffpoint.fi. \r\n\r\nWork begins immediately after finding the right person. Applications will be processed during the application period.\r\n\r\nTelephone inquiries from Monday to Friday 08-09 am. Contact number 020 720 6435.\r\n\r\n\r\nEdellytämme sinulta\r\n\r\nGood physical fitness.\r\n\r\nAt least 18 years of age.\r\n\r\nAccuracy and diligence.\r\n\r\nThe Finnish driving license valid for at least two years (Only for car couriers)\r\n\r\n\r\nTarjoamme sinulle\r\n\r\nWe offer a work for a large operator, with the possibility of a long-term employment relationship.\r\n\r\n\r\nArvostamme\r\n\r\nA brisk and self-directed grasp of work.\r\n\r\n\r\nKiinnostuitko?\r\n\r\nRegister as a candidate at www.staffpoint.fi and fill out the application carefully and paste your CV with your salary application. It is very important for us to know what you've done before, what you know and what you want to do in the future.\r\n\r\n\r\nLisätietoja\r\n\r\nAleksi Laaksonen\r\nRekrytointikonsultti\r\nTeollisuus-, rakennus- ja logistiikkatoimialat\r\nStaffPoint Oy, Luomantie 1-3, 93600 KUUSAMO\r\n020 720 6435, Vaihde 030 047 2000\r\naleksi.laaksonen@staffpoint.fi, www.staffpoint.fi",
