				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for frontend, backend and full stack developers to work in our projects in Oulu, Tampere and Espoo. To master this trade you should be a sovereign programmer and possess a versatile technological skill-set. We especially appreciate experience in software development, preferably in large complex environments. To really make a lasting impression you must be following the latest technologies and have a self-improvement attitude as part of your identity. \r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n-Experience in agile software development projects \r\n-Good programming and scripting skills \r\n-Experience and familiarity with web services, stack layers, security standards and complex multi-application/embedded systems.\r\n-Problem solving skills (Client, API Layer, Database, Server, OS)\r\n-Understanding at least in some of next technologies and tools: Java, JavaScript, Junit, Python, Jenkins, Git, AngularJS, Ruby, Node.js, REST, JSON, Ansible, SQL, NoSQL, AWS,  Mongo.\r\n-Server/Virtual server understanding \r\n-Database competence and experience\r\n-Experience in continuous integration and automated UI acceptance testing\r\n-Fluency in written and spoken English\r\n\r\nIn addition we appreciate: \r\n\r\n-Linux knowledge\r\n-Cloud SW understanding and competence \r\n-Good communication and team working skills\r\n-Open-minded attitude",
