				"kuvausteksti" : "Bittium's Espoo team is looking for more engineers for various duties. Now we have an opening for a jack-of-all-trades team leader to boost our front and back end development, cloud architectures and SW development. As a team leader you would also get your own hands dirty with actual hard core development work, so we are looking for someone with strong technical know-how with credentials but also with strong people skills and an understanding for the big picture from project management point of view. \r\n\r\nAt Bittium our way of working enables people to get their ideas heard; we appreciate our staff that is at its best when thinking out-of-the box. Working in agile mode, Continuous Integration, DevOps - that is how it's done.\r\n\r\nWith the following characteristics and skills you will hit the ground running:\r\n\r\n-Team leading and project management skills\r\n-Cloud solution deployments (preferably Azure or AWS deployments) \r\n-Building PaaS based customer solutions - IoT Platform experience is a bonus\r\n-SW and comms/network security\r\n-SW integration and API development and management - iPaaS knowledge would be nice\r\n-Big data and analytics\r\n\r\nFollowing knowledge and skills would be a bonus:\r\n\r\n-AI and machine learning\r\n-Sensor networks and gateway technologies and edge computing\r\n-Certificate in cloud programming\r\n-SaaS solution operations\r\n\r\nIf you are not on team leader level yet but you master two or more of these areas, send your application anyway.  Let's start a discussion on what would inspire you at Bittium.",
