				"kuvausteksti" : "We're currently looking for Design Handover Engineer for our international client in the OL3 Site. The job starts as soon as the right candidate is found and lasts approximately 8 months depending on our client's need.\r\n\r\nCriterions:\r\n\r\nSuitable educational background (Engineer)\r\nAbility and experience to handle several activities; understanding of technical and quality documents\r\nGood communication skills\r\nExperience in working at OL3 site is a plus\r\n\r\nAs a person you are multi-tasks, autonomous, rigorous\r\n\r\nTechnical knowledge:\r\nProficient with Excell\r\nAutoCad acknowledge is a plus\r\nLanguage skills: Advanced English skills (written, spoken), good skills in French, German and/or Finnish would be a plus\r\n\r\nResponsibilities:\r\n\r\nCheck that all the technical documents expected from the Supplier for engineering and manufacturing contracts are received before the Supplier contract is closed.\r\nCheck that there is no open point remaining on those documents and that they are in an as-built status and that those documents were provided in native format. Metadata of those documents also need to be checked.\r\nFill in check lists to indicate that the check was performed as requested\r\nContact the supplier when documents are missing and engineering department when open point are not yet closed.\r\n\r\nThis is a great ability to work with an international company where you can use and develop your skills.\r\n\r\nPlease apply for the \"Design Handover Engineer\" position by registering at www.adecco.fi. Attach your English CV to the application. For more information please contact HR Consultant Eerika Jantunen +35846 875 0111.",
