				"kuvausteksti" : "We are currently looking for Cost Controller for our international client in the OL3 site starting as soon as the right person is found. The contract is fixed-term for 12 months.\r\n\r\nWe expect you to have Master's level university or business school degree with Finance as a major.\r\nAs a person, you are reliable, analytical and rigorous. You are able to work autonomously, but also as dependable team player.\r\nRequired technical skills include excellent skills in Excel. Previous experience working with SAP is considered as a plus. Fluent English is mandatory. French, German and/or Finnish skills are a plus.\r\n\r\nYour main responsibilities will include, but are not limited to the following:\r\nCost follow-up and internal reporting\r\nConstruction invoice and purchase request handling for Cost Controller\r\nPeriodical financial reviews related to own scope\r\nPeriodical closings related to own scope\r\nCash-forecast related to own scope\r\n\r\nWe offer you an opportunity to develop and prove your skills in the field of Cost Controlling and to work in an international atmosphere.\r\n\r\nPlease apply for the \"Cost Controller\" position by registering at www.adecco.fi. Attach your English CV to the application. The position will be fulfilled as soon as the suitable candidate is found! For more information contact Eerika Jantunen +358 46 875 0111.",
