				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for several senior software engineers and specialist to join our Radio Network SW development teams in Oulu and Kajaani. With us you get an opportunity to develop next generation Radio Base Station management solutions. As a candidate for these positions you should have several years of experience working with Radio Access Network. Radio Base Station and O&M SW experience are preferred.\r\n\r\n \r\nJob responsibilities:\r\n\r\n-Specifying new features and updating the old ones to fulfill new BS architecture and requirements\r\n-Communicating with system architects and R&D teams to find the best solutions for every challenge\r\n-Helping SW development and verification teams to do their work and reach goals\r\n\r\nJob requirements for an ideal candidate:\r\n\r\n-Experience on Radio Access Network O&M\r\n-Several years of experience writing SW system specifications and documents   \r\n-Eagerness and ability to solve complex technical problems\r\n-Team playing skills\r\n-Fluency in written and spoken English\r\n-Excellent communication skills in multi team and multisite environments\r\n\r\nIn addition we appreciate:\r\n\r\n-Strong technical background \r\n-Embedded SW design experience\r\n-Radio base station verification experience\r\n-Knowledge on 2G, WCDMA, LTE and 5G",
