				"kuvausteksti" : "Bittium has many intriguing projects ongoing that need the insight and expertise of an experienced RF engineer or specialist. Let us know what you have accomplished so far and what are your next goals for professional development - then let's talk about finding you the perfect role to fit your talent.\r\n\r\nQualities we appreciate in a candidate:\r\n\r\n-Solid experience in RF design work in telecommunication area and RF design including schematics, PWB and testing\r\n-Mentor and ADS/AWR-Aplac tools knowhow\r\n-Fluency in Finnish and English\r\n-Nice set of social skills and positive attitude",
