				"kuvausteksti" : "We seek for Swedish speaking Customer Service officer for prestigious international company for permanent employment relationship. Our client company is a respected international mobile financial services provider listed on the stock exchange. Its own intelligence-based big data system delivers immediate credit decisions based on cutting-edge data security.\r\n\r\nDuties:\r\n\r\nIn your daily work, you will consult customers with regars to bank's products and services face-to-face, by phone and email and identify sales potential based on customer needs. Your work includes, among other things, opening accounts, issuing and blocking payment cards, acquiring of customer information in line with the banks policies. Also essential part of your work is close co-operation with other departments and land coordinators\r\n\r\nWhat we require:\r\n\r\nTo succeed in your work, you need customer orientated attitude and team skills, as well as genuine interest towards banking and finance sector. The key to your job is the ability to quickly learn new systems and practices. In addition, you will need fluent English and Swedish written and oral skills, excellent communication and negotiation skills and Microsoft Office skills.\r\n\r\nWhat's the best:\r\n\r\nWe offer permanent employment relationship with a prestigious international company, competitive salary and benefits. Competent personnel are the main asset and our customer regularly invest in training and support for the skills of their employees. In addition, you will receive support from your friendly and supportive team. The sunny malta offers beaches, sunsets, crystal clear sea, history and nature experiences. In addition, excellent weather conditions in Malta enable a wide range of outdoor activities and recreational opportunities.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in the position, please submit your application as soon as possible!\r\n\r\n________________________________________________________________________________\r\nBiisoni Oy on auktorisoitu valtakunnallinen henkilöstöpalveluyritys.\r\nYritys on vuonna 2006 perustettu vastuullinen toimija, jonka\r\nerityisosaamisena ovat henkilöstövuokraus-, rekrytointi- ja\r\nulkoistuspalvelut.",
