				"kuvausteksti" : "-PRO Resources Oy Ltd is a staffing and recruiting company belonging to Nipromec Group focusing mainly on needs of our customers in the fields of energy, industry and offshore.\r\n\r\nWe are now looking for Support for Spare part team (7 positions) for our client in Olkiluoto. Work starts as soon as possible and estimated duration is 2 months.\r\n\r\nMain tasks:\r\n-Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time.\r\n-Review and search for items in warehouse inventories.\r\n-Search for technical / quality documentation in databases / folders.\r\n-Follow-up of the Purchase Requests and Purchase Orders.\r\n-Provide the documentation of the spare parts for maintenance reports and other work orders.\r\n\r\nGeneral and technical background expected:\r\n-Exposure to facets of either maintenance, commissioning, quality, warehousing, procurement, or spare parts is beneficial.\r\n\r\nSkills required\r\n-Understanding of technical documentation\r\n-General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology\r\n-Computer literacy in MS-Office\r\n-Understanding of quality documentation and certificates.\r\n-Fluent English both written and spoken is required.\r\n\r\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For more information please go to www.n-pro.fi",
