				"kuvausteksti" : "Technical Software Consultant\r\n\r\nAre you interested being a solution hunter and creator, a problem solver and making customers happy? As a technical consultant you will be implementing QPR's software products to customers, integrating them to customers' systems and providing customized solutions if they are needed and documenting them. As a member of the consulting team you serve mostly our direct customers in Finland but also our customers and partners abroad.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for motivated people and quick learners of new things. You don't need to be a master on the topics below, but knowledge and ability to learn quickly and execute in some of them is needed. We expect technical software consultants to have several of the following skills:\r\n\r\nGeneral IT knowledge (IT infrastructure, MS Windows (incl. servers), MS IIS, MS SQL Servers, networking, Active Directory)\r\nKnowledge of some data integration (SQL, databases, Microsoft SSIS)\r\nHTML and CSS\r\nJavaScript\r\njQuery\r\nVisual Basic / VBScript\r\nWeb service interfaces\r\nYou are organized and can handle several projects at the same time. Fluent spoken and written English is a must. Fluent spoken and written Finnish is preferred.\r\n\r\nWe offer you an exciting forefront position to see and learn how different organizations develop their operations, execute their strategy and monitor their performance.\r\n\r\nPlease send your application, salary request and CV as soon as possible via our website at https://www.qpr.com/company/careers. We will proceed with the process as soon as we find a suitable person Further information about this opportunity and requirements can be obtained from Pauli Mertanen. He can be reached at pauli.mertanen@qpr.com.\r\n\r\nHeadhunters and recruitment agencies may not submit resumes/CVs through this Web site or directly to managers. QPR Software does not accept unsolicited headhunter and agency resumes. QPR Software will not pay fees to any third-party agency or company that does not have a signed agreement with the Company.\r\n\r\nAbout QPR Software\r\n\r\nQPR Software provides solutions for strategy execution, performance and process management, process mining and enterprise architecture in over 50 countries. Users of QPR Software gain the insight they need for informed decisions that make a difference.\r\n\r\nWith 25 years of experience, 2 000 customers and over a million licenses sold, QPR's products are highly regarded by industry analysts and customers alike.\r\n\r\nDare to Improve.\r\n\r\nwww.qpr.com",
