				"kuvausteksti" : "N-PRO Resources Oy Ltd is a staffing and recruiting company belonging to Nipromec Group focusing mainly on needs of our customers in the fields of energy, industry and offshore.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a Supplier Documentation Check Team Leader for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration 12 months.\r\n\r\nUnder the authority of the Final Documentation Manager the Supplier Documentation Check Team leader shall lead the activity that will ensure complete supplier documentation delivery. The main aim of this activity is to secure complete final documentation delivery for client's customer.\r\nPrevious experience of team leading or management is mandatory in this position. Experience of business process modelling considered as a plus\r\n\r\nThe tasks will include, but are not limited to the following\r\n-Schedule the supplier documentation check activities according to project priority.\r\n-Negotiate about the upcoming priorities with various technical disciplines and the supply chain.\r\n-Following-up the quality of the checks.\r\n-Report progress.\r\n-Give the general leadership to team members.\r\n-Author the needed project instructions.\r\n-Fluent spoken and written English is required. Ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus.\r\n\r\nGeneral and technical background expected:\r\n-Engineer (generally from any relevant field).\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n-Good leadership skills and a good team player.\r\n-Capacity of organizing the day-to-day activities.\r\n-Rigorous especially for adherence to procedures.\r\n-Good writing skills.\r\n\r\nTechnical:\r\n-Good general knowledge of office tools is mandatory.\r\n-Knowledge in data mining, databases (SQL) and macro programming would be considered as a plus.\r\n\r\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi or fill in an application at www.n-pro.fi",
