				"kuvausteksti" : "Wärtsilä Marine Solutions enhances the business of its marine and oil & gas industry customers by providing innovative products and integrated solutions that are safe, environmentally sustainable, efficient, flexible, and economically sound. Being a technology leader, and through the experience, know-how and dedication of its personnel, Wärtsilä is able to customise solutions that provide optimal benefits to its customers around the world. \r\n\r\nPosition description\r\n\r\nAre you passionate about engines and their development? Do you want to work among the best experts in the industry? \r\nIf your answer is \"yes\", then we have an opportunity for you. \r\n\r\nWärtsilä is looking for a Gas Engine Expert to strengthen gas engine development in Marine Solution, Engines, Technology, Testing & Validation. Preferable location is Vaasa, Finland and alternatively Trieste, Italy or Bermeo, Spain. \r\n\r\nResponsibilities\r\n- Participate in gas engine projects on all engine platforms (W20 - W50) as a gas engine expert \r\n- Give gas engine related technical support \r\n- Participate in test activities on gas engines \r\n- Give presentations in technical meetings. \r\n\r\nRequirements\r\n- A genuine passion for gas engines \r\n- M.Sc. or B.Sc. in automation or mechanical engineering \r\n- Knowhow of Wärtsilä gas engines, both SG and DF \r\n- Experience of gas engine automation systems \r\n- Systematic and structured way of working \r\n- Good team working skills \r\n- Good command of written and spoken English. \r\n\r\nContact person to give further information\r\nStefan Saario, GM Engine Operation Expertise \r\nTel: +358 400 703154 (workdays 9-16) \r\nE-mail: stefan.saario@wartsila.com",
