				"kuvausteksti" : "Oy Reagena Ltd was established in 1987 and is celebrating the 30th anniversary in 2017. The company develops, manufactures and sells reagents and diagnostic tests for hospitals as well as pharmaceutical and  chemical industries. The Domestic and international sales and distributed products by Reagena  are continuously growing. Reagena has strong market position in Finland and is a leader in selected niche segments. Reagena products are currently exported to more than 20 countries. The company is located in Toivala, Siilinjärvi near Kuopio Airport, and has a branch office in Turku. Read more at www.reagena.com/en\r\n\r\nhttp://www.reagena.com/fi/ \r\n\r\nWe are looking for an experienced and energetic Key Account Manager to our global sales team\r\n\r\nYour main responsibility is to actively seek and establish new partnerships and further develop the existing customer relationships. You will analyze different market areas and manage new and existing contracts in an international environment. You set and achieve your sales targets ambitiously and are prepared to gain results. You enjoy being in the international atmosphere and you excel in networking in different cultures.\r\n\r\nIdeally, you would have:\r\n\r\n-5 years relevant experience in international sales with a proven track record\r\n-Knowledge on how distribution and sales networks function in an international environment\r\n-Fluency in Finnish and English is essential, command of Swedish is considered to be a plus\r\n-Proactive and self-reliant attitude\r\n-Team and communication skills with an ability to work also independently\r\n-\"Can do\" attitude\r\n-Experience in the diagnostic/biotechnology field\r\n Experience in developing customer relationships and managing projects with key accounts\r\n-Driver's license\r\n\r\nYou will have the full support of our professional R&D, sales and marketing teams. Extensive travelling is required.",
