				"kuvausteksti" : "Miradore is an 11-year-old, steadily growing and privately held, Finnish software company. Miradore develops and sells products for IT systems management and device management covering support for workstations, servers, tablets and mobile phone devices.\r\n\r\nMiradore has two offices in Finland - in Vantaa and in Lappeenranta - and branch offices in Stockholm and Singapore. In addition, Miradore has local presence in different regions, including the USA, Baltics and Central Europe. To date, over 700 000 devices are managed by Miradore products, reaching 160+ different countries. We have around 30 skilled people working for us in a great team.\r\n\r\nNow we are looking for a Marketing Specialist to join our marketing team at our Vantaa office. This is a permanent position.\r\n\r\nJOB DESCRIPTION\r\n\r\nYour tasks will include at least the following:\r\n-Coordinating daily activities\r\n-Taking part in decision making and planning marketing activities\r\n-Developing the Miradore website\r\n-Co-coordinating many things such as meetings and webinars\r\n-Creating content (news, newsletters, etc.)\r\n-Updating the Miradore web site and Social Media accounts\r\n-Proofreading our content (blog posts, our website, etc.)\r\n\r\nREQUIREMENTS\r\n\r\nWe expect you to have at least the following in order to be successful in your work:\r\n- 3 years in Marketing experience, especially Digital Marketing\r\n- Digital Marketing Skills\r\n--- SEO\r\n--- Google Analytics\r\n- Native or excellent English. Finnish and other languages are a plus\r\n\r\n\r\nWE OFFER\r\n\r\nWe offer you an inspirational and international working environment. We offer our employees the option to work from home, a free mobile phone and home internet as well as lunch benefits. Above everything else, we promise that you will benefit from:\r\n- superb international colleagues\r\n- an inspirational working atmosphere\r\n- the possibility to work with cutting-edge technology\r\n- lunch benefit and Smartum card and of course\r\n- an unlimited amount of coffee included in your workdays!\r\n\r\n\r\nAPPLYING\r\n\r\nNow, that we have told you about us, it's time for us to hear about you! Make your move and apply no later than the 12th of November by sending us your application and CV via e-mail to rekry(a)miradore.com. \r\n\r\nAdditional information can be requested from Mira Majuri, mira.majuri(a)miradore.com or 050 327 7520.",
