				"kuvausteksti" : "Wärtsilä Energy Solutions is a leading global energy system integrator offering a broad range of environmentally sound solutions. Our offering includes ultra-flexible internal combustion engine based power plants, utility-scale solar PV power plants, energy storage & integration solutions, as well as LNG terminals and distribution systems. The flexible and efficient Wärtsilä solutions provide customers with superior value and enable a transition to a more sustainable and modern energy system. As of 2017, Wärtsilä has 65 GW of installed power plant capacity in 177 countries around the world.\r\n\r\nWärtsilä Energy Solutions, Project Controls & Planning, is looking for a Contract Manager to support project teams delivering EPC projects.\r\n\r\nPosition is located in Vaasa, Finland.\r\n\r\nResponsibilities\r\n- Identify, initiate and manage proactively contractual variation orders\r\n- Lead and communicate the contract and contract triggers and mechanisms within the project towards sub suppliers and customer\r\n- Awareness of project specific requirements, e.g. HSE, Quality, Documentation, and determining their impact in the project with subject matter experts\r\n- Coach the project team in contractual issues\r\n- Subcontracting together with project team, preparing and taking part of negotiations with subcontractors from bidding phase to contract closing\r\n- Monitoring and controlling subcontractor/customer compliance to contractual requirements.\r\n\r\nRequirements\r\n- B.Sc. or M.Sc. in Engineering or Industrial Economics and Management\r\n- Good communication and presentation skills\r\n- Effective team working and interpersonal skills\r\n- Excellent leadership skills as well as proactive and persistent attitude\r\n- Organized, able to multi-task and manage large sets of information even under pressure\r\n- Fluency in English and Finnish, other language skills are seen as a plus.\r\n\r\nContact Person\r\nPeter Storm\r\nGeneral Manager, Project Controls and Planning\r\nTel: +358 40 5836629 \r\nEmail: peter.storm@wartsila.com",
