				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for ANDROID DEVELOPER who is proactive and highly motivated mobile app engineer with good knowledge of the Android SDK, experience building Android apps, and a strong desire to learn and grow. \r\n\r\nAs a Android developer, your responsibilities include implementing UI, porting Android/Linux kernel to new embedded devices and developing communication APIs between various embedded devices.  \r\n \r\nYOU WILL\r\n- Develop for a wide variety of devices and OS versions\r\n- Develop APIs for wired/wireless communications. \r\n- Port Android/Linux kernel to new embedded devices (ARM)\r\n - Work directly with product and UX design teams\r\n- Develop solutions to improve app quality and development speed\r\n\r\nREQUIREMENTS\r\n- A Computer Science degree or similar\r\n- Object-oriented software development experience\r\n- Experience in building consumer facing Android apps in Java\r\n- Understanding of AOSP, Android Framework and Media frameworks\r\n\r\nITS COOL IF YOU\r\n- Rock at Android\r\n- Know embedded devices and C\r\n- Enjoy a small, enthusiastic team environment\r\n- Dig Gyro Gearloose.\r\n\r\nAre you ready to rock with us and take the challenge? Make your move and send your application and CV via our recruitment system by 31.11.2017. We look forward hearing from you!\r\n\r\nFor more information on the position, please contact Patrik, Patrik Ljungqvist Tel: +358 40 740 6975 or patrik.ljungqvist@microteam.fi  \r\n\r\nMicroteam Oy is a Finnish technology company providing design and project services to its customers. The company is particularly focused on embedded systems, machine automation, and enriching vehicle technology, increasing the added value for its customers through software and automation technology. \r\n\r\nRead more www.microteam.fi \r\n\r\nMicroteam is part of the Comatec Group which is a growing and developing company. We provide mechanical, electrical and automation design as well as expert- and project management services. We employ more than 500 professionals in 20 locations in five different countries. Our company has a strong experience of mobile machineries, commercials vehicles, material handling systems, production equipment and lines and boilers and power plants. \r\n\r\nWe are known especially for the ability to implement mechanical, electrical, automation and other challenging assignments to our customers in technology industry. Our solutions bases on over thirty years of experience, expertise and courage. The goal is to continue our strong growth to be the most preferred partner for the industry.",
