				"kuvausteksti" : "N-PRO Resources Oy Ltd is a staffing and recruiting company belonging to Nipromec Group focusing mainly on needs of our customers in the fields of energy, industry and offshore.\r\n\r\nWe are now looking for Spare parts Engineers / Technicians (4 positions) for our client in Olkiluoto. Work starts as soon as possible and estimated duration is 4 months.\r\n\r\nTasks:\r\n-Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time.\r\n-Review and search for items in warehouse inventories.\r\n-Generate purchase requests and technical requisition files.\r\n-Follow-up of the purchase requests and purchase orders.\r\n-Coordinate the required inspections of the spare parts.\r\n-Generate issue notes to receive parts from the warehouse.\r\n-Provide the documentation of the spare parts for maintenance reports and other work orders.\r\n-Prepare the pick-up and handover of required spare parts.\r\n\r\nGeneral and technical background expected:\r\n-First experience with specifications and documents (construction plan) are favorable.\r\n-Exposure to facets of either maintenance, commissioning, quality, warehousing, procurement or spare parts is mandatory.\r\n-Fluent English both written and spoken is required.\r\n\r\nSkills required:\r\n-Engineering degree/diploma with an emphasis on Mechanical Engineering (or similar) or experienced technician with a mechanical or electromechanical background.\r\n-Understanding of technical documentation for power plant components.\r\n-General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology.\r\n-Computer literacy in MS-Office.\r\n-Good communicator.\r\n\r\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi",
