				"kuvausteksti" : "Country Manager, Finland \r\n\r\nJoin us and help Europeans to find great fashion bargains online and ease their online shopping experience. We are currently looking for a Country Manager for our Finnish market. \r\n\r\nWe seek for a passionate marketing and sales professional, who appreciates working in an international startup and having an overall responsibility of our home market. You would be a part of a company that is building an eCommerce platform for millions of monthly users in multiple countries. You would have the overall responsibility of the platform from partner negotiations to designing and implementing marketing activities. \r\n\r\nWe expect you to have between 2-7 years of background within marketing and sales. \r\n\r\nYour profile is: \r\n- Marketing professional \r\n- Sales oriented \r\n- Strong negotiation skills and entrepreneurial thinking \r\n- Experienced professional in eCommerce, marketing or affiliate industry \r\n- Innovative, growth hacker mindset \r\n- Problem solving attitude \r\n- Good understanding of online marketing activities (SEM, FB, SEO) and Google Analytics \r\n- Team player \r\n- Self-confident, self-dependent, proactive and ambitious individual \r\n- Structured, accurate and communicative \r\n- Strong communication and writing skills \r\n- Fluent in spoken and written Finnish and English \r\n\r\n\r\nAs part of our team you will be facing tasks such as: \r\n- Partner web store negotiations and collaboration \r\n- Responsible for the marketing campaigns and activities including conception and execution \r\n- Managing the Finnish platform and it's operations \r\n- Acquiring new clients (partner shops, web agencies) \r\n- Responsible for the quality of the platform (content, products) \r\n- Analyzing the competition and the market \r\n\r\n\r\nThings we offer: \r\n- High responsibility - Make a difference! \r\n- Opportunity to influence your own work \r\n- Self-development and self-improvement \r\n- Low hierarchy \r\n- Fun, inspiring and international working environment \r\n- Coffee & Snacks & Company activities & Friday Beers \r\n\r\n\r\nSPOT-A-SHOP is the Momondo for Fashion. We bring all the best international fashion web stores and their on sale items into one destination. So we help people to find the best fashion bargains possible online. We are already present in Finland, Germany, France, Sweden and Poland and expanding quickly to other European countries. \r\n\r\nYou can find us on www.spot-a-shop.fi, www.spot-a-shop.de, www.spot-a-shop.fr, www.spot-a-shop.se, www.spot-a-shop.pl \r\n\r\nIf you're looking for a great place to work, SPOT-A-SHOP is definitely the right place for you! SPOT-A-SHOP is a dynamic startup and everyone has a chance in gaining responsibilities and growing in the position. \r\n\r\nApply today or share with your friends! \r\n\r\nPlease send your cv, salary request and cover letter to jesse@spot-a-shop.com",
