				"kuvausteksti" : "GBTIMES Ltd. is a cross-cultural media company, producing and delivering unique content over all media platforms. Our company provides the most relevant insights and perspectives, helping our global audience to broaden their cultural horizons, thus building an interactive venue for all their communication needs. We bring our audience news, features, opinions and analysis on China from a global perspective, encouraging dialogue between China and the world.\r\n\r\nGBTIMES Ltd. is looking for a full time Audio-Visual Producer to join our international and dynamic team in our HQ in Tampere.\r\n\r\nYour tasks will mainly include:\r\n\r\n- Developing video, photo, infographic and other audio-visual content in line with the \r\n  company's media strategy\r\n- Filming and post-producing of company's video content, especially on commercial and \r\n  promotional purpose\r\n- Social media management\r\n\r\nWe are looking for someone with:\r\n- At least two years of relevant work experience\r\n- Good understanding of media contents\r\n- Ability to use relevant photo and video editing tools\r\n- Strong verbal and written skills in English\r\n- Ability to work independently in self-directed, fast-paced environment\r\n\r\nTo apply for this position, please send your free-form application and CV with salary request to job.finland(at)gbtimes.com at latest on November 15th. This position will be filled as soon as the right candidate is found.",
