				"kuvausteksti" : "World Duty Free operates 11 high-end Duty Free stores at Helsinki Airport, one of Finland's most international work environments. Our stores carry a large variety of Duty Free products and we are open every day of the year between 4 AM and midnight. We are part of Dufry Group which is currently present in 63 countries worldwide. You can find more information regarding our operations at www.Dufry.com. \r\n\r\nWorld Duty Free (WDFG Helsinki Oy) is looking for a full-time Beauty Advisor to work in our Beauty Store at Helsinki Airport. The position is full-time and permanent, starting as soon as possible.  \r\n\r\nAs a Beauty Advisor your responsibilities include acting as an ambassador for Jo Malone London and representing the brand and its products to our clientele, customer service and sales tasks and any other tasks related to the daily store operations. \r\n\r\nBeauty Store is specialized in cosmetics and skincare, representing six world class brands including Jo Malone London, Tom Ford Beauty, La Mer, Bobbi Brown, Origins, and MAC Cosmetics. The store is located in Finland's most international work environment at Helsinki Airport and is open every day of the year from 4 AM to midnight. \r\n\r\nWe are expecting the candidate to have the following qualities:\r\n-Previous experience in customer service and sales preferably from the beauty industry\r\n-Customer-service oriented mindset\r\n-Willingness and commitment to work in shifts between 4 AM and midnight throughout the year\r\n-Fluent spoken English language skills, Finnish and Chinese language skills are an asset in this role\r\n\r\nEmployees who use public transportation for commuting between home and workplace are entitled to complimentary taxi service between 23:00 and 06:00. \r\n\r\nWe offer you the possibility to join an international travel retail operator working with prestigious brands as a part of a global sales-oriented team. Our employees are provided with customer service, sales and product trainings on a regular basis. We also offer our staff health and wellbeing related benefits. \r\n\r\nOur employees are entitled to a complimentary taxi service for commuting between home and work between 23 and 06 AM. As our employee you are also entitled to free parking at Helsinki Airport.\r\n\r\nInterested? Please send your application and CV in English to hr.helsinki@dufry.com no later than Sunday, November 12th 2017. Please title your email \"Beauty Advisor\". \r\n\r\nFor further inquiries regarding this role, please contact  hr.helsinki@dufry.com.",
