				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense International Oy provides its customers with resourcing solutions which appreciate the fluctuations in their projects. Our company is an ISO 9001:2008/14001:2004-certified actor with more than ten years of experience in operating in close cooperation with large-scale nuclear and construction sites, the Olkiluoto 3 nuclear power plant site being the largest of them.\r\nWe are currently looking for Spare Part Team Support for our Client in Olkiluoto Nuclear Power Plant, Finland. We are offering challenging work in an international project environment.\r\n\r\nMain tasks and responsibilities:\r\n\r\n-Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time\r\n-Review and search for items in warehouse inventories\r\n-Search for technical/ quality documentation in databases/ folders\r\n-Follow-up of the purchase requests and purchase orders\r\n-Provide the documentation of the spare parts for the maintenance reports and other work orders\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\n-Understanding of technical documentation\r\n-General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology\r\n-Computer literacy in MS-office\r\n-Perfect management of usual software (Excel, Work, Powerpoint, Outlook,..)\r\n\r\nLanguage skills:\r\n\r\n-Fluent in English\r\n-German, French and Finnish considered as benefit\r\n\r\nPlease register as a jobseeker and apply for the position through our website.\r\n\r\n\r\nDrug test and concise security clearance will be done for the selected person in order to get the permanent access to OL3 site.\r\n\r\nPlease note that due to client's urgent need only applicants with a valid working permit / EU-citizenship can be considered.\r\n\r\nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
