				"kuvausteksti" : "We are now looking for an experienced Program Manager to join JOT Automation's team in Oulu. The employment is temporary for approximately six months. However, there is a possibility to prolong the assignment after the six-month period or you might also be recruited to a permanent employment with JOT.\r\n\r\nAs a Program Manager, you will be working as an important part of global Test Automation Unit. You are responsible for customer project planning and deliveries according to business needs together with Business Unit management and support. Your key responsibilities are to achieve the customers' and projects' goals, implement RFQ process with Business Unit management, lead and manage projects' tasks and resources, plan, agree and communicate schedule with project team and customers. You are also responsible for ensuring the manufacturing delivery capability and reporting the project status and feedback to Business Unit management.\r\n\r\nRegular communication is an important part of your role with customer and JOT Group stakeholders. Moreover, this role requires willingness and ability to oversee customer cooperation and after sales actions.\r\n\r\nWe expect you to have\r\n\r\n- Strong experience in executing programs e.g. in product transfer, R&D, production, production testing areas in an international working environment\r\n- Suitable technical degree in, for example, engineering\r\n- Experience in multitasking in project environment\r\n- Excellent cooperation, communication, leadership and management skill\r\n- Active and innovative hands-on attitude towards challenges\r\n- Willingness to travel\r\n- Good spoken and written Finnish and English.\r\n\r\nWe appreciate the following skills\r\n\r\n- Knowledge of automation solutions and/or SW project management\r\n- After sales activities\r\n- Experience in international project management.\r\n\r\nJOT Automation is No. 1 for the automated production testing of wireless products with billions of devices tested with JOT's solutions since its founding in 1988. The company is a global partner for the industry giants manufacturing smart devices powered by all the major mobile operating systems.\r\n\r\nNow you have a chance to be part of JOT Automation's success story! Apply now and ensure your participation in this search for a Program Manager!\r\n\r\nNeed for further information? Please, contact Kristiina Vormala (040 837 4019), best available on Thursdays at 13-14.",
