				"kuvausteksti" : "Embedded software developer\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an engineer / developer to join oir R&D team to develop our testing tools. We offer you a position that involves challenging development work in a multiprocessor environment.\r\n\r\nThe developer's tasks will involve creating new functionalities for our testing tools, and supporting the Customer support engineer in debugging and fixing any issues raised by our customer. The work will mainly involve low-level hardcore coding in C. The job requires good command of low level software architecture and embedded software skills as well as knowledge of IP protocols.\r\n\r\nRequired skills:\r\n\r\n   Familiarity with C\r\n   Understanding of IP protocols \r\n   Experience in embedded SW design\r\n\r\nDesired skills:\r\n\r\n    Experience in continuous integration\r\n    Understanding of configuring routers, firewalls, etc. \r\n\r\nIf this like a position for you, please send us your application to careers@ruggedtooling.com\r\n\r\nRaimo Jormalainen will give more information about the position. His address is raimo.jormalainen@ruggedtooling.com.",
