				"kuvausteksti" : "Koskisen is an internationally renowned Finnish wood products specialist whose customers are, amongst others the construction, joinery and transportation industries. The company's turnover was 264 M? in 2016 and over half of the production was exported worldwide. The 1,000-strong staff are united by an uncompromising commitment to wood.\r\n\r\nTo strengthen Koskisen Oy ICT team, we are now looking for an ambitious, innovative and business oriented person to join in developing our Panel Industry ICT.\r\n\r\nThe Job\r\n\r\nAs ICT Solution Owner, Panel Industry you will join our ICT team and work as owner of Panel Industry ICT development portfolio. You will work very closely with your business colleagues to identify development opportunities, analyze them and through business co-operation prioritize and roadmap the items. You will also lead development projects and manage some external project managers in your field. You will be reporting to ICT Manager of Koskisen Oy.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, we expect that you will:\r\n\r\nBe the ICT representative in Panel Industry management team.\r\nBe a key person in the ICT management team and drive continuous development and project management practices.\r\nLearn Panel Industry operative processes so that you can drive and support process excellence and optimization.\r\nIdentify and develop digital opportunities to enable business growth and development\r\nWork in close co-operation with our end customers\r\n Profile\r\n\r\nWe expect that you have an IT relevant education with some work experience within application management, digitalization and process excellence. Even more important is your ambition for development and attitude for getting things done. You love to work with people/team and you rather propose solutions than raise up problems.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, you have/are:\r\n\r\nPractical experience of managing projects\r\nDedicated drive for application and process development\r\nExperience in vendor management\r\nProven skills with process optimization using e.g. lean and/or six sigma-methods\r\nGood written and spoken Finnish & English\r\n\r\nWe Offer\r\n\r\nWe offer you a challenging position in international company. Possibility to affect directly in our success by value creating solutions of digitalization. Opportunities to self-develop your professional skills in the field of ICT and forest industry.\r\n\r\nMore information: IT Manager Teemu Similä 16.11.2017 klo 13.00 - 16.00\r\n\r\napplication by 20th November via this link",
