				"kuvausteksti" : "Job title:  Channel Sales Coordinator\r\n\r\nMain Responsibilities:\r\n- Coordinating and directing efforts across company sales teams and across Nordic business groups.\r\n- Following up the work guidance and policy of the headquarter from China\r\n- Providing support to the Nordic sales team\r\n- Assisting in the implementation of telecom operator sales business and and improving high & mid-level customer relationships\r\n- Acquiring and analyzing operators' requirement information. Assisting in the formulation and execution of market business plans\r\n- Participating in promoting brand image in key operator channel\r\n- Assisting in building successful win-win business with key telecom operators\r\n \r\nRequirements:\r\n- University or Bachelor's degree in major of telecommunication\r\n- At least 3 years telecom device sales experiences in the industry\r\n- Familiarity with mobile telecommunication terminal area, including product knowledge, marketing and branding business knowledge and so on\r\n- Fluent English and Chinese communication skills and able to work in a multinational team",
