				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you interested about online services, cryptocurrencies or writing? \r\n\r\nWe are looking for students to do their internship. The work will be done mostly with computer. Main task is writing/searching informative content about cryptocurrencies.\r\n\r\nIf we find you as a good and efficient writer, we could reward you with a reasonable student compensation. You can work anywhere. We can also offer you a working desk in our small office in Kamppi. The team in our company is very easy-going. You don't need to worry about wearing a fancy business suit or dress. We only care about your passion to learn and  work.\r\n\r\nIf you have a group of fellow students who are interested in cryptocurrencies, we can arrange you a mutual internship interview. Working in a good team is important for us.\r\n\r\nIf the internship goes well we are open to discuss about the future. We guarantee that during the internship you will learn a lot about online services and cryptocurrencies.\r\n\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\nInterested in cryptocurrencies\r\nGood / Excellent English literacy\r\nUnderstanding of Search Engine Optimization (SEO) in creating website content\r\nBasic computing skills\r\nGood attitude\r\n\r\nIt's a big plus if you have experience in using MediaWiki platform.",
