				"kuvausteksti" : "Keysight's Nemo solutions provide testing, measurement, optimization, and analytics systems to the global wireless market based on its specialist sector knowledge and proprietary software and hardware products. Customers include major manufacturers of mobile devices, chipsets, and network equipment, mobile network operators, regulatory authorities, and independent test houses.\r\n\r\nKeysight Nemo solutions Oulu is looking for a Windows SW Developer\r\n\r\nAs an experienced Windows software developer you will be responsible for comprehensive software development of our Windows client-server applications with the opportunity to use the latest technologies of the software industry. Development of our data analytics solutions with big-data on Windows environment makes it possible for you to create something new all the time and become an expert in the field. We expect strong skills in software design, and in addition you have the ability to design innovative, technologically advanced, and reusable software solutions.\r\n\r\nJob Qualifications\r\nTo succeed in this job, we are looking for a candidate with the following qualifications/skills:\r\n\r\n-MSc/BSc degree in Computer Science, Engineering or relevant field\r\n\r\n-Proven work experience as a Windows Software Developer and experience designing interactive applications and data driven systems\r\n\r\n-Ability to develop software in C#, C++ or other programming languages on Windows environment with good knowledge of databases and SQL\r\n\r\n-Good understanding of cellular networks\r\n\r\n-Strong troubleshooting and debugging -skills on Windows environment and ability to execute full software development life cycle\r\n\r\n-Clearly and regularly communicate with management and technical support colleagues",
