				"kuvausteksti" : "Tosibox was born from the idea that secure remote access doesn't have to be complicated, expensive or time-consuming. Today our Plug & Go technology is patented and internationally awarded. Our products are used in more than 110 countries and our sales organization now covers Europe, the Far East, Oceania and North America. Our products are manufactured in Finland and our headquarters is located in Oulu. Our turnover was over EUR 2.2 million in 2016, with increasing growth rate during 2017.\r\n\r\nTosibox invests heavily in research and development and we are looking for experienced and innovative\r\n\r\nSOFTWARE ENGINEER\r\n\r\nto reinforce our R&D team. We seek for candidates with broad knowledge and who are eager to learn and contribute to all the areas and phases of product development. We want people with solution oriented and proactive mindset.\r\n\r\nWe expect from you:\r\n- Good skills in one of the following: Qt, C++, C, Java (no need to master them all)\r\n- Knowledge of basic networking protocols: IP, TCP, UDP etc.\r\n- Experience from Linux OS, Linux routers, or firewalls\r\n- Fluent written and oral English skills\r\n\r\nIn addition, we value:\r\n- Knowledge of SQL or NoSQL databases\r\n- Experience from the following: git, scrum, OS X, Android, iOS, distributed databases, OpenWrt\r\n- Knowledge of VPN connection technologies, cryptographic applications and information security in general\r\n- Experience from participating in open source projects\r\n\r\nWe offer you an exciting place in a rapidly growing company, with lots of diversity, possibilities to influence and to see the results of your work benefiting the customers directly. The job location is preferably at our headquarters at Technopolis Linnanmaa campus in Oulu, or at our Helsinki office, but we do welcome also applications from outside these areas.\r\n\r\nPlease send your CV and application with your salary request to jari.tenhunen@tosibox.com. For more information, please contact jari.tenhunen@tosibox.com or +358 (0)50 486 9479.",
