				"kuvausteksti" : "As our eager and experienced Inside Sales Representative, you will join our sales team and grow our business in Finland. You will take the full ownership over our small in-bound leads and generate new sales. You will also nurture and manage these accounts, adding value to our customers, ensuring high retention and upsales. \r\n\r\nYour responsibilities will include\r\n\r\n- Processing inbound SME leads and generating new sales\r\n- Managing your own Client base securing high retention\r\n- Upselling to named existing clients\r\n- Sales pipeline management in our company's CRM system\r\n- Reporting accurate Sales forecasts\r\n- Participating events - representing HON service (CX and HR)\r\n- Campaign arrangements and follow-ups, potentially booking etc.\r\n- Topical and seasonal e-mail and calling campaigns\r\n\r\nAs our ideal candidate you will have\r\n\r\n- Several years experience in successful sales positions\r\n- Ability to prioritize the workload and focus on the essentials in meeting your personal sales targets\r\n- Proactive approach to focusing time on the right tasks\r\n- Strong social skills with a 100% team player mentality\r\n- Result oriented and entrepreneurial attitude\r\n- Willingness to travel within Finland\r\n- Solid computer skills (Excel, invoicing systems, CRMs, etc.)\r\n- Finnish and English language proficiency in order to communicate fluently with with our local customer and  international team efficiently\r\n\r\nThe following is considered as an advantage: SaaS experience.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat we offer: \r\n\r\nOur work environment is open, energetic, multicultural, flexible, and positive. We have a significant international client base and a large reseller network all over the world. Joining our happy team means becoming part of the company behind the globally recognized 4 Smileys whose mission is to make people happier - one Smiley at a time.\r\n\r\n--\r\n\r\nAbout us\r\n\r\nHappyOrNot® is the global leader in instant customer and employee satisfaction reporting. Our innovative feedback collecting Smileys and intelligent data analytics Reporting Service help our clients to improve their customer experience, relationships, and employee engagement. We serve nearly 4,000 companies across 117 countries and have collected and reported on over a half billion feedbacks.\r\n\r\nP.S: don't forget to check us out on our website and social media!",
