				"kuvausteksti" : "Junior B2B Project Manager, German market\n\nManagement Events is an innovative growth company that connects executive decision makers around the world at high quality events. Management Events Group has +250 employees and is active in more than 10 countries. www.managementevents.com\n\nWe are looking for a sales-minded Junior Project Manager to join our German team working for the delegate acquisition of our B2B invitation only events. Your location of work could be one of our offices in Helsinki, Stockholm, Amsterdam or Berlin. This position is a great opportunity for learning various set of skill, e.g. sales skills, which are very valuable assets in the work life. \n\nIn this position you are contacting top executives from the biggest companies in Germany. You invite and commit these executives to our high-class events in these countries, research their business interests and investment needs. You provide the executives a chance to come to the event for networking with similar business leaders, hear interesting content and possible solutions for their investment needs. You would also commit some of the executives to take an active part as speakers at the event. This job requires fluent German and working knowledge of English as well as good communication over the phone and email. High energy and a drive to surpass oneself is important to succeed in this role.\n\nWhy choose a career at Management Events?\n\n- Get to work with a unique business concept and influence to your own earning level!\n- Be a part of the culture where we enjoy spending time together and work together towards our targets\n- We offer a well-organized On-Boarding process run by our experienced trainers at the start of your employment. We also provide you with continuous training and self-development opportunities on your ME career path.\n- Join the international growth organization with plenty of opportunities: What's it like to work at Management Events? https://www.facebook.com/managementevents/videos/1154662604546810/\n\nWe would love to hear more about your aspirations and what makes you as a successful Junior Project Manager! Please apply by sending your CV, cover letter and salary request in English.\n\nhttp://managementevents.com/jobs/oECB2fwD/?s=FI_MOL",
