				"kuvausteksti" : "Neste Jacobs is unique. We have 60 years of industry-leading experience of innovating, designing, engineering, constructing, starting up, operating, optimizing and maintaining the world's most competitive industrial plants. Neste Jacobs' vision is to be the preferred solution provider for hydrocarbon and bio-industries with the mission of delivering Excellence in Engineering. To fulfill our vision and mission we continuously seek out and work to retain leading professionals from around the world.\n\nPlease consider joining us!\n\nWe are now looking for\n\nProject Engineer\n\nto technology and investment projects, project planning and management in our Project Control function.\n\nPriority tasks include:\n\nCost estimation\nCost follow-up and control, data analysis\nProject reporting\nProject schedule planning, preparation and follow-up\nProgress reporting for engineering, procurement and construction\nDevelopment of reporting and planning tools\nWe are looking for a person with good interpersonal skills and the ability to collaborate with different parties. Working in a multi-project environment requires good organization, prioritization and time management skills. We expect oral and written English skills. Finnish language is an advantage. \n\nPosition is suitable for a person with a Master's or Bachelor's degree. We value the experience in industrial investment projects (e.g. project management, engineering, procurement, site operations, financial reporting). Economical know-how is considered an advantage. We also hope that you have willingness to travel, the possibility to relocate internationally is also considered an advantage.\n\nWe offer you an interesting position in a versatile working environment with a good view in industrial investment projects at home and abroad. You have an opportunity to participate in the development and implementation of project planning and its tools in an evolving company.\n\nThe position is located in Kilpilahti industrial area in Porvoo, Finland. The person selected must pass a health examination including a drug test. Security clearance is obtained for the person with their consent.",
