				"kuvausteksti" : "Citec is expanding its engineering activities to the minerals and metals industry. We are now looking for a skilled Chief Civil Engineer to work for us in the Helsinki area. As a Chief Civil Engineer, you will be managing the structural design scope and lead the structural design team within the projects.\n\nWe are looking for an enthusiastic, customer oriented person with experience in leading engineering projects, who is ready to be part of growing business and developing the relationship with our valued customer.\n\nMain responsibilities:\n\n-Leading the scope of civil engineering of our multi-discipline engineering projects\n- Acting as Senior Structural Engineer in domestic and international projects\n- Securing that the customer requirements are met in the projects\n- Leading the civil project team to success\n- Providing technical support in the sales phase\n- Acting as the main contact within own area towards the customer\n- Cooperation with other disciplines and within the project team\n\nQualifications:\n\n- B.Sc. of M.Sc. in Civil/Construction Engineering\n- Strong experience (10 years) and track record in structural engineering projects\n- Experience in minerals and metals industry\n- Experience in modern 3D design tools\n- A- or AA- FISE qualification within structural engineering is seen as a benefit, but not necessary\n- Experience in technical leadership is seen as a benefit\n- Good communication skills in Finnish and English\n- Customer focused and proactive way of working\n\nWe offer you:\n\n- Interesting and challenging work in both domestic and international projects\n- International and flexible work environment in a growing company\n- Skilled colleagues and friendly atmosphere\n\nWould you like to join our team of professionals? For more information please contact Head of Civil Engineering, Joakim Ingves +358 50 322 3126. Read more and apply via www.citec.com/careers, Citec needs your expertise!",
