				"kuvausteksti" : "Citec is expanding its engineering activities in the minerals and metals industry. We are now looking for skilled Chief Piping & Layout Engineers to work for us in Helsinki area. As a Chief Piping & Layout Engineer, you will be managing the piping and layout design scope and lead the piping team within the projects.\n\nWe are looking for an enthusiastic, customer oriented person with experience in leading engineering projects, who is ready to be part of growing business and developing the relationship with our valued customers.\n\nMain responsibilities:\n\n-Steering and controlling the piping and layout design\n-Ensuring fulfilment of design standards, instructions, time schedule, cost-effectiveness and best practices for the given design tasks\n-Ensuring that the customer requirements are met in the projects\n-Leading the piping & layout design team to successful project\n-Providing technical support in the sales phase\n-Acting as the main contact within own discipline towards the customer\n-Coordination and cooperation with other disciplines' project teams\n\nQualifications:\n\n-B.Sc. or M.Sc. in Mechanical Engineering\n-At least 8 years of work experience\n-Hands on experience in layout, piping & support design and understanding of pipe stress calculations\n-Experience in modern 3D design tools such as PDMS, E3D, SP3D\n-Experience in minerals & metals industry\n-Project leading skills\n-Good communication skills in Finnish and English\n-Capability to lead people including good communication skills, team-spirit and driving attitude\n\nWe offer you:\n\n-Interesting and challenging work in both domestic and international projects\n-International and flexible working environment in a growing company\n-Skilled colleagues and friendly atmosphere\n\nWould you like to join our team of professionals? For more information, please contact Head of Plant Engineering, Jari Hänninen +35850 3181 028. Read more and apply via www.citec.com/careers, Citec needs your expertise!",
