				"kuvausteksti" : "Citec is expanding its engineering activities in the minerals and metals industry. We are now looking for a skilled multi-discipline Project Manager to be located in Helsinki area.\n\nAs a Project Manager, you will take the main responsibility in managing multi-discipline projects, lead the people in project teams and participate in sales activities. To succeed in this role, you need to be confident in making own decisions and an excellent communicator with proactive and self-driven way of working.\n\nWe are looking for an enthusiastic person with experience in leading engineering projects, who is ready to be part of growing business and developing the relationship with our valued customers.\n\nMain responsibilities:\n\n-Managing multi-discipline engineering projects\n-Participating in sales and offering stages of projects, active engagement in customer relationship\n-Ensuring that the customer requirements are met in the projects\n-Capability to lead people including good communication skills, team-spirit and driving attitude\n\nQualifications:\n\n-A minimum of 10 years' experience of engineering projects or/and project management\n-B.Sc or M.Sc in mechanical, structural or process engineering\n-Experience in minerals and metals industry\n-Excellent communication, negotiation and leadership skills\n-Determined and goal-oriented way of working\n-Good communication skills in Finnish and English\n-Capability to lead people including good communication skills, team-spirit and driving attitude\n\nWe offer you:\n\n-Interesting and challenging work in international projects\n-Possibility to work in a team of project management professionals\n-Flexible working environment\n\nWould you like to join our team? For more information please contact Head of Project Management Antti Hahtala +358 40 0647 959. Read more and apply at www.citec.com/careers, Citec needs your expertise!",
