				"kuvausteksti" : "Citec is expanding its engineering and documentation activities in the minerals and metals industry. We are now looking for skilled Document Controllers to work for us in the Helsinki area. As a Document Controller, you will be managing the project document flow between the customer company and customer's client and/or with vendors.\n\nWe are looking for an enthusiastic, customer oriented persons, who are ready to be part of growing business and developing the relationship with our valued customer.\n\nMain tasks include:\n\n-Managing the project document flow between the customer company and customer's client and/or with vendors according to the contract document schedule.\n-Determining the documentation requirements and preparing documentation instructions for the project and vendors.\n-Supporting projects and vendors in document management and publication\n-Archiving and delivering the project documents in the end of the project\n\nQualifications for the job:\n\n-M.Sc or B.Sc,or equivalent skills\n-Excellent communication skills in spoken and written Finnish and English\n-At least 3-5 years of experience of project document control\n-Experience in minerals and metals industry is seen as a benefit\n-Customer oriented and systematic way of working\n\nFor more information, please contact Sonja Ahonen, Head, Information Services +358 50 4283 809. Read more and apply via www.citec.com/careers , Citec needs your expertise!",
