				"kuvausteksti" : "N-PRO Resources Oy Ltd is a staffing and recruiting company belonging to Nipromec Group focusing mainly on needs of our customers in the fields of energy, industry and offshore.\n\nWe are now looking for Shift Assistants (5 positions) for our client in Olkiluoto. Work starts 01.11.2017 and estimated duration is 12 months.\n\nMain tasks:\n-Perform all administrative work in the main control room and in the PTW office.\n-Perform administrative activities in CMS.\n-Work order, permit to test and blocking print out and distribution.\n-Storage of work order, permit to tests and blocking list printouts.\n-Receiving back work orders and permits to test from supervisors and commissioning engineers.\n-Preparation of tags for blockings.\n-Transfer of blocking results to CMS.\n-Give out and receive back of room and cabinet keys.\n\nGeneral and technical background expected:\n-Formation in all secretarial works.\n-Experience with technical documentation.\n-Fluent in English and Finnish required.\n\nSkills required\n-MS Office.\n-CMS if possible.\n\nTechnical\n-Basic knowledge of the EPR technology is a plus but not mandatory.\n\nThe work will be performed in shifts.\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For more information please go to www.n-pro.fi",
