				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are looking for Electrical and I&C PTW Officers (4 positions) for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration is until 31.12.2018.\n\nTasks:\n-Technical clarification of work orders / permit to test and creation validation of blocking / simulation.\n-Execution of blockings and simulations.\n-Oversee in field operator teams for establishing safe work conditions (equipment alignment, depressurizing, de-energizing, locking and tagging).\n-Coordinate activities with operating, construction, installation and commissioning units.\n-Prepare permit to work documentation and ensure strict compliance.\n\nExpected deliverable:\n-Validated work orders and blockings.\n-Carried out blockings.\n-Work programs.\n\nSkills required:\n-Electrical or I&C engineering degree, or experienced technician.\n-At least 5 years of experience in nuclear power plants. \n-At least 5 years of experience with work orders and blockings as requestor and for clarification.\n-Detailed knowledge about the electrical and I&C documentation.\n-Ability to work on the different process diagrams, isometrics, preparation of solution and support for inventories in the field.\n-General understanding of mechanics, thermodynamics, fluid mechanics and measurement / instrumentation technology.\n-General understanding in electrical technology.\n-Ability to use the different project data bases, software etc.\n-MS Office knowledge.\n-Knowledge about the EPR technology.\n-Working experience with permit to work offices.\n-Fluent English, both written and spoken. Ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus.\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi. For further information please go to www.nipromec.com.",
