				"kuvausteksti" : "Lapland Welcome is a famous program service company in Lapland. We offer services all over Lapland and our head quarters is in Rovaniemi. \r\n\r\nWe are now looking for snowmobile safari guides in Kemi. The work consists of different wilderness safaris and snowmobile safaris in Kemi and Katkavaara area. English language, good car driving skills and basic maintenance skills are needed for this work. We will organize training for this work.\r\n\r\nWelcome to our international team!",
