				"kuvausteksti" : "Do you want to join us and write the next chapter of luxury hotels?\r\n\r\nHotel St. George, Helsinki challenges the world, manners and attitudes of hos-pitality. It also challenges the word of luxury.\r\n\r\nSt. George will be a hotel, with a strong, distinguish concept, which requires a deep motivation from the managers and employees. It is about combining the city and the hotel as a one experience, turning them together to a destination. Creating memorable customer journey needs to have a deeper meaning. The curiosity and passion for people, tolerance and understanding of cultural differ-ences need to be naturally genuine. Culture, art, gastronomy, life with all forms, something to feel a desire to.\r\n\r\nJoin the team in creating the Hotel St. George food experiences.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for passionate professionals from managers and chefs to waiters and sommeliers to join our F&B team.\r\n\r\nRestaurant Andrea will open its doors at the beginning of next year at Lö-nnrotinkatu 4. Hotel St. George and Restaurant Andrea will offer food experi-ences together and individually, as separate concepts. Restaurant Andrea will be more than a hotel restaurant. Its concept will be created by Mehmet Gürs to-gether with Antto Melasniemi.\r\n\r\nMehmet Gürs is one of the super stars of Turkish restaurant world. Antto Me-lasniemi is a food visionary and a Helsinki restaurateur. A great duo.\r\n\r\nRestaurant Andrea believes in fun rather than fine dining. Wintergarden Bar and St. George Bakery will expand the food experiences at Hotel St. George to new dimensions.\r\n\r\nWe invite you to send us your application and CV through the link below by November 30th, 2017 at the latest. Tell us who you are and what motivates you!\r\n\r\nSt. George, Moments are More",
