				"kuvausteksti" : "Megaklinikka is a growing international healthcare service company. Our unique and innovative ERP system is used at our dental clinic in Helsinki, as well as by our customers in Sweden and several Finnish municipalities. Megaklinikka is part of Panostaja Oyj.\nWe are looking for a Senior Software Engineer to revolutionize healthcare processes. You will be part of an agile software development team, with a mission to improve healthcare in Finland and internationally.\n\nWe offer you challenges and opportunities in creating new information systems and processes for healthcare, and you have the opportunity to develop yourself as well as the whole healthcare industry. Our work culture is flexible and hands-on; we like to move fast and avoid unnecessary bureaucracy. Your workplace is located in the center of Helsinki.\n\nWe require the following:\n- Excellent Java programming skills, preferably at least three years of professional experience.\n- Excellent knowledge of modern Java frameworks and libraries, especially Hibernate.\n- Experience of several other programming languages, like Python, Scala, PHP, JS and TypeScript.\n- Experience of designing complex and distributed software architectures\n- Excellent problem solving and debugging skills\n- Comprehensive SQL skills\n- Excellent spoken and written English skills\n- Great team work skills as well as determination and proactivity to develop the best software as well as your own skills\n\nWe appreciate:\n- Web development skills\n- PostgreSQL and web server configuration and administration skills\n- Knowledge of CI and DevOps tools, experience of setting up CI pipelines\n- Experience of major systems integration projects\n- Solid unit testing experience\n\nSend your application along with a salary request as soon as possible to hr@megaklinikka.fi. The position will be filled when a suitable candidate is found.\n\nMore information about the position is given by Head of Product Development Ossi Ottka, 044 013 7024.",
