				"kuvausteksti" : "Mechanical Engineers\n\nWould you like to be part of a team in one of the most innovative and globally oriented automation companies in the field of automated robotic solutions for intralogistics? A growing number of large and technically challenging projects have given us the opportunity to strengthen our engineering department. We are looking for ambitious mechanical engineers with experience in the automation industry and competence in strength calculation. You will be working at our headquarters in Ulvila.\n\nKey responsibilities\nAs a mechanical engineer, you will\n\n- Be part of the engineering team \n- Manage versatile 3D mechanical engineering tasks, especially delivery planning\n- Be responsible for completing the engineering as scheduled, reviewing and verifying it according to process and project requirements\n- Manage cost effective design, taking durability and safety into account\n- Participate in making Cimcorp stand out through high quality engineering\n\nSkills, education,and experience\nWe expect you to have\n\n- Technical education and knowledge\n- Strength calculation skills\n- Knowledge of manufacturing technology\n- Teamwork skills\n- Problem-solving skills, persistence and ability to make decisions\n- Ability to function and co-operate in different environments and situations\n- Fluent Finnish and English, especially written. Other language skills are an advantage \n\nWe offer\nIn our team you will have an opportunity to grow in international projects and work with passionate people. We offer extensive employee benefits and additional education and training. We strive to create an innovative and collaborative working culture where good performance is recognized.",
