				"kuvausteksti" : "Areva OL3 IT Team is looking for a spare part Engineer/ Technician\n\nJob description: \n\n- Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time\n- Review and search for items in warehouse inventories \n- Generate purchase requests and technical requisition files\n- Follow-up of the purchase requests and purchase orders \n- Coordinate the required inspections of the spare parts \n- Generate issue notes to receive parts from the warehouse \n- Provide the documentation of the spare parts for maintenance reports and other work orders \n- Prepare the pick-up and handover of required spare parts \n\nCandidate profile: \n- Experience with specifications and design documents (construction plans) are favorable. Exposure to facets of either maintenance, commissioning quality, warehousing, procurement, or spare parts is mandatory. \n- Engineering degree/diploma with an emphasis on Mechanical Engineering (or similar) or experienced technician with an Mechanical or Electromechanical background.\n- Understanding or technical documentation for power plant components\n- General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology\n- Computer literacy in MS-Office\n- Good communication skills \n\n\nJoin us to experience something new! We can offer you challenging and interesting tasks, competitive salary, good team and the possibility to work in a truly international company.",
