				"kuvausteksti" : "We are now looking for an EXECUTIVE ASSISTANT to work in a game-based learningstartup in Tampere. In this position you get the opportunity to work in a young, flat organization with geeky but fun teammates.\n\nAs Executive Assistant you are the anchor to the executive team, working independently ensuring no balls are dropped and that the leadership team works efficiently. The position is full-time and permanent and will be filled once the right candidate is found.\n\nWe hope you are:\n\nYou are passionate about working as an Executive Assistant in a fast paced and changing environment. You have excellent organizational skills, ability to multi-task and prioritize. \n\nWe are looking for an independent and fast learning person with a can-do attitude and effective working style. The ideal candidate has excellent interpersonal communication skills and high attention to detail. Your spoken and written English is fluent. \n\nBasic working tools such as Google Apps and Microsoft Office are familiar to you. Your education background should include studies in business administration or similar.\n\nYour job includes:\n\nAs an Executive Assistant you work as the right hand for the executive team and the CEO. You are proactively planning and coordinating the work as well as managing the calendar and schedule changes. Your job includes preparing materials and presentations, making meeting minutes, coordinating travel arrangements and supporting in various running tasks and projects. You are actively communicating with both internal and external stakeholders and act as the first point of contact for the CEO. You have the possibility to travel and spend time with the team over breakfasts and sports events.\n\nIf you became interested, apply today by sending an email to mikael@teachergaming.com\nand include a CV. Feel free to ask any questions via email or phone (+358 40 7289 428).\n\nCheers,\nMikael Uusi-Mäkelä\nCOO @ TeacherGaming",
