				"kuvausteksti" : "Virta is the innovation leader in electric mobility charging IT-business systems. Based in Helsinki, Finland Virta enables B2B-vendors and B2C-vendors to make business from electric vehicle charging services with comprehensive end-to-end cloud-based and open interfaced IT service solutions. Service solution can easily adapted for different branding. Virta provides a modular scalable turn-key solution for EV charging networks. It enables roaming between networks and enable different business models from crowdsourcing of EV-charging to utility-driven EV infrastructure management.  The Virta customers are owners of charging stations, retailers of charging services, energy utilities and also any organisation that wants to provide commercial charging services to electric vehicle users. See more at www.virta.global/ \n\nWe are now strengthening our team with several positions\nLEAD & SENIOR DEVELOPERS\n\nWe offer you an interesting chance to utilize all your creativity and develop many new things among the first companies in the world.  You are a key person designing and developing our business through technology. You are developing further the digitalization and automation of our systems to provide better service to our clients and grow our business. Together with our team and partners, you are implementing our software solutions with a hands on approach. Guiding junior developers and helping them to grow professionally forms part of your duties. \n\nTo boost our growth and development further we have several opportunities open such as\n\nFullstack Software Developer\n\n-You are jack of all trades when it comes to development - focusing on both back end and front end development or our systems (e.g. SaaS, CRM etc). Background from e.g. PHP, Node JS, html, javascript, css, web technology libraries.\n\nInfrastructure and Server Specialist\n\n-You are taking care of server configurations, databases, APIs, business logic. Background from Servers, Cloud, AWS and infrastructure technologies etc.\n\nMobile Application Developer\n\n-You are taking care of our mobile application design and development actions and tasks. Background from mobile software development on iOS and Android.\n\nWe expect you to have wide experience from some of the substance areas mentioned above through different ICT development projects. You have experience from developing solutions with various technologies and methods (programming languages, architectures etc) but more importantly, you are open minded towards diverse approaches.  You are fluent in English. Finnish is not mandatory. If you find yourself in some of the positions above, but are not yet a well experienced, we might have an opportunity for you as well.\n\nWe have an innovative startup company mentality, an excellent working environment and very open and positive culture. The colleagues and stakeholders are some of the best experts in the world in this area and fun to work with. We are flexible and result oriented, not office oriented. Today our development team is located in Helsinki and Tampere. Even though we are a quickly growing startup company, we have a very solid financial situation.\n\nInterested? Please send your application together with your cv and salary request via https://www.mercuriurval.com/en-fi/Opportunity/?jobadid=50153, reference number FI-11463. The positions will be filled when the right candidates are found, so apply soon.  For more information, please contact Esko Oja tel. +358 207 420 535 Mika Mäkelä +358 207 420 521 at Mercuri Urval.",
