				"kuvausteksti" : "Dekati Ltd. is one of the world's leading manufacturers of instrumentation for fine particle detection. For over 20 years, Dekati has provided measurement solutions globally for environmental air quality monitoring, research institutes, automotive industry, energy production sector and nanotechnology companies. More than 95% of Dekati customers are located outside of Finland where Dekati sales is organised via global distribution network. The biggest markets for Dekati products are currently in China, Japan, Europe and North America. \r\n\r\nWe are looking for a Technical Sales Engineer for our Client Dekati Ltd. The position is based in Kangasala, Finland, and provides an exciting opportunity to work in an international business environment. This position gives you an excellent place to view the development of cutting-edge environmental technology solutions.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities \r\n\r\n- support sales channel partners in both technical and sales related activities for the assigned products\r\n- support our global sales network locally in their countries both in pre-sales activities and instrument installations\r\n- participate in relevant scientific conferences, symposiums and meetings\r\n- create and maintain technical and sales product documentation\r\n\r\nYou will succeed in this position if you have\r\n\r\n- an appropriate technical or commercial degree (B.Sc or higher)\r\n- understanding of and interest in science, technology and high-tech products\r\n- B2B sales experience preferably in an international industrial business environment\r\n- willingness to travel globally\r\n- excellent written and spoken communication skills in English. Other language skills are considered as an advantage\r\n\r\n \r\nWe expect you to have business-oriented mindset, customer-focused and proactive attitude and excellent communication skills. \r\n\r\n\r\nWe offer you\r\n\r\nA full-time position in an international and growing technology business where you will have interesting and variable projects in diverse business environment. We offer a great opportunity for personal and professional development in product management, sales and sales channel development. You will have devoted, supportive and experienced team to work with and you will have good training/introduction in the beginning.",
