				"etatyo" : false,
				"kuvausteksti" : "We are looking for you HR professional with a solid command both in Finnish and English as an HR Administrator to join our HR Finland team.\n\nYour main responsibilities will be:\n\n- Taking care widely of employment related tasks during the whole employment life cycle\n- Supporting managers and employees in employment related tasks and questions\n- Working together with our payroll supplier\n- Maintaining and updating HR data to HR systems\n- Working as an employment task specialist in HR community\n\nWe expect You to have/are:\n\n- Strong experience in HR admin area\n- Experience about using HR systems\n- Process and result oriented\n- Agile learner\n- Flexible\n- Positive to changes\n- Team player as well as comfortable with independent working\n\nKnowledge about labour laws, collective agreements and key HR frameworks, processes, tools and practices.\nFluent Finnish and English\n\nFor more information about the position, please contact our partner in recruitments Barona, Senior Consultant Janne Laaksola, 050-467 2652.\n\nTieto is the leading IT service company in Northern Europe providing IT and product engineering services. Our highly specialized IT solutions and services complemented by a strong technology platform create tangible business benefits for our local and global customers. As a trusted transformation partner, we are close to our customers and understand their unique needs. With about 14 000 experts, we aim to become a leading service integrator creating the best service experience in IT.",
