				"kuvausteksti" : "Experis is the global leader in professional resourcing and project based workforce solutions. We attract, assess and place specialist professional talent, connecting the passion of individuals with the ambition of business. We specialize in providing professional opportunities across IT and Engineering, Finance and Accounting, Sales, Marketing, Communications and HR. We deliver high-demand talent for mission-critical positions to clients in over 50 countries. Experis is part of ManpowerGroup, the world leader in innovative workforce solutions.\n\n\nOur customer is an international ICT Company located in Espoo. We are now searching Change Management & Communications Lead to our customers 6 month project, start date ASAP. Contract is a fixed term contract via ManpowerGroup.\n\nMain tasks:\n\n  - Communications / Business Change Management planning and approach\n  - Stakeholder analysis and stakeholder management\n  - Coordination of communication and business change management activities on all levels of the organization\n  - Alignment with other communications / business change management activities ongoing in the organization\n  - Business change management / communications material creation\n  - Information session planning and execution\n  - Training / info session material creation\n  - Training / info session administration\n\nDesired experience:\n\n  - BCM / communications work experience or relevant education\n  - Program / project management and stakeholder management\n  - Ability to understand concepts and big picture\n  - Understanding / experience of change and people's response to change\n  - Experience of driving ways of working and mind set changes through organizations\n  - Excellent writing skills\n  - Hands-on worker with a can-do attitude\n\nIf you are interested, please apply at www.experis.fi with your CV and salary request ASAP.\n\nFor more information, please contact Senior Consultant Petteri Paassola, 040 17 55 818 or petteri.paassola@fi.experis.com",
