				"kuvausteksti" : "Areva OL3 IT Team is looking for additional Spare Part Team Support. \n\nJob description: \n\n- Assess maintenance and commissioning data to initiate spare parts and consumable orders in due time.\n- Review and search for items in warehouse inventories \n- Search for technical/ quality documentation in databases / folders \n- Follow-up of the purchase requests and purchase orders \n- Provide the documentation if the spare parts for maintenance reports and other work orders \n\nCandidate profile: \n\nGeneral and technical background expected: \n- Understanding of technical documentation\n- General understanding of mechanical, electrical and instrumentation technology\n- Computer literacy in MS-Office\n- Management of all usual software (Excel, Work, Powerpoint, Outlook)\n- Languages: Fluent in English (written and spoken), French/ German or Finnish is seen as a plus \n\nRequired consent as foreseen: \nTo work in controlled area (radiation protection): No \nTo work in shift/rotation: No\n\nJoin us to experience something new! We can offer you challenging and interesting tasks, competitive salary, good team and the possibility to work in a truly international company.",
