				"kuvausteksti" : "Are you looking for an opportunity to grow your expertise in web developing in a prestigious company? Do you have some previous experience from work or your own projects? We are looking for a .NET developer to work full time in our client's long-term project. In this position you get to work in part of a great team and in close contact with clients. If this sounds interesting to you, don't waste any time and apply right away!\n\nABOUT THE ROLE\n\nAcademic Work is looking for a .NET developer to our client company.\n\nThis job is a staffing position, which means that you will be employed by Academic Work and work as a consultant at our client company.\n\nJOB DUTIES\n\nOur client is looking for someone to work in their long-term project which will last up to 2 years. The job will be .NET developing in a large team including experienced co-workers and you will have a great opportunity to grow your own knowledge. Your tasks will be determined based on your experience and skills. In the team you will have both English and Finnish speaking colleagues and you will also be in a close contact with clients. In this position you get to work with the most modern technologies and tools in the industry.\n\nThe position suits you who would like to commit for more long term position and get experience in working in one of the leading companies in the industry.\n\nTechnologies used in the team: C#, VB, ASP.NET.\n\nWE ARE LOOKING FOR\n\nOur ideal candidate has a relevant academic background or is about to graduate. You have work experience in .NET developing or at least or from your own projects. Your co-operation skills are great and you communicate fluently in English. It is beneficial if you are also able to communicate in Finnish with your co-workers.\n\nApply for this position if you have:\n\n-Relevant academic background\n-.NET experience from work or your own projects\n-Great communication skills and customer oriented approach\n-Fluent English skills\n\nIt is also seen as an advantage if you have experience from financial or pension insurance or working with SAFe framework.\n\nPublished: 7.11.2017\n\nIn this position you will be employed by Academic Work and we take care of all the legal responsibilities of an employer such as salary payments, insurances and health care. It is important for us that you feel well and perform in your job. Your consultant manager will be in regular contact with you during the assignment and guides you on your career. Academic Work is an authorized staffing and recruitment agency and our employees are extremely satisfied, something that we are very proud of. We are here to help you succeed!\n\nINFORMATION ON THE APPLICATION PROCESS\n\nTo apply for the job click on \"Apply here\" below. Remember to attach your CV into your application! We only handle applications through our website but if you have questions about the position you can reach us via email in esp01@academicwork.fi. Please write the advert ID in the subject and paste the advert link in the mail. We are continuously screening and contacting candidates so make sure to send your application as soon as possible. Please notice that the advert can be removed before eventual last dates on our external advertising pages. When the advert is being removed it's either due to that the processes is finished or because we have many qualified applications and are continuing in the selection/interview phase.\n\nWe are the Home of the Young Professionals. We are experts in recruitment and staffing university students, recently graduated and professionals in the beginning of their career. You can be employed by us as a consultant in one of our client companies or be recruited directly to our client via our recruitment co-operation. You can read more about us at www.academicwork.fi.\n\nWhen employed at Academic Work you will have your own dedicated Consultant Manager, whose role is to answer your questions, support your career development and ensure you enjoy your place of work.\n\nINFORMATION ABOUT THE COMPANY\n\nOur client is a large provider of digital solutions.",
