				"kuvausteksti" : "Top graduates will get the opportunity to join \n\nThe NIBE Climate Solutions Sales Trainee Program \n\nWill YOU be one of them? \n\nWe are looking for candidates who are excited about a fast track learning opportunity in Sales and are ready to take on a great challenge. To apply you should have a bachelor's degree or equivalent and a maximum of three years of relevant working experience prior to or after graduation. Our corporate language is English and you also speak fluent Finnish. Strong Swedish skills is considered a plus. You are a team player and have strong analytical and problem-solving skills. We encourage both male and female applicants to apply. Most importantly, you are sales oriented, have a strong desire to achieve and have the courage to make a difference. If that sounds like you, come join our team! \n\nThe opportunity \n\nThe NIBE Climate Solutions JUST Program ensures a genuine introduction to sales, exposure to multiple fields, local and international training and the support of a dedicated mentor. You will be employed at NIBE Energy Systems Oy joining the sales force. You will conduct research and analyze information to support business decisions. \n\nDuring the two-year program, the candidates will meet regularly at different locations in Europe and North America for training. You will be introduced to company values, business principles, and sales strategies. During the course of the program, you will individually carry out an assignment related to sales to be presented to top management. \nThe program will start in February 2018. \nWhat we offer \n\nOnce accepted to the program, you will be a member of the NIBE Climate Solutions JUST Program and employed at one of our European sales companies from day one. You will join a company that invests in you and you will be an important part of a global network. Following successful completion of the program, you will be offered a position within sales that will continue to foster your growth and further development. If you perform well, you will get the opportunity to attain a key position. \n\nTo Apply \n\nIn this recruitment process, we are cooperating with TEMP-TEAM Finland Oy. Questions about the role or the recruitment process can be addressed to Peter Aspenholt at TEMP-TEAM Finland Oy between 13-16, peas@temp-team.fi, tel. 040 75 67 316. \n\nPlease fill in your application on www.temp-team.fi - NIBE Climate Solutions Sales Trainee Program (code 5559) as soon as possible. Please attach a CV and cover letter in English. \n\n\nNIBE is a global group that helps reduce climate footprints through intelligent energy use. By developing and producing energy-efficient indoor comfort solutions for all types of buildings, NIBE helps its customers reduce their energy consumption and environmental impact. NIBE also provides the market with components and solutions for intelligent heating and control in industry and infrastructure. \n\nFrom its beginnings in the Småland city of Markaryd more than 60 years ago, NIBE has grown into a global group with a market presence on all continents. Investments in sustainable product development and acquisitions have helped the NIBE Group expand substantially, resulting in sales of just over SEK 15 billion in 2016. Operations are conducted within three business areas - NIBE Climate Solutions, NIBE Element and NIBE Stoves - with more than 13,000 employees across the globe. NIBE has been listed under the name NIBE Industrier on Nasdaq Stockholm, Large Cap list, since 1997, with a secondary listing on the SIX Swiss Exchange since 2011.",
