				"kuvausteksti" : "Enersense is a trusted industrial software supplier. Our software development is multidisciplinary. \nWe create completely new products, integrate already existing solutions and help our clients with their development projects, both in Finland and abroad.\nAs we continue to grow, we are looking for motivated and experienced Software Developers to join our team in Saint-Petersburg, Russia. \nAs a Software Developer, you have the opportunity to develop software solutions for daily use for the biggest industrial and construction companies in Finland. \n \nRequired Experience:\n\n-At least 2 years of experience working in software development projects with the required technologies\n-Software development \n-Coding \n\nApplication programming interface (API):\n-PHP 7\n-Doctrine 2\n-Slim Framefork\n-Codeception\n-Docker\n-MySQL\n\nUser Interface (UI):\n-Javascript (ES2015/ES6)\n-React\n-Redux\n-Immutable.js\n-Webpack\n-Material design\n-HTML(5)\n-CSS(3)\n\nOther requirements:\n-Fluent English \n-Good communication skills \n-Team player\n-Open-minded attitude \n\nPlease register as a jobseeker and apply for the position through our website. \nThe post will be filled as soon as a suitable applicant is found.",
