				"kuvausteksti" : "Our HW operations have grown rapidly during this year but we are still looking for new employees to fulfill our customers' needs.\n\n\nWe are now looking for JUNIOR ELECTRONICS ENGINEERS\n\nAs Junior Electronics Engineer your main tasks consists of designing and testing electronics products in varying customer projects from concepting through productisation all the way to the manufacturing support and production testing. We are expecting you to have good communication and team working skills. You are dedicated to what you do and have customer centric attitude. We appreciate your ability to work both as a part of team and independently. You value both small and long term customer assignments equally.\n\nYou are finishing your studies or you already have a qualification from the field of electronics, preferably B.Sc. or M.Sc. level but not that much work experience. More than work experience we value your motivation. Hobbies related to electronics or software coding would be an advantage. You should be able to communicate both in Finnish and in English.\n\nIf you recognize yourself as the Junior Electronics Engineer we are looking for, please send your CV and application letter (including your salary request) to jobs.finland@sasken.com. Last date to apply is 31.12. but we'll start interviews as soon as we find potential candidates!\n\n\nSasken Finland Oy is serving domestic and global customers by designing and developing both hardware and software products for industries like telecommunication, smart devices, wearables, industrials, public safety, satellite communication and testing. Sasken Finland Oy has a hardware site in Kaustinen and a software site in Tampere. Sasken Finland is a subsidiary of Sasken Technologies Ltd.\n\nwww.sasken.fi\nwww.sasken.com\n\n\nApply now!",
