				"kuvausteksti" : "At Jeanne d'Arc Living you will be part of a dynamic and strong sales department, where your primary tasks will be maintaining and developing the Finnish market. If you got a natural talent for sales and high ambitions, where average isn't enough, you might be the one we are looking for.\n\n\nAbout the job:\n\nYour area will be Finland; currently a large market for us, but with the potential for us to growth even more. You will get at a strong organization to support you and a large worldwide sales team of colleagues to network with, giving you the time to focus on building relations and expanding sales. You will get great possibilities to plan your schedule and control your everyday life, in companionship with a great team who like to be upfront.\n\nYour primary tasks will be:\nExpansion and developing of the Finnish market\nSales process from a-z\nCustomer visit \nParticipating at fairs (Finland/Sweden)\nAnnual sales meetings at the head quarter in Denmark \nDays at your office; costumer support, SoMe marketing, administration etc.\n\n\nWe are searching for a person who knows that results are gained through a determined and dedicated effort, with focus on the possibilities rather than limitations.\n\nWe expect that you:\nHave flair for sale and talent for creating relations\nSee the big picture and can work independent\nHave an organized and out-reaching sales profile\nCan document sales experience.\nHave the winner mentality and likes sale made from relations.\nKnow how to structure your everyday.\nKnow MS office\n\n\n\n\nExperience from the business is preferred, but not a demand. The job will call for you to be solution-oriented, can keep the calm overview and can plan your own work. You will need good contact skills and follows up on tasks as natural part of your identity. \n\nWe offer:\n\nA challenging agent job with great development potential\nAmbitious and commissioned colleagues\nA company willing to adapt, with short from idea to action\nPossibility to characterize and develop your own job\nBe part of an organization in development\nSalary: Either base salary € 1550-2500 Euro + commission or 100% commision based\n\nIf you have any questions, please contact Sales and Marketing Manager Kristian Mikaelsen; +45 36932010\n\nWe want to fill in the position quick and will take interviews fluent, but we will of course wait for the right person for our team.\n\nWhen you find the job interesting, please send your motivated application to:\nHead of administration; Jørgen Jensen\nJrj@jeannedarcliving.dk\n\n\nFind more info at www.jeannedarcliving.dk",
