				"kuvausteksti" : "Promotion Point is Finland's leading sales orientated experience marketing agency - we meet customers exactly where they spend their time. The encounters take place face to face with customers. We have campaigns in cooperation with reputable companies that are well known both nationally and internationally. Read more about us on our website www.promotionpoint.fi/en. You can also find us on Facebook and Instagram.\n\nWe are looking for energetic fundraisers for WWF's fundraising campaign to work in shopping centers in the Helsinki metropolitan region.\n\nWe are looking for a person who is sales- and customer-oriented as well as has an interest in environmental and nature protection issues. We encounter customers face to face and that is why we require our employees the courage to face new people in a joyful and brisk attitude. The work will be done at a WWF branded sales stand, the location of which changes weekly.\n\nWe work in several shifts, five days a week. Employees have the opportunity to commit to full-time or part-time work. However, we require all employees to work at least two shifts per week. Work is done in pairs.\n\n\nAs an employer, we offer you the opportunity to get involved in an important fundraising campaign, joyful and motivating work environment, proper training and orientation, as well as a competitive salary.\n\nIf you feel inspired, please send your application as soon as possible and come and hear more about our work!\n\nApplications: http://promotionpoint.fi/en/work-for-us/job-application-form/\n\nCheck more about our work: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9YL1vUKyI8Y\n\n#promotionpoint #welovepromotionpoint\n\nWe are a part of #AviapolisJobs -employer community: http://tyopaikat.aviapolis.fi",
