				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are looking for an Electrical and IC PTW work planner for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration is 12 months.\n\nTasks:\n-Open point handling and management.\n-Preparation and management of COREV-1 outage.\n-Commissioning support for all electrical components.\n-Preparation of all relevant documents related to components based on project requirements (e.g. supplier review sheets).\n-Manage the interface processes (e.g. I&C, field design team, installation, commissioning etc.).\n-Participation in clarification meetings.\n-Evaluation of supplier deviations.\n\nSkills required:\n-Electrical engineer degree.\n-Overall knowledge about MV-, LV-switchgears and other electrical components.\n-Interface management to other disciplines (HVAC, process, civil, etc.)\n-Knowledge of OL3 open point management system.\n-Knowledge about power supply structure of NPP (single line diagram).\n-Fluent English, both written and spoken.\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi. For further information please go to www.nipromec.com",
