				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are looking for a Transverse Test Analysis Engineer for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration of 10 months.\n\nFunction:\nWithin OL3 project, inside Commissioning Department and under Technical Commissioning Manager's responsibility, the main duties of the Transverse Test Analysis Engineer are the following:\n-Validation of the Commissioning Documentation through the RFA (Ready For Application) process for the NSSS (Nuclear Steam Supply System) and BNI (Balance of Nuclear Island) and participation in the RFA meetings\n-Test support analysis for the NSSS and BNI\n-Preparation of the Result Record Sheets (RRS) before the commissioning tests of the motors, actuators and control valves and binary and analog measuring circuits, including the review of design changes and open points before testing, review of the RRS after testing, and issuance of the associated test reports.\n-Technical event analysis\n-Technical control of the commissioning master files.\n\nOther points:\nWorking organization:\n-Basic working organization is 5 days per week\n-Possible adaptation according to project activity (weekend work, shift work, on duty work)\nLanguage:\n-Fluent English is required\n-Ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus\n\nQualification:\n-Engineer Degree mechanical, electrical and/or I&C\n-at least 2 years field experience in nuclear power plant or preliminary period within nuclear project. Oil, Gas and Shipbuilding experience can also be considered\n-PWR technology and EPR technology knowledge would be a plus\n-System design experience would be a plus\n-MS Office knowledge, \n-Document writing capacity\n-Versatile, adaptable, rigorous, good interpersonal skills, client and result oriented, attention to detail\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For more information please go to www.nipromec.com",
