				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are now looking for an As-built documentation Electrical engineer for a project in Olkiluoto. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration until 31.12.2017.\n\nFunction:\n-Work within the team of as-built documentation for electrical entity.\n-Checking of data bases regarding correct revision and implementation of all changes in electri-cal documentation (field change requests, design change requests, open points, etc.)\n-Modification of AutoCAD and pdf drawings where necessary to get documentation in as-built state.\n-Coordination with sub-suppliers where as-builts are in scope of sub-suppliers\n-Reporting of work progress to as-built-task leader of electrical engineering.\n\nGeneral and technical background expected:\n-Experience in Electrical Engineering (especially documentation).\n-Engineer with/without Bachelor or Master in Electrical Engineering or related.\n\nSkills required:\n-Work confidently within site teams and HBO.\n-Able to express clearly verbally and in writing (English language).\n-Adapt successfully to changing situations and environments.\n-Gather information systematically to establish facts and principles.\n-Problem solving., manage time effectively and able to work to deadlines.\n-Target oriented.\n\nTechnical requirements:\n-Experienced in Electrical Engineering (e.g. cabling, transformers, electrical actuators, switch-gears, motors, UPS-systems).\n-Basic knowledge of the OL3-Project (tools, project-structure, teams and documentation).\n-Knowledge in AutoCAD, pdf-processing, MS-Office (including MS Access).\n-Knowledge in PDMS (Plant Design Management Tool - no operator skills needed).\n-Knowledge in work with data bases (required for customer's information management system).\n-Fluent English. Ability with French, German or Finnish is a plus.\n\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For any further information, you might require please go to www.nipromec.com",
