				"etatyo" : false,
				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are now looking for I&C Commissioning Engineers - TXP for a project in Olkiluoto. Work starts as soon as possible and estimated duration is 8 months.\n\nScope (including main skills):\nPlanning (preparation):\nTogether with the Process, Overall, or Architecture Commissioning Engineer:\n- Perform a review of the commissioning schedule to identify tests to be prepared\n- Identify the equipment involved in the tests and their expected status\n- Check if any interlocks which could block the test and identify measures to ensure execution of the test (simulations/scripts/temporary modifications)\n- Check plant condition at the time of the test and test boundaries, including active simulation/temporary modifications. Identify any missing or blocking signal and identify measures to ensure execution of the test (simulations/scripts/temporary modifications)\n- Plan an I&C test preparation task in the overall commissioning schedule to cover the implantation of simulations/temporary modification\n\nExecution:\n- Implement requested simulation after impact analysis on running process systems\n- Request 1/0 cards availability according to components involved in the tests to the I&C system leaders\n- Support process or overall tests according to applicable procedures under the Process, Overall, or Architecture CE supervision\n- Record any simulation change during test execution according to traceability procedures in force\n- Provide a support for logic troubleshooting whenever function tests are failing\n- Remove simulations related to test after execution\n- Assist to the preparation of the test reports including the assessment of the I&C test outcomes and by providing I&C configuration at test execution time (simulations, provisional changes, engineering changes)\n- Enforcement of the IT-Security and HSE rules including applicable PTT / PTW processes\n- Manage interfaces with Engineering and I&C system commissioning for clarification, open points and troubleshooting\n\nControl and monitoring:\n- Retrieve and review periodically (every 2 weeks) the list of implemented simulation/temporary simulation with the Process commissioning engineer for the systems in charge of to identify and removed outdated.\n- Check if the implemented simulations list is in line with simulation traceability tool\n- Inform Process, Overall, or Architecture CE in case of any deviation in simulation list/state\n- Provide inputs to progress measurement and reporting linked to his / her activities\n- Initiate corrective actions in case of deviations\n\nClosure:\nThe completion of the commissioning activities related to the entrusted activities is sanctioned by following events:\n- Simulations are removed after tests execution\n- I&C related information are provided to Process, Overall, or Architecture commissioning engineer for test report completion\n- Open points are recorded in the Open point tracking tool\n\nMain skills:\nThe TELEPERM XP product lines used on OL3 project consist of following main components.  The applicant ought to be familiar with a portion the product lines according to his / her missions on site:\n- ES 680 Engineering and Commissioning Tools\n- Web4TXP Process Engineering and Commissioning Tools\n- Tec4function tool\n- OM 690 Operating and Monitoring System\n- AS 6208 (FUM) Automation System including communication modules\n- OS 670 Diagnosis system\n- Bus systems including Industrial Ethernet and Profibus DP fieldbus\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For any further information, you might require please go to www.nipromec.com",
