				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n\nWe are looking for a Commissioning Technician HVAC systems for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible estimated duration of 12 months.\n\nFunction:\nCommissioning Technician HVAC systems tasks:\n-Coordinate commissioning interfaces on the field (which other disciplines/systems, electrical, I&C, vendors, etc.) for assigned tasks.\n-Safely perform test activities according to the commissioning schedule, commissioning instructions and site procedures.\n-Document test results including the collection of test data records/plots and Results Record Sheets.\n\nLanguage:\n-English is required.\n-Ability with French, German or Finnish would be a plus.\n\nQualification:\nRequired:\n-Technical degree required in one of the following disciplines: Mechanical equipment or nuclear technician.\n-At least 2 years' commissioning/outage experience.\n-Flexibility in working time due to the commissioning schedule necessities.\n-Proficiency with MS Office Suite (and Documentum).\n-Basic knowledge of system commissioning activities.\n\nDesired:\n-Knowledge of pressurized Water Reactor (PWR) systems.\n-Commercial nuclear plant (PWR) operational or test experience.\n-Basic knowledge about nuclear power plant startup test activities (technically, organizational), including standard test equipment.\n\nPosition is filled as soon as suitable candidate is found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For more information please go to www.nipromec.com",
