				"kuvausteksti" : "Nipromec Oy Ltd is a global consulting and engineering company operating in energy-, industry- and offshore fields. \n \nWe are looking for I&C change database engineers for our client working on the Olkiluoto 3 project. Work starts as soon as possible, estimated duration is 10 months.\n\nUnder the authority of the I&C commissioning methods leader, the I&C database engineer will be in charge of following tasks identified with regards to the phases of the project:\n\nI&C commissioning change database:\n-Drafting a database specification according to change management procedures.\n-Design and implementation of the change database to record all the temporary modifications and changes from existing database and I&C systems.\n-Implementation of relevant reports functions.\n-Preparing and performing trainings to I&C and process commissioning teams.\n-Administration and upgrade of I&C change database according to procedure updates.\n\nSimulation management:\n-Defining assessment to be done before simulation block implementation.\n-Managing temporary modifications removal.\n-Track deviations in TM traceability processes.\n\nThe scope of responsibility of the I&C change database engineer is defined by the I&C commission-ing methods leader on behalf of the I&C commissioning branch manager, in accordance with the qualification evaluation and the actual needs. As such, additional tasks can be assigned to the holder of that position.\n\nSkills required:\n-Experience in database creation, implementation and administration mandatory.\n-Excellent knowledge of Visual basic, SQL, MS Access and excel.\n-Experience in configuration management.\n-Experience in I&C design/engineering/commissioning would be a plus.\n-EPR knowledge would be a plus.\n-Analysis and synthesis skills.\n-Rigorous especially for adherence to procedures in force on site including configuration man-agement.\n-Good relational and communication skills.\n-Good oral expression and writing skills.\n-Ability to work in an international al team.\n-Aware of HSE and IT security aspects.\n-Fluent English. Ability with French, Finnish or German would be a plus.\n\nPositions are filled as soon as suitable candidate are found. To apply please send application and CV with salary request to info@n-pro.fi . For more information please go to www.nipromec.com",
