				"kuvausteksti" : "Optimi Training Oy is a dynamic language school providing high-quality language and communication skills training for companies. Our diverse experience guarantees interesting and challenging customers for example in the banking, insurance, health care, service, IT and industrial fields. \n\nWe are now looking for qualified and experienced, native English-speaking freelance teachers in Helsinki for courses starting in January 2018. The ideal candidates should have at least three years of experience teaching professional English in a variety of companies and /or organisations. \n\nPlease send your application & CV by e-mail to \nsanna.saarinen@optimitraining.fi as soon as possible, latest by 24 November 2017.",
