				"kuvausteksti" : "Econia Business Services Ltd is founded in 1996 and serves Finnish and foreign companies in all work force related issues. Through us hundreds of persons get a job every year working in industry, manufacturing, logistic, client service and building industry. We are authorized HPL member.\n\nWe are looking for our client in Pori area\nGreenhouse workers\n\nWork is mainly picking and packing greenhouse products. Work is suitable for a person, who is looking for extra work (sometimes two weeks, sometimes two days). Your advantage is if you have experience on greenhouse working. \n\nWork begins when suitable persons are found and is on needed bases. If you're a fex. student looking for extra work, this might be your place. \n\nAll applicants need to have a work permit to work full time in Finland and speak understandable English or Finnish.\n\nIf you are interested in working at greenhouse on temporary and when needed bases, please apply to rekry@econia.com and mention in header the place you are applying to (Greenhouse worker).",
