				"kuvausteksti" : "For our office in Oulu we are currently seeking a:\r\n\r\nPROJECT MANAGER / PROJEKTIPÄÄLLIKKÖ\r\n\r\nVSB Uusiutuva Energia Suomi Oy is part of the VSB Group: one of Europe's leading providers of complete and full-service solutions for renewable energy project development. Since 1996 VSB has invested over 1 billion euros across Europe, creating wind farms and solar parks to supply green electricity to more than half a million households. For more information: www.vsb.energy/fi/fi/kotisivu/\r\n\r\nYOUR TASKS:\r\n\r\n- Project development for wind and solar facilities\r\n- Assessment of national regulatory framework\r\n- Understanding of conditions and opportunities for successful planning\r\n- Definition and implementation of market strategies\r\n- Networking with landowners, service providers, banks, political and regulatory institutions etc.\r\n\r\nYOUR PROFILE:\r\n\r\n- An academic degree\r\n- Project Management knowledge and experience\r\n- Legal or Financial Training\r\n- Sales or negotiation experience\r\n- Fluency in commercial English\r\n- Refined communication skills\r\n- Willingness to travel\r\n\r\nOUR OFFER:\r\n\r\n- A wide variety of challenging opportunities\r\n- Excellent career opportunities\r\n- Access to an internationally fast-growing industry\r\n- Motivating and harmonious work atmosphere\r\n\r\nPlease apply by email with CV and references to:  suomi@vsb.energy\r\n\r\nContact person: Christopher Small,  Tel. +358 (50) 410 8883\r\n\r\nFor more information: www.vsb.energy/fi/fi/kotisivu/",
