				"kuvausteksti" : "ARTASFin Oy was established in 2015 and is located in Otaniemi, Espoo. It is a specialized engineering and contracting company in the field of environmental protection technology. We are devoted to deliver the best complying and cost effective solutions that meet our customers' needs. We co-operate with well-known international manufacturers.\n\nWe deliver treatment processes for:\n\nWater treatment\nWastewater treatment\nGas treatment and desulphurization\nBioenergy: Biogas generation from organic wastes\n\nWe are looking for an efficient and professional administrative person, who would provide professional and high-quality support to the sales team and customers without forgetting positive and helpful spirit. This position is full time and continued until further notice.\n\nYour responsibilities together with our technical team\n\nPreparing and compiling commercial procurement documentation in the tender processes\nTaking in orders and order processing, searching for tender requests\nAnswering to customer inquiries related to orders, deliveries and invoices \nArranging meetings and appointments\nMaking travel arrangements\nTaking care of other administrative office routines\n\nYour team\n\nYou will be part of the small ARTASFin team, which provides daily support and back up function to help you succeed in your work.\n\nThe person we are looking for\n\nHas a degree in business administration (economics or sales), or equivalent\nMust be fluent (oral and written) in both Finnish and English, Swedish and Turkish is considered as an advantage (not obligatory)\nProficient in MS Office programs\nHas experience in handling tender processes\nPrevious knowledge of the environmental technologies is an advantage\n\nPersonal qualifications:\n\nIndependent and efficient team player\nContributing in creating positive and open atmosphere\nEnjoys routine tasks and wants to get things done\nGood written and verbal communication skills\nService-minded",
